  <para style="toc3">Ayub</para>
  <para style="mt1">AYUBU</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Ayubu aarĩ mũndũ mwega, na mũtongu, na mwĩtigĩri Ngai. Mũthenya ũmwe Shaitani nĩathiire mbere ya Ngai na akĩmũthitanga atĩ aatungataga Ngai tondũ wa indo iria aarathimĩtwo nacio. Ngai nĩetĩkĩririe Shaitani ahutie ũtonga, ciana, o na ũgima wake wa mwĩrĩ. Ũndũ ũcio warĩ wa kũgeria kana Ayubu nĩangĩaikarire ehokete Ngai. Ayubu o na aacemania na maũndũ macio, ndaagarũrire wĩhokeku wake harĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="ip">Arata atatũ a Ayubu, nĩo Elifazu, na Bilidadi, na Zofaru, nĩmookire kũmũũmĩrĩria. Arata acio meetĩkĩtie atĩ ũtonga na ũgima mwega wa mwĩrĩ ciarĩ kĩonereria kĩa irathimo cia Ngai. Arata acio makĩĩra Ayubu atĩ Ngai aamũherithagia nĩ ũndũ wa mehia marĩa eekĩte. O na gũtuĩka Ayubu na arata ake nĩmaguucanirie mũno, matiigana kuona kĩhonia kĩa maũndũ macio. Ayubu aarĩkĩrĩirie na kuuga atĩ we ndarĩ mehia eekĩte.</para>
  <para style="ip">Mũrata wa kana wa Ayubu wetagwo Elihu, ũrĩa warĩ mwĩthĩ, nĩacookire kwaria. Nĩarakarire tondũ arata acio matiigana kuona kĩhonia kĩa maũndũ marĩa Ayubu aagereire, kana macookio ma mĩario ya Ayubu agĩĩtetera. Elihu nĩageririe kuonia Ayubu na arata acio angĩ atĩ Ngai ndahĩtagia. Elihu aaragĩrĩria Ngai o ũndũ ũmwe na Ayubu, na akĩregana na arata acio atatũ nĩ ũndũ wa kuuga Ayubu aaherithagio ni mehia marĩa eekĩte. Nĩonanirie ũnene na ũkaru wa Ngai nĩ ũndũ wa ũmbi wake.</para>
  <para style="ip">Marigĩrĩrio-inĩ Ngai nĩomĩrĩirie Ayubu, no ndaigana kũmwĩra gĩtũmi gĩa kũnyariirĩka gwake. Ngai nĩamuonirie maũndũ maingĩ marĩa matangĩamenyekire nĩ mũndũ. Ngai nĩarathimire Ayubu na akĩmũcookeria ũtonga maita meerĩ ma ũrĩa aarĩ naguo mbere ĩyo. O na gũtuĩka Ayubu ndaigana kũmenya gĩtũmi gĩa kũnyariirĩka gwake-rĩ, we nĩaikarire arĩ mwĩhokeku harĩ Ngai, na nĩamenyaga atĩ mũthenya ũmwe Ngai nĩakamũhonokia kuuma kũrĩ maũndũ macio (19:25-27).</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="ip">O na gũtuĩka ibuku rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩarĩtie mũno ũhoro wa Ayubu, mwandĩki warĩo ti Ayubu. No nĩgũtuĩkaga ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ mũndũ wa kuuma Isiraeli warĩ na ũũgĩ wa kwandĩka marebeta.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Kĩambĩrĩria kĩa mathĩĩna ma Ayubu <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 1:1-2:13">1:1–2:13</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mĩario ya mbere <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 3:1-14:22">3:1–14:22</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mĩario ya keerĩ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 15:1-21:34">15:1–21:34</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mĩario ya gatatũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 22:1-31:40">22:1–31:40</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mĩario ya Elihu <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 32:1-37:24">32:1–37:24</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Macookio ma Ngai kũrĩ Ayubu <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 38:1-41:34">38:1–41:34</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kũhonio kwa Ayubu <char style="ior"><ref loc="JOB 42:1-17">42:1-17</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ciugo cia Kwambĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 10:23">Kĩam 10:23</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:11">Jak 5:11</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 11:7">Thab 11:7</ref></char>
    </note>Bũrũri-inĩ wa Uzu nĩ kwarĩ mũndũ watũire kuo wetagwo Ayubu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Bũrũri wa Uzu warĩ mwena wa irathĩro wa Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani; Ayubu ndaarĩ mũndũ wa Isiraeli.</char></note> Mũndũ ũcio ndaarĩ ũcuuke ningĩ aarĩ mũndũ mũrũngĩrĩru; nĩetigĩrĩte Ngai na agatheemaga maũndũ marĩa mooru. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Ayubu aarĩ na ariũ mũgwanja na airĩtu atatũ, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 13:2">Kĩam 13:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 103:10">Thab 103:10</ref></char></note>ningĩ nĩ aarĩ na ngʼondu 7,000, na ngamĩĩra 3,000, na ndegwa cia kũigana kuohwo macooki 500, na ndigiri 500, na nĩ aarĩ na ndungata nyingĩ mũno. Nĩwe warĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mũnene mũno kũrĩ andũ arĩa angĩ othe a mwena wa Irathĩro.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ariũ ake nĩmagĩaga na iruga o mũndũ riita rĩake gwake mũciĩ, na nĩmetaga aarĩ a nyina acio atatũ nĩguo marĩĩanĩre na manyuuanĩre nao. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NEH 12:30">Neh 12:30</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 21:10">1Ath 21:10</ref>, <ref loc="1KI 21:13">13</ref></char></note>Na matukũ ma maruga maathira, Ayubu nĩamatũmanagĩra moke nĩguo amatherie. Nĩokagĩra rũciinĩ tene akaruta igongona rĩa njino nĩ ũndũ wa o ũmwe wao, tondũ eeciiragia atĩrĩ, “No gũkorwo ciana ciakwa nĩciĩhĩtie ikaruma Ngai na ngoro.” Ũcio nĩguo warĩ mũtũgo wa Ayubu wa mahinda mothe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũgerio kwa Ayubu kwa Mbere</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 22:19">1Ath 22:19</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:31">Luk 22:31</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũmwe araika nĩmathiire kũrũgama mbere ya Jehova, na Shaitani o nake agĩthiĩ hamwe nao. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 5:8">1Pet 5:8</ref></char></note>Nake Jehova akĩũria Shaitani atĩrĩ, “Uuma kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Shaitani agĩcookeria Jehova atĩrĩ, “Nyuma kũriũnga thĩ, o na gũcangacanga kuo kũndũ na kũndũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 25:12">Thab 25:12</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:20">Thaam 20:20</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jehova akĩũria Shaitani atĩrĩ, “Nĩũcũũranĩtie ũhoro wa ndungata yakwa Ayubu? Ũkoona atĩ kũu thĩ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩ ũhaana take; ndarĩ ũcuuke na nĩmũrũngĩrĩru, mũndũ mwĩtigĩri-Ngai na ũtheemaga maũndũ marĩa mooru?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Shaitani agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ Ayubu agĩĩtigagĩra Ngai o ro ũguo tũhũ? <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1SA 25:16">1Sam 25:16</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 34:7">Thab 34:7</ref></char></note>Githĩ wee ndũmũirigĩire na ũkamũrigiicĩria hamwe na nyũmba yake, o hamwe na maũndũ make mothe? Nĩũrathimĩte wĩra wa moko make, nĩ ũndũ ũcio ũhiũ wake na ndũũru ciake ciyũrĩte bũrũri wothe. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 22:31">Luk 22:31</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 24:11">Alaw 24:11</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ta tambũrũkia guoko gwaku ũhutie indo ciothe iria arĩ nacio, na ti-itherũ ndarĩ hĩndĩ ategũkũruma o ũthiũ-inĩ waku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:13">1Akor 10:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jehova akĩĩra Shaitani atĩrĩ, “No wega, indo ciothe iria arĩ nacio nĩndaciiga moko-inĩ maku, nowe mwene ndũkanamũhutie.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Shaitani akiuma hau mbere ya Jehova.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũmwe hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ariũ na aarĩ a Ayubu maarĩĩaga na makanyua ndibei kwa mũrũ wa nyina wao ũrĩa mũkũrũ-rĩ, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 36:24">Kĩam 36:24</ref></char></note>mũkinyia-ũhoro agĩkora Ayubu, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ndegwa nĩkũrĩma ikũrĩmaga na mĩraũ, nacio ndigiri ikũrĩĩaga o hau hakuhĩ, <verse number="15" style="v"/>nao andũ a Sabea<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Andũ a Sabea maarĩ arĩithi arĩa morũũraga na mahiũ mao.</char></note> macitharĩkĩra na macitaha. Ndungata nacio maciũraga na rũhiũ rwa njora, na no niĩ nyiki ndahonoka, ndagĩũka gũkũrehere ũhoro!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 1:12">2Ath 1:12</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 10:2">Alaw 10:2</ref></char>
    </note>O akĩaragia-rĩ, mũkinyia-ũhoro ũngĩ agĩũka, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwaki wa Ngai uumire na igũrũ na wacina ngʼondu o na ndungata waniina biũ; no niĩ nyiki ndahonoka, ndagĩũka gũkũrehere ũhoro!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 11:28">Kĩam 11:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O akĩaragia-rĩ, mũkinyia-ũhoro ũngĩ agĩũka, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Akalidei<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Akalidei maarĩ arĩithi arĩa morũũraga na mahiũ mao. Maatũũraga Mesopotamia, na nĩo thuutha-inĩ maathondekire ũthamaki wa Babuloni.</char></note> meyũmba mbũtũ ithatũ, maatharĩkĩra ngamĩĩra ciaku na macitaha, maathiĩ nacio. Ndungata nacio maciũraga na rũhiũ rwa njora; na no niĩ nyiki ndahonoka, ndagĩũka gũkũrehere ũhoro!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>O akĩaragia-rĩ, mũkinyia-ũhoro o ũngĩ agĩũka, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ariũ na aarĩ aku mekũrĩĩaga, makĩnyuuaga ndibei kwa mũrũ wa nyina wao ũrĩa mũkũrũ; <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 11:6">Thab 11:6</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 24:26">Ezek 24:26</ref></char></note>na rĩrĩ, o hĩndĩ ĩyo rũhuho rũnene rwahurutana ruumĩte werũ-inĩ, na ruo rwahũũra nyũmba ĩyo koine ciayo inya, yamomoka, yamagwĩra maakua; na no niĩ nyiki ndahonoka, ndagĩũka gũkũrehere ũhoro!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 37:20">Kĩam 37:20</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:6">1Pet 5:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Ayubu aigua-ũhoro ũcio, akĩrũgama, agĩtembũranga nguo yake ya igũrũ, na akĩenjwo mũtwe. Agĩcooka akĩĩgũithia thĩ, akĩhooya Ngai, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ECC 5:15">Koh 5:15</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:7">1Tim 6:7</ref></char></note>akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ndoimire nda ya maitũ ndĩ njaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngoima thĩ ĩno ndĩ njaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩ Jehova waheanire, na nĩ Jehova wacookera:</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩĩtwa rĩa Jehova rĩrogoocwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 39:1">Thab 39:1</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:20">Arom 9:20</ref></char>
    </note>Thĩinĩ wa maũndũ macio mothe-rĩ, Ayubu ndaigana kwĩhia na ũndũ wa gũtuĩra Ngai mahĩtia.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kũgerio kwa Ayubu gwa keerĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 6:2">Kĩam 6:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 1:6">Ayub 1:6</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ nĩ kwarĩ mũthenya ũngĩ araika maathiire kũrũgama mbere ya Jehova, na Shaitani o nake agĩthiĩ hamwe nao kũrũgama mbere yake. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nake Jehova akĩũria Shaitani atĩrĩ, “Uuma kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Shaitani agĩcookeria Jehova atĩrĩ, “Nyuma kũriũnga thĩ o na gũcangacanga kuo kũndũ na kũndũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 20:20">Thaam 20:20</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 9:17">Ayub 9:17</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jehova akĩũria Shaitani atĩrĩ, “Nĩũcũũranĩtie ũhoro wa ndungata yakwa Ayubu? Ũkoona atĩ kũu thĩ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũhaana take; ndarĩ ũcuuke na nĩ mũrũngĩrĩru, mũndũ mwĩtigĩri-Ngai na ũtheemaga maũndũ marĩa mooru. Ningĩ no arũmĩtie wĩhokeku wake, o na gũtuĩka nĩwaningĩrĩirie ndĩmwanange hatarĩ gĩtũmi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nake Shaitani agĩcookeria Jehova, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Gĩkonde kĩrĩhagwo na gĩkonde! Mũndũ no arute indo ciake ciothe nĩguo ahonokie muoyo wake. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 102:5">Thab 102:5</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:7">Thaam 20:7</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ta tambũrũkia guoko gwaku ũhutie mahĩndĩ na nyama cia mwĩrĩ wake, na ti-itherũ ndarĩ hĩndĩ ategũkũruma o ũthiũ-inĩ waku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 12:7">2Akor 12:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 1:12">Ayub 1:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jehova akĩĩra Shaitani atĩrĩ, “No wega, rĩu arĩ moko-inĩ maku; no ndũkahutie muoyo wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:35">Gũcook 28:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Shaitani akiuma hau mbere ya Jehova, akĩnyamaria Ayubu na ironda ciarĩ na ruo mũno kuuma makinya ma magũrũ make nginya mũtwe. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 18:27">Kĩam 18:27</ref>; <ref loc="JER 6:26">Jer 6:26</ref></char></note>Nake Ayubu akĩoya gacere ka nyũngũ ethũage nako, agĩikara thĩ harĩa haitagwo mũhu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 5:8">1Athe 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="2KI 6:33">2Ath 6:33</ref></char>
    </note>Nake mũtumia wake akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Anga no ũrũmĩtie wĩhokeku waku o na rĩu? Ruma Ngai wĩkuĩre!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 1:21">Ayub 1:21</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:12">Jak 1:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Ayubu akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũraaria ta mũndũ-wa-nja mũkĩĩgu. Kaĩ turĩkĩamũkagĩra o maũndũ mega kuuma kũrĩ Ngai, na tũtiamũkĩre mathĩĩna?”</para>
  <para style="p">Thĩinĩ wa maũndũ macio mothe-rĩ, Ayubu ndaigana kwĩhia thĩinĩ wa mĩario yake.</para>
  <para style="s1">Arata Atatũ a Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 25:2">Kĩam 25:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:19">Joh 11:19</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 17:7">Ayub 17:7</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 15:23">2Sam 15:23</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 7:6">Josh 7:6</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa arata atatũ a Ayubu, nĩo Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Elifazu aarĩ wa kuuma Edomu.</char></note> na Bilidadi ũrĩa Mũshuhi, na Zofaru ũrĩa Mũnaamathi, maaiguire mathĩĩna marĩa mothe maakorete Ayubu-rĩ, makĩgĩa gĩathĩ, makiuma o mũndũ gwake na magĩcemania nĩguo mathiĩ makamũcakaithie o makĩmũhooreragia. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 17:7">Ayub 17:7</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 15:23">2Sam 15:23</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 7:6">Josh 7:6</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa maamuonire marĩ o haraaya-rĩ, makĩrigwo nĩwe nĩ ũrĩa aahaanaga; makĩambĩrĩria kũrĩra maanĩrĩire, na magĩtembũranga nguo ciao, o na makĩĩhurĩria rũkũngũ mĩtwe. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 3:26">Isa 3:26</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 17:28">Thim 17:28</ref></char></note>Ningĩ magĩcooka magĩikara thĩ hamwe nake matukũ mũgwanja, mũthenya na ũtukũ, na gũtirĩ mũndũ wamwaragĩria kiugo o na kĩmwe, nĩgũkorwo nĩmoonire atĩ kũnyamarĩka gwake kwarĩ kũnene mũno.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 15:10">Jer 15:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha wa matukũ macio, Ayubu agĩtumũra kanua, akĩruma mũthenya ũrĩa aaciarirwo. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 4:2">Koh 4:2</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 6:3">6:3</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:24">Math 26:24</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũthenya ũrĩa niĩ ndaciarirwo ũroora,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ũtukũ ũcio kwerirwo atĩrĩ, ‘Mũtumia nĩaciara mwana wa kahĩĩ!’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, ũrotuĩka o nduma;</para>
  <para style="q2">Ngai arĩ igũrũ aroaga kũũrũmbũiya;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũthenya ũcio ũroaga gũthererwo nĩ ũtheri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 10:21">Ayub 10:21</ref>; <ref loc="JER 2:6">Jer 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="JER 13:6">13:6</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũcio ũrokĩĩnyiitĩrwo nĩ nduma nene na kĩĩruru gĩa gĩkuũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrohumbĩrwo nĩ itu;</para>
  <para style="q2">nduma ĩrotooria ũtheri waguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ũtukũ ũcio-rĩ, ũronyiitwo nĩ nduma ndumanu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũroaga gũtaranĩrio na mĩthenya ĩrĩa ĩngĩ ya mwaka,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ũtarwo harĩ mweri o na ũrĩkũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 20:5">Thab 20:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 51:48">Jer 51:48</ref></char>
    </note>Ũtukũ ũcio ũrothaata;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtikanoigwo ngemi ũtukũ ũcio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:21">Kĩam 1:21</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 74:14">Thab 74:14</ref></char>
    </note>Arĩa marumaga mĩthenya maroruma mũthenya ũcio,</para>
  <para style="q2">o acio moĩ kwarahũra nyamũ ĩrĩa ĩĩtagwo Leviathani.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 41:8">Ayub 41:8</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 3:4">Ahib 3:4</ref></char>
    </note>Njata ciaguo cia rũciinĩ irotuĩka nduma;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũroeterera ũtheri na wage kũwona,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ũroaga kuona ruoro rũgĩtema,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>nĩ ũndũ ndũigana kũhinga mĩrango ya nda ya maitũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndũigana kũgirĩrĩria maitho makwa kuona thĩĩna.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Ndaagire gũkua ngĩciarwo nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ndaagire gũkua ngiuma nda nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ndaamũkĩrirwo maru-inĩ nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ndaamũkĩrirwo nyondo-inĩ atĩ nĩguo nyongithio nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 17:13">Ayub 17:13</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 8:22">Isa 8:22</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo rĩu ingĩkomete ndĩ na thayũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩu ingĩrĩ toro hurũkĩte</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 14:9">Isa 14:9</ref>; <ref loc="NAM 3:7">Nahu 3:7</ref></char>
    </note>hamwe na athamaki na aheani kĩrĩra a gũkũ thĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa meeyakĩire kũndũ kũrĩa kwanangĩku rĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>o hamwe na aathani arĩa maarĩ na thahabu,</para>
  <para style="q2">o arĩa maiyũrĩtie nyũmba ciao betha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 58:8">Thab 58:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩ kĩĩ kĩagiririe thikwo tĩĩri-inĩ ta kĩhuno</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ta gakenge karĩa gatoonire ũtheri wa riũa?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Kũu andũ arĩa aaganu nĩmatigĩte kũnyamarĩka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kũu arĩa anogu nĩmahurũkĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 51:14">Isa 51:14</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 15:13">Kĩam 15:13</ref></char>
    </note>Kũu-rĩ, mĩgwate o nayo nĩĩkenagĩra kwaraha kwayo;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩĩtigĩte kũigua kĩgũthũko kĩa nyabaara ya ngombo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Andũ arĩa anini na arĩa anene othe marĩ kuo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo ngombo nĩĩrekereirio kuuma kũrĩ mũmĩathi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 1:10">1Sam 1:10</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 27:30-31">Ezek 27:30-31</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga andũ arĩa marĩ na mĩnyamaro maheo ũtheri,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo muoyo ũkaheo arĩa marĩ na ruo rwa ngoro,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 9:6">Kũg 9:6</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 2:4">Thim 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>o acio meriragĩria gĩkuũ na gĩtingĩũka,</para>
  <para style="q2">o arĩa magĩcaragia gũkĩra kĩndũ kĩa goro kĩrĩa kĩhithe,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>acio maiyũragwo nĩ gĩkeno</para>
  <para style="q2">magakena maakinya mbĩrĩra?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 4:19">Thim 4:19</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 88:8">Thab 88:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga muoyo ũheo mũndũ ũũrĩte njĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ũcio mũhingĩrĩrie nĩ Ngai?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 5:1">Thab 5:1</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 1:15">1Sam 1:15</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ handũ ha ndĩe irio, no kuumwo nyumagwo nĩ ngoro;</para>
  <para style="q2">nakuo gũcaaya gwakwa gũitĩkaga ta maaĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 7:9">Ayub 7:9</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 13:3">Hos 13:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ũndũ ũrĩa ndeetigagĩra nĩũngorete;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũndũ ũrĩa wamakagia mũno nĩguo ũnginyĩrĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 48:22">Isa 48:22</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:4">Ayub 7:4</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 7:14">14</ref></char>
    </note>Ndionaga thayũ, o na kana ngahoorera;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndionaga ũhurũko, no mĩnyamaro.”</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Elifazu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 36:11">Kĩam 36:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani agĩcookia, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Mũndũ angĩgeria gũkũgwetera koigo kamwe-rĩ, hihi wamũkirĩrĩria?</para>
  <para style="q2">No rĩrĩ, nũũ ũngĩhota kwĩgirĩrĩria kwaria?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:2">Gũcook 32:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 35:3">Isa 35:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ririkana ũrĩa wanataara andũ aingĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũrĩa wanekĩra moko marĩa maregeru hinya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 1:7">Isa 1:7</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 12:12">Ahib 12:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ciugo ciaku cianatiirĩrĩra arĩa manahĩngwo makenda kũgũa;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩwe wanekĩra maru marĩa magondoku hinya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>No rĩu-rĩ, nĩũkoretwo nĩ thĩĩna, nawe ũkoorwo nĩ hinya;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũhũũrĩtwo, nawe ũkanyiitwo nĩ kĩmako.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 3:26">Thim 3:26</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 6:9">Kĩam 6:9</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ wĩtigĩri Ngai waku tiguo wagĩrĩirwo gũtuĩka ũũmĩrĩru waku,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩthiĩre yaku ĩtarĩ ũcuuke-rĩ, githĩ tiyo mwĩhoko waku?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 41:12">Thab 41:12</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 12:21">Thim 12:21</ref></char>
    </note>“Ta wĩcũũranie atĩrĩ: Nĩ mũndũ ũrĩkũ wanathĩĩnĩka atekĩte ũũru?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ kũ andũ arĩa arũngĩrĩru marĩ maniinwo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 14:18">Atiir 14:18</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 6:7">Agal 6:7</ref></char>
    </note>Niĩ ũrĩa nyonete-rĩ, nĩ atĩ andũ arĩa marĩmaga ũũru,</para>
  <para style="q2">na arĩa mahaandaga thĩĩna-rĩ, maũndũ macio no mo magethaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 15:10">Thaam 15:10</ref>; <ref loc="2TH 2:8">2Athe 2:8</ref></char>
    </note>Manangagwo nĩ mĩhũmũ ya Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q2">makaniinwo nĩ kĩhuhũkanio kĩa marakara make.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Mĩrũũthi no ĩrume na ĩrarame,</para>
  <para style="q2">no magego ma mĩrũũthi ĩyo mĩnene nĩmakoinangwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:41">Gũcook 28:41</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 30:14">Thim 30:14</ref></char>
    </note>Mũrũũthi nĩũkuaga nĩ kwaga gĩa kũguĩma,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ciana cia mũrũũthi wa mũgoma ikahurunjũka.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“Nĩ kũrĩ kohoro karanginyĩire na hitho,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo matũ makwa marakaigua gakĩhehanwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Ũtukũ ngĩĩcũũrania ũhoro wa cioneki cia kũmakania,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtukũ rĩrĩa andũ makoragwo marĩ toro mũnene,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 48:6">Thab 48:6</ref>; <ref loc="HAB 3:16">Hab 3:16</ref></char>
    </note>ngĩnyiitwo nĩ guoya na kũinaina,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo mahĩndĩ makwa mothe magĩthingitha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>O hĩndĩ ĩyo roho ũraahĩtũkĩra o ũthiũ-inĩ wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio njuĩrĩ cia mwĩrĩ wakwa irambarara.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 19:12">1Ath 19:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Roho ũcio ũrarũgama,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ndinahota kũmenya ũrĩa ũratariĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">Mbere yakwa hararũgama mũhianĩre wa kĩndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩracooka ndĩraigua gũkĩario na mĩheehũ gũkĩũrio atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:2">Ayub 9:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 18:26">Thab 18:26</ref></char>
    </note>‘Mũndũ wa gũkua-rĩ, aahota gũtuĩka mũthingu gũkĩra Ngai?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũndũ aahota gũtuĩka mũtheru gũkĩra Mũmũũmbi?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo Ngai ndangĩhota kwĩhoka ndungata ciake-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na angĩkorwo nĩonaga araika ake marĩ na mahĩtia-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 64:8">Isa 64:8</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref></char>
    </note>githĩ to oone mahĩtia maingĩ mũno ma andũ arĩa matũũraga nyũmba cia ndoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">acio mĩthingi yao ĩrĩ rũkũngũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">acio mamemendagwo na ihenya gũkĩra kĩĩhuruta!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 14:2">Ayub 14:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 89:47">Thab 89:47</ref></char>
    </note>Kuuma rũciinĩ nginya hwaĩ-inĩ moinangagwo tũcunjĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">magathira tene na tene matekũrũmbũiyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:24">Joh 8:24</ref>; <ref loc="JER 9:3">Jer 9:3</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ mĩkanda ya hema yao ndĩmunyũrĩtwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo makue matarĩ na ũũgĩ?’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Wenda gwĩtana, ĩtana, no rĩrĩ, nũũ ũngĩgwĩtĩka?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ ũrĩkũ wa arĩa atheru ũngĩũrĩra kũrĩ we?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 12:16">Thim 12:16</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 5:26">Agal 5:26</ref></char>
    </note>Rũngʼathio rũũragaga kĩrimũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũiru ũkooraga mũndũ ũrĩa mũkĩĩgu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 37:35">Thab 37:35</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 3:33">Thim 3:33</ref></char>
    </note>Niĩ mwene nĩnyonete kĩrimũ gĩkĩgĩa na mĩri,</para>
  <para style="q2">no-o rĩmwe nyũmba yakĩo ĩkĩrumwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ciana ciake nĩiraihanĩrĩirie na ũgitĩri,</para>
  <para style="q2">ihatĩrĩirio igooti-inĩ itarĩ na mũndũ wa gũciciirĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 26:16">Alaw 26:16</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 6:15">Mik 6:15</ref></char>
    </note>Ũrĩa mũhũtu arĩĩaga magetha make,</para>
  <para style="q2">amoyaga o na marĩ mĩigua-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa anyootu makahũmagĩra ũtonga wao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo hatĩka ndĩkunũkaga kuuma thĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana thĩĩna ũkamera tĩĩri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 3:17">Kĩam 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 51:5">Thab 51:5</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, mũndũ aciaragwo arĩ wa kuonaga thĩĩna,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa na ma thandĩ cia mwaki irathũkaga na igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩ, korwo nĩ niĩ ingĩthaitha Mũrungu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ingĩneana ciira wakwa kũrĩ we.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 29:29">Gũcook 29:29</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:33">Arom 11:33</ref></char>
    </note>We ekaga maũndũ ma magegania marĩa mataangĩmenyeka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akaringa ciama itangĩtarĩka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:45">Math 5:45</ref>; <ref loc="JER 14:22">Jer 14:22</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩwe uuragĩria thĩ mbura;</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩwe ũrehagĩra bũrũri maaĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Arĩa menyiihagia nĩwe ũmatũũgagĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa marĩ na kĩeha moyagwo na igũrũ makagitĩrwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NEH 4:15">Neh 4:15</ref>; <ref loc="JER 19:7">Jer 19:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩwe ũthaatagia mĩbango ya arĩa marĩ waara,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha moko mao matikagĩe na ũhootani.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 37:24">Ayub 37:24</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:19">1Akor 3:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩanyiitaga arĩa oogĩ waara-inĩ wao,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo mathugunda ma arĩa oingumania akaameheria biũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nduma ĩmakoraga kũrĩ o mũthenya;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũthenya barigici makahambataga taarĩ ũtukũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:23">Thaam 22:23</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 4:10">Ayub 4:10</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩahonokagia arĩa abatari kuuma kũrĩ rũhiũ rwa njora rũrĩa rũrĩ tũnua-inĩ twao;</para>
  <para style="q2">amahonokagia moko-inĩ ma arĩa marĩ hinya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio athĩĩni makagĩa na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ciira ũtarĩ wa kĩhooto ũgatumia kanua.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 94:12">Thab 94:12</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 12:5-11">Ahib 12:5-11</ref></char>
    </note>“Kũrathimwo nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũrũngagwo nĩ Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndũkamene irũithia rĩa Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nĩaguraranagia, no rĩrĩ, acookaga akooha nguraro ĩyo wega;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩatiihanagia, no moko make no mo mahonanagia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 3:17">Dan 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 91:10">Thab 91:10</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩagagũteithũra harĩ mĩtino ĩtandatũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ĩrĩ mũgwanja-rĩ, gũtirĩ ũũru ũgaagũkora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 39:18">Jer 39:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ya ngʼaragu nĩagagũkũũra kuuma kũrĩ gĩkuũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ hĩndĩ ya mbaara agũkũũre ndũkooragwo na rũhiũ rwa njora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 31:20">Thab 31:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩũkagitĩrwo harĩ rũcamiũ rwa rũrĩmĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndũgetigĩra hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwanangĩko ũgooka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nĩũgathekerera mwanangĩko na ngʼaragu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndũgetigĩra nyamũ cia gũkũ thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 28:15">Isa 28:15</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 34:25">Ezek 34:25</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩũkagĩa na kĩrĩkanĩro na mahiga ma werũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio nyamũ cia gĩthaka itũũre irĩ na thayũ nawe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nawe ũikarage ũũĩ atĩ hema yaku nĩ ngitĩre;</para>
  <para style="q2">nawe nĩũkooya ithabu rĩa indo ciaku ũkore hatirĩ kĩndũ kĩũrĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:4">Gũcook 28:4</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 72:16">Thab 72:16</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩũkamenya atĩ ciana ciaku nĩikaingĩha,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio njiaro ciaku cingĩhe o ta nyeki ya gũkũ thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 15:15">Kĩam 15:15</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 8:13">Koh 8:13</ref></char>
    </note>Ũgaathiĩ mbĩrĩra-inĩ ũrĩ o na hinya,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũhaana ta itĩĩa cia ngano ĩgethetwo hĩndĩ ya magetha.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>“Nĩtũtuĩrĩtie ũhoro ũyũ, na nĩ wa ma.</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ ũndũ ũcio kĩũigue na ũũmenye wee mwene.”</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 31:6">Ayub 31:6</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 5:27">Dan 5:27</ref></char>
    </note>“Naarĩ korwo ruo rũrũ ndĩ naruo rwathimwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩnyamaro ĩno ndĩ nayo yothe ĩigĩrĩrwo ratiri igũrũ!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 4:29">1Ath 4:29</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ yakorwo ĩrĩ mĩritũ gũkĩra mũthanga ũrĩa ũrĩ maria-inĩ marĩa manene;</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩkĩo ndĩrahiũhire kwaria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 17:1">Kĩam 17:1</ref>; <ref loc="JER 15:18">Jer 15:18</ref></char>
    </note>Mĩguĩ ya Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩĩndoonyete,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo roho wakwa nĩũranyua ũrũrũ wayo;</para>
  <para style="q2">maũndũ ma kũmakania mũno ma Ngai nĩmerekeirio harĩ niĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Njagĩ ya werũ-inĩ-rĩ, nĩyaanagia rĩrĩa ĩrĩ na nyeki ya kũrĩa,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ndegwa ĩkaania rĩrĩa ĩtuĩrĩirwo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 107:18">Thab 107:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Irio itarĩ mũcamo nĩ irĩĩkaga itekĩrĩtwo cumbĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũruru wa itumbĩ ũrĩa mwerũ-rĩ, nĩ urĩ mũrĩo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Niĩ ndingĩcihutia;</para>
  <para style="q2">irio ta icio no itũme njire ngoro.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“Naarĩ korwo ndaheo ũndũ ũrĩa ndĩrahooya,</para>
  <para style="q2">korwo Ngai aahe ũndũ ũrĩa ndĩrerirĩria,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 11:15">Ndar 11:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>naguo nĩ atĩ Ngai eetĩkĩre kũũmemenda,</para>
  <para style="q2">arekererie guoko gwake kũũniine!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 2:11">Ayub 2:11</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 8:38">Mar 8:38</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo no ngĩe na ũndũ wa kũũhooreria,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũndũ wa gĩkeno ruo-inĩ rũrũ rũtarathira,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ niĩ ndikaanĩte ciugo cia Ũrĩa Mũtheru.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Ndĩ na hinya ũrĩkũ atĩ nĩguo njikare ndĩ na mwĩhoko?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ndĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩkũ atĩ nĩguo ngirĩrĩrie?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Niĩ ndĩ hinya ta ihiga?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mwĩrĩ wakwa nĩ wa gĩcango?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 26:2">Ayub 26:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Niĩ ndĩ na hinya wa gwĩteithia,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuona atĩ rĩu nĩndunyĩtwo ũhootani?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 20:42">1Sam 20:42</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:17">1Joh 3:17</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũndũ ũtarĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro aagĩrĩire gũteithio nĩ arata ake,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na angĩkorwo nĩatiganĩirie ũhoro wa gwĩtigĩra Ũrĩa Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>No ariũ a baba maagĩte kwĩhokeka o ta tũrũũĩ tũrĩa tũhũaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ o ta tũrũũĩ tũrĩa tũiyũraga tũkoina,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 147:18">Thab 147:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>rĩrĩa tũirĩtio nĩ mbarabu ĩgĩtweka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na tũkaiyũrwo nĩ tharunji ĩrĩa ĩratweka,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 24:19">Ayub 24:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>no rĩrĩ, tũtithereraga rĩrĩa kwara,</para>
  <para style="q2">na hĩndĩ ya ũrugarĩ tũkahũa mĩtaro-inĩ yatuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ikundi cia agendi nĩithaamaga njĩra ciacio,</para>
  <para style="q2">ikambata werũ-inĩ, igathirĩra kuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 25:15">Kĩam 25:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ikundi cia agendi cia Tema icaragia maaĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">agendi a wonjoria a Sheba makamacaria marĩ na mwĩhoko.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 14:3">Jer 14:3</ref>; <ref loc="JOL 1:11">Joel 1:11</ref></char>
    </note>Magathĩĩnĩka, tondũ makoretwo marĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro;</para>
  <para style="q2">no maakinya ho magakora hatirĩ kĩndũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 38:11">Thab 38:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O na inyuĩ-rĩ, mũtuĩkĩte andũ matangĩheana ũteithio;</para>
  <para style="q2">muonaga ũndũ wa kũmakania mũgetigĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 35:31">Ndar 35:31</ref>; <ref loc="JER 15:10">Jer 15:10</ref></char>
    </note>Niĩ-rĩ, nĩ ndĩ ndoiga atĩrĩ: ‘Heanai kĩndũ nĩ ũndũ wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngũũrai na indo cianyu,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>honokiai guoko-inĩ gwa thũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngũũrai kuuma moko-inĩ ma arĩa matarĩ tha’?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 2:10">Ayub 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 5:2">Koh 5:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Atĩrĩrĩ, ndutaai ũhoro na nĩngũkira;</para>
  <para style="q2">nyonereriai harĩa hĩtĩtie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Kaĩ ciugo cia ma irĩ ruo-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">No rĩrĩ, ngarari cianyu nĩ kĩhooto kĩrĩkũ irarehe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Anga mũrenda kũruta mahĩtia ũrĩa njugĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũgatua ciugo cia mũndũ ũũmĩirwo tha taarĩ rũhuho?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOL 3:3">Joel 3:3</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 10:2">Isa 10:2</ref></char>
    </note>Inyuĩ o na no mũcuukĩre mwana wa ngoriai mĩtĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mwendie mũrata wanyu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“No rĩu-rĩ, ndamũthaitha mwĩtĩkĩre kũndora.</para>
  <para style="q2">Anga no ngĩheenanie o maitho-inĩ manyu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 40:27">Isa 40:27</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 66:10">Thab 66:10</ref></char>
    </note>Mwĩcũraniei nĩguo mũtikogomie kĩhooto;</para>
  <para style="q2">njookererai, nĩgũkorwo wĩhokeku wakwa nĩguo ũraarũithio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 12:11">Ayub 12:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ kũrĩ wĩhia ũrĩ mĩromo-inĩ yakwa?</para>
  <para style="q2">Anga kanua gakwa gatingĩhota gũkũũrana maũndũ ma rũmena?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 14:14">Ayub 14:14</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 25:50">Alaw 25:50</ref></char>
    </note>“Githĩ mũndũ ndakoragwo na ũtungata mũritũ gũkũ thĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Githĩ matukũ make matihaana o ta ma mũndũ mwandĩke wĩra?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 2:23">Koh 2:23</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 19:13">Alaw 19:13</ref></char>
    </note>O ta ngombo ĩkwĩrirĩria ciĩruru cia hwaĩ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ta mũndũ mwandĩke ũgũthethũkĩra mũcaara wake-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 6:6">Thab 6:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 16:9">Isa 16:9</ref></char>
    </note>ũguo nĩguo niĩ ngaĩirwo mĩeri ya tũhũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngatuĩrwo atĩ ũtukũ ndaarage ndĩ na kĩeha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:67">Gũcook 28:67</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa ndakoma ndĩyũragia atĩrĩ, ‘Ndĩrĩũkĩra rĩ?’</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũtukũ ũkaraiha, na ngaraara ngĩĩgarũra nginya gũgakĩa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 14:11">Isa 14:11</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 28:35">Gũcook 28:35</ref></char>
    </note>Mwĩrĩ wakwa ũiyũrĩtwo nĩ igunyũ na ngũcĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakĩo gĩkonde gĩakwa gĩatũkangĩte na gĩgatogota.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>“Matukũ makwa maraathira na ihenya rĩkĩrĩte rĩa kanyamũ karĩa gakonjithanagia uuthi ngoora ĩgĩtumwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">magagĩkinya mũthia itarĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 27:46">Kĩam 27:46</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 78:39">Thab 78:39</ref></char>
    </note>Wee Ngai-rĩ, ririkana atĩ muoyo wakwa no ta mĩhũmũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">namo maitho makwa matigacooka kuona ũndũ mwega rĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Riitho rĩrĩa rĩranyona rĩtigacooka kũnyona rĩngĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũkaanjaria, no ndigakorwo ho.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="AMO 9:2">Amos 9:2</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 12:23">2Sam 12:23</ref></char>
    </note>O ta ũrĩa itu rĩthiiaga rĩkabuĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũguo noguo ũrĩa ũthiiaga mbĩrĩra-inĩ atacookaga kuoneka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Ndagacooka kũinũka gwake mũciĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">harĩa aaikaraga ndagacooka kuonwo ho.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:2">Thab 22:2</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 1:10">1Sam 1:10</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, ndigũkira;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngwaria nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa roho wakwa ũrĩ na ruo,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩtetere nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa ngoro yakwa ĩrĩ na marũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩ iria rĩa maaĩ, kana nyamũ ĩrĩa nene ĩtũũraga iria thĩinĩ kũrĩa kũriku,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ nĩkĩo nangagĩrwo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa ngwĩciiria ũrĩrĩ wakwa nĩguo ũkũũhooreria,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atĩ gĩtanda gĩakwa no kĩĩniinĩre gũteta-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:34">Ayub 9:34</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 41:8">Kĩam 41:8</ref></char>
    </note>o na hĩndĩ ĩyo ũũmakagia na irooto,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ũkanjiguithia guoya na cioneki,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 19:4">1Ath 19:4</ref>; <ref loc="REV 9:6">Kũg 9:6</ref></char>
    </note>nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngathuura kaba gũitwo, na gĩkuũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">handũ ha gũikara na mwĩrĩ ũyũ wakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:21">Ayub 9:21</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 39:13">Thab 39:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩthũire muoyo wakwa; ndikwenda gũtũũra nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="q2">Tigana na niĩ tondũ matukũ makwa no ma tũhũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 8:4">Thab 8:4</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 2:6">Ahib 2:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũndũ-rĩ, akĩrĩ kĩ, tondũ ũmwĩkĩrĩire ũguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkamũrũmbũyia mũno ũguo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 73:14">Thab 73:14</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 14:3">Ayub 14:3</ref></char>
    </note>atĩ ũmũthuthuuragia ngoro o rũciinĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkamũgeragia mahinda mothe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Kaĩ gũtarĩ hĩndĩ ũgaatiga gũikara ũndorete,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũtigane na niĩ o na kahinda kanini?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 35:6">Ayub 35:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Angĩkorwo nĩnjĩhĩtie-rĩ, nĩ atĩa niĩ ngwĩkĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee mũrori wa andũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmĩte ũnjorote?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ nduĩkĩte mũrigo harĩwe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 119:20">Thab 119:20</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:19">Kĩam 3:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ kĩĩ kĩragiria ũnjohere mahĩtia makwa</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndekere mehia makwa?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩgũkorwo ndĩ hakuhĩ gũkoma tĩĩri-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nawe nĩũkanjaria no ndigakorwo ho.”</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Bilidadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 25:2">Kĩam 25:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 18:1">Ayub 18:1</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Bilidadi ũrĩa Mũshuhi agĩcookia, akĩũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Nĩ nginya rĩ ũgũikara ũkĩaragia maũndũ ta macio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ciugo ciaku no ta inegene rĩa rũhuho rũkĩhurutana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:5">Arom 3:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 12:1">Jer 12:1</ref></char>
    </note>Mũrungu-rĩ, nĩogomagia ciira wa kĩhooto?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩogomagia ũndũ ũrĩa ũrĩ wa ma?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa ciana ciaku ciamwĩhĩirie-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩacirekereirie iherithio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma cio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:15">Ayub 9:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, wee ũngĩcũthĩrĩria Mũrungu</para>
  <para style="q2">na wĩthaithanĩrĩre harĩ Ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 58:9">Isa 58:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>ũngĩkorwo ũrĩ mũtheru na mũrũngĩrĩru-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na rĩu no arahũke nĩ ũndũ waku</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo agũcookie handũ harĩa hakwagĩrĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>O na gũtuĩka kĩambĩrĩria gĩaku no kĩoneke kĩrĩ kĩnini,</para>
  <para style="q2">thuutha-inĩ nĩũkagaacĩra mũno.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:7">Gũcook 32:7</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 71:18">Thab 71:18</ref></char>
    </note>“Ũria ũhoro harĩ njiarwa cia tene,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũtuĩrie maũndũ marĩa maithe mao meerutire,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 47:9">Kĩam 47:9</ref>; <ref loc="1CH 29:15">1Maũ 29:15</ref></char>
    </note>nĩgũkorwo ithuĩ tũraciarirwo o ro ira na tũtirĩ ũndũ tũũĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo matukũ maitũ ma gũikara gũkũ thĩ no ta kĩĩruru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Acio githĩ to makũrute na makũhe ũhoro?</para>
  <para style="q2">Acio githĩ to maarie ũhoro marĩ na ũmenyo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Irura-rĩ, no rĩkũre handũ hatarĩ itomboya?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ithanjĩ-rĩ, no rĩtheereme handũ hatarĩ maaĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 19:26">2Ath 19:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩngĩkũrĩra handũ hatarĩ maaĩ rĩũmaga narua gũkĩra nyeki,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na rĩtakinyĩte rĩa gũtuuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 37:38">Thab 37:38</ref>; <ref loc="JER 17:6">Jer 17:6</ref></char>
    </note>Ũcio nĩguo mũthia wa arĩa othe mariganagĩrwo nĩ Mũrungu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũguo no ta guo mwĩhoko wa arĩa matooĩ Ngai ũthiraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 59:5">Isa 59:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kĩrĩa ehokete no kĩndũ kĩhũthũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩrĩa egiritanagia nakĩo no ta rũrenda rwa mbũmbũĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:26-27">Math 7:26-27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Etiiranagia na rũrenda rwake, naruo rũgatuĩka;</para>
  <para style="q2">akenyiitĩrĩra harĩ ruo, no rũtingĩmũtiirĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 80:11">Thab 80:11</ref>; <ref loc="JER 11:16">Jer 11:16</ref></char>
    </note>Ahaana ta mũtĩ ũitĩrĩirio maaĩ wega ũrĩ riũa-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtambũrũkĩtie thuuna ciaguo mũgũnda-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>mĩri yaguo ĩĩthiororokeirie kĩhumbu kĩa mahiga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩcaragia ha kwĩgwatĩrĩra rwaro-inĩ rwa mahiga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa wakũũrwo harĩa ũraarĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">handũ hau hagakaana mũtĩ ũcio, hakoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ndirĩ ndakuona.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:30">Ayub 15:30</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 1:4">Koh 1:4</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ muoyo waguo ũmaga ũgathira,</para>
  <para style="q2">naho hau tĩĩri-inĩ ũcio hagakũra mĩtĩ ĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>“Ti-itherũ Mũrungu ndangĩrega mũndũ ũtarĩ ũcuuke,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ekĩre moko ma arĩa mekaga ũũru hinya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZR 3:13">Ezar 3:13</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 126:2">Thab 126:2</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, no arĩiyũria kanua gaku mĩtheko,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩromo yaku yanĩrĩre nĩ gũkena.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 6:10">Thab 6:10</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 8:3">1Sam 8:3</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 14:11">Thim 14:11</ref></char>
    </note>Thũ ciaku nĩikahumbwo thoni,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio hema cia arĩa aaganu itigacooka kuonwo.”</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:30">Arom 3:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ti-itherũ nĩnjũũĩ ũhoro ũcio nĩ wa ma.</para>
  <para style="q2">No rĩrĩ, mũndũ angĩhota atĩa gũkorwo arĩ mũthingu mbere ya Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>O na korwo mũndũ enda gũkararania na Ngai-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndangĩhota kũmũcookeria kĩũria o na kĩmwe harĩ ciũria ngiri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 2:20">Dan 2:20</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 13:12">2Maũ 13:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ũũgĩ wake nĩ mũingĩ mũno, na ũhoti wake nĩ mũnene.</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ wanaregana nake akĩgaacĩra?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 17:20">Math 17:20</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 1:4">Mik 1:4</ref></char>
    </note>Eeheragia irĩma itekũmenya,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agacingʼaũrania nĩ kũrakara.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 12:26">Ahib 12:26</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 2:21">Isa 2:21</ref></char>
    </note>Athingithagia thĩ ĩkoima handũ hayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akainainia itugĩ ciayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 34:4">Isa 34:4</ref>; <ref loc="ZEP 1:15">Zef 1:15</ref></char>
    </note>Aathaga riũa rĩkaaga kũratha;</para>
  <para style="q2">nake agiragĩrĩria ũtheri wa njata.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:1">Kĩam 1:1</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 1:8">8</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:19">Joh 6:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩwe watambũrũkirie igũrũ arĩ o wiki,</para>
  <para style="q2">na athiiaga agĩkinyangaga makũmbĩ ma iria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩwe Mũũmbi wa njata iria ciĩtagwo Nduba, na Karaũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na Kĩrĩmĩra, o na ikundi cia njata cia mwena wa gũthini.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 6:22">Gũcook 6:22</ref>; <ref loc="JER 32:20">Jer 32:20</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩekaga magegania matangĩmenyeka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akaringa ciama itangĩtarĩka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 23:8-9">Ayub 23:8-9</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 35:14">35:14</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa aahĩtũkĩra harĩa ndĩ, ndingĩmuona;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na rĩrĩa aathiĩra harĩa ndĩ ndimenyaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 23:20">Ndar 23:20</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 45:9">Isa 45:9</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:20">Arom 9:20</ref></char>
    </note>Angĩgutha kĩndũ-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩhota kũmũgiria?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũngĩmũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩ atĩa ũreka?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 10:15">Ayub 10:15</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 30:7">Isa 30:7</ref></char>
    </note>Ngai ndahingagĩrĩria marakara make;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na arĩa maateithagĩrĩria Rahabu nĩmamũinamagĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>“Niĩ-rĩ, ndaakĩhota atĩa kũmũkararia?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ingĩruta kũ ciugo cia kũmũcookeria?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 8:5">Ayub 8:5</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 50:6">Thab 50:6</ref></char>
    </note>O na korwo ndihĩtĩtie-rĩ, ndingĩhota kũmũcookeria ũndũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa ingĩĩka no gũthaitha ingĩthaitha Mũnjiirithia anjiguĩre tha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>O na ingĩamwĩtire nake anjĩtĩke-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndingĩĩtĩkia nĩangĩathikĩrĩirie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:10">Thab 10:10</ref>; <ref loc="JON 1:4">Jon 1:4</ref></char>
    </note>We angĩamemendire na kĩhuhũkanio,</para>
  <para style="q2">na aingĩhie ironda ciakwa hatarĩ gĩtũmi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ndarekaga njookererwo nĩ mĩhũmũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">no nĩahatagĩrĩria na mathĩĩna.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Korwo no ũhoro wa hinya-rĩ, we arĩ hinya mũno!</para>
  <para style="q2">Na korwo no ũhoro wa ciira wa kĩhooto-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩmwĩta?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>O na korwo ndiahĩtĩtie-rĩ, kanua gakwa no kandue mũhĩtia;</para>
  <para style="q2">korwo ndiarĩ na ũcuuke-rĩ, nĩkangĩanduire mũhĩtia.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 6:9">Kĩam 6:9</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 11:15">Ndar 11:15</ref></char>
    </note>“O na gũtuĩka ndirĩ na ũcuuke-rĩ, ndikwĩrĩrĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">muoyo wakwa nĩndĩwagĩire kĩene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 9:2">Koh 9:2</ref>, <ref loc="ECC 9:3">3</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 21:3">Ezek 21:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ũhoro no ũrĩa ũmwe; nĩkĩo ndĩroiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Aniinaga arĩa matarĩ ũcuuke o na akaniina arĩa aaganu.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ihũũra rĩarehe gĩkuũ kĩa narua,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩathekagĩrĩra kũũrwo nĩ hinya kwa arĩa matarĩ na mahĩtia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 10:3">Ayub 10:3</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 73:12">Thab 73:12</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa bũrũri wagĩa moko-inĩ ma andũ aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩahingaga aciirithania maitho.</para>
  <para style="q2">Akorwo ti we-rĩ, nũũ wĩkaga ũguo?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 7:6">Ayub 7:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 18:2">Isa 18:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Matukũ makwa marahanyũka gũkĩra mũkinyia-ũhoro;</para>
  <para style="q2">mombũkaga matarĩ na gĩkeno o na kĩnini.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 46:3">Thab 46:3</ref>; <ref loc="HAB 1:8">Hab 1:8</ref></char>
    </note>Mahĩtũkaga na ihenya mũno ta tũtarũ twa irura,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Tũtarũ tũtaarĩ tũnene twa ithanjĩ twathondekagĩrwo Misiri.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">kana ta nderi igũcuuhũkĩra kĩndũ gĩa kũrĩa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Ingiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩngũriganĩrwo nĩ mateta makwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngũtiga gũtukia gĩthiithi, ngene,’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 34:7">Thaam 34:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>no ngeetigĩra mĩnyamaro yakwa yothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo nĩnjũũĩ ndũkandua atĩ ndiĩhĩtie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Kuona atĩ nĩndĩkĩtie gũtuuo mũhĩtia-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ kĩĩ gĩgũtũma ndĩĩnogie tũhũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 3:2">Mal 3:2</ref>; <ref loc="JER 2:22">Jer 2:22</ref></char>
    </note>O na ingĩĩthamba na thabuni,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndĩĩthambe moko na igata-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>no ũndikirie irima rĩa gĩcoro</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha o na nguo ciakwa iithũũre.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 9:20">Arom 9:20</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 6:10">Koh 6:10</ref></char>
    </note>“We ti mũndũ ta niĩ atĩ nĩguo ndĩmũcookerie,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo tũngʼethanĩre igooti-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:25">1Sam 2:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naarĩ korwo nĩ harĩ mũndũ ũngĩtũiguithania,</para>
  <para style="q2">atũigĩrĩre guoko gwake ithuĩ eerĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 39:10">Thab 39:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>mũndũ wa kũnjehereria rũthanju rwa Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha ndigacooke kũmakio nĩ itebeebania rĩake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩingĩacooka kwaragia itekũmwĩtigĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ũrĩa ndariĩ rĩu-rĩ, ndingĩhota.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 19:4">1Ath 19:4</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:11">Ayub 7:11</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩthũire gũtũũra muoyo ũyũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndikũhingĩrĩria mateta makwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na nĩ ngwaria nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa ngoro yakwa ĩrĩ na marũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 3:13">Isa 3:13</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:33">Arom 8:33</ref></char>
    </note>Ngwĩra Ngai atĩrĩ: Tiga kũndua mwĩhia,</para>
  <para style="q2">no nyonia kĩrĩa ũrandũithĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Kaĩ ũkenagio nĩ kũũhinyĩrĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũgathũũra wĩra wa moko maku,</para>
  <para style="q2">o rĩrĩa ũrakenera mathugunda ma andũ arĩa aaganu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 16:7">1Sam 16:7</ref>; <ref loc="JER 11:20-23">Jer 11:20-23</ref></char>
    </note>Kaĩ maitho maku marĩ o ta maitho ma andũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ muonere waku ũhaana o ta wa mũndũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 39:5">Thab 39:5</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 3:8">2Pet 3:8</ref></char>
    </note>Kaĩ matukũ maku maigana ta ma andũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana mĩaka yaku ĩkaigana o ta ya mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>nĩguo ũcarĩrĩrie mahĩtia makwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ũtuĩragie mehia makwa,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>o na gũtuĩka wee nĩũũĩ atĩ ndiĩhĩtie,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkamenya atĩ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũũhonokia moko-inĩ maku?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 14:14">2Sam 14:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Moko maku nĩmo maathondekire na makĩnyũmba.</para>
  <para style="q2">Rĩu nĩũgũkĩgarũrũka ũnyanange?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ririkana atĩ wanyũũmbire ta rĩũmba.</para>
  <para style="q2">Rĩu ũgũcooka ũndue rũkũngũ rĩngĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Githĩ ndwanjitire ta iria,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũgĩcooka ũkĩĩmatia ta maguta marĩo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 139:13">Thab 139:13</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 139:15">15</ref></char>
    </note>ũkĩĩhumbĩra na nyama na gĩkonde,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkĩohania mahĩndĩ na mĩkiha yakwa hamwe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 2:25">1Pet 2:25</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩwaaheire muoyo o na ũkĩnyonia ũtugi waku;</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũmenyereri waku nĩguo ũtũirie roho wakwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“No nĩwahithire maũndũ maya ngoro-inĩ yaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩnjũũĩ no warĩ na ũndũ ũyũ meciiria-inĩ maku:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 34:7">Thaam 34:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ingĩehirie wee nĩwanyonaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndũngĩagire kũũherithia nĩ ũndũ wa wĩhia wakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Kaĩ akorwo nĩnjĩhĩtie ndĩ na haaro-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">O na ingĩiguĩka ndiĩkĩte ũũru, ndingĩhota gũtiira mũtwe wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩgũkorwo njiyũrĩtwo nĩ thoni,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngarikĩra mathĩĩna-inĩ makwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 17:34">1Sam 17:34</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 28:21">Isa 28:21</ref></char>
    </note>Ingĩtiira mũtwe wakwa-rĩ, wee ũnjeemaga o ta mũrũũthi,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ningĩ ũkonania ũhoti waku mũnene wa kũnjũkĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 21:10">1Ath 21:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩũndeheire aira angĩ manjũkĩrĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩwongereire marakara maku igũrũ rĩakwa;</para>
  <para style="q1">mbũtũ ciaku ikanjũkĩrĩra o ta makũmbĩ ma maaĩ marũmanĩrĩire.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:9">Thab 22:9</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 4:2">Koh 4:2</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 7:1">7:1</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ kĩĩ gĩatũmire ũndute nda ya maitũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Naarĩ korwo ndakuire itoneetwo nĩ maitho ma mũndũ o na ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Naarĩ korwo ndiaciarirwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana korwo ndaciarirwo njerekeirio mbĩrĩra!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 6:12">Koh 6:12</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:16">Ayub 7:16</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ matukũ makwa o na marĩ manini matikirie gũthira?</para>
  <para style="q2">Tigana na niĩ nĩguo ngĩe na gĩkeno gwa kahinda kanini,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 12:23">2Sam 12:23</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 12:5">Koh 12:5</ref></char>
    </note>kamũira thiĩte kũrĩa mũndũ athiiaga na ndacooke,</para>
  <para style="q2">bũrũri wa nduma, o nduma nene ya gĩkuũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>o bũrũri ũrĩa ũtukũ wakuo ũrĩ mũtumanu mũno,</para>
  <para style="q2">bũrũri wa nduma ya gĩkuũ, na ũtarĩ kĩhaarĩro,</para>
  <para style="q2">kũrĩa o na ũtheri ũhaana o ta nduma.”</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Zofaru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Zofaru ũrĩa Mũnaamathi agĩcookia, akĩũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 41:6">Kĩam 41:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ciugo icio ciothe-rĩ, nĩcikwaga gũcookio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mwaria ũyũ-rĩ, nĩegũgĩtuuo mwagĩrĩru?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 4:29">Aef 4:29</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 1:1">Thab 1:1</ref></char>
    </note>Mwĩraho ũcio waku-rĩ, nĩguo ũgũkiria andũ naguo?</para>
  <para style="q2">No kwage mũndũ ũngĩgũkaania rĩrĩa ũranyũrũrania?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Wee ũreera Ngai atĩrĩ, ‘Wĩtĩkio wakwa ndũrĩ ũcuuke,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na niĩ ndĩ mũtheru maitho-inĩ maku.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 20:19">Thaam 20:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naarĩ korwo Ngai no aarie,</para>
  <para style="q2">atumũre mĩromo yake agũũkĩrĩre,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:4">Ayub 9:4</ref>; <ref loc="EZR 9:13">Ezar 9:13</ref></char>
    </note>na akũguũrĩrie hitho cia ũũgĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũũgĩ ũrĩa wa ma nĩ wa mĩena ĩĩrĩ.</para>
  <para style="q2">Menya ũndũ ũyũ; atĩ Ngai ndakũherithĩtie kũringana na ũrĩa mehia maku maigana.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 3:11">Koh 3:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wee no ũhote kũmenya maũndũ marĩa mahithe ma Ngai?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kana no ũhote gũtuĩria kũna maũndũ ma Mwene-Hinya-Wothe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:18">Aef 3:18</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 55:9">Isa 55:9</ref></char>
    </note>Maũndũ make nĩmatũũgĩru gũkĩra igũrũ, wee nĩ atĩa ũngĩka?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ mariku gũkĩra ũriku wa mbĩrĩra, wee nĩ atĩa ũngĩmenya?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:19-20">Aef 3:19-20</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 22:12">Ayub 22:12</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 35:5">35:5</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩthimo kĩamo nĩ kĩraihu gũkĩra thĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ kĩaramu gũkĩra iria rĩrĩa inene.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:12">Ayub 9:12</ref>; <ref loc="REV 3:7">Kũg 3:7</ref></char>
    </note>“Angĩũka agũikie njeera-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">acooke etane ciira-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩmũgiria?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:14">Thab 10:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ nĩoĩ andũ arĩa maheenanagia;</para>
  <para style="q2">na rĩrĩa oona ũndũ mũũru-rĩ, githĩ ndaũmenyaga?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 16:12">Kĩam 16:12</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 6:36">2Maũ 6:36</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, mũndũ ũtarĩ ũũgĩ ndangĩtuĩka mũũgĩ o na rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa njaũ ya ndigiri ya gĩthaka ĩtarĩ hĩndĩ ĩngĩciarwo ĩrĩ mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 7:3">1Sam 7:3</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 9:29">Thaam 9:29</ref></char>
    </note>“No rĩrĩ, ũngĩneana ngoro yaku kũrĩ Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũtambũrũkie moko maku kũrĩ we,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:23">Ayub 22:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>ũngĩeheria mehia marĩa marĩ guoko-inĩ gwaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũgirie ũũru ũikare thĩinĩ wa hema yaku-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>hĩndĩ ĩyo no ũhote gũtiira ũthiũ waku na igũrũ ũtegũconoka;</para>
  <para style="q2">no ũrũgame wega ũtarĩ na guoya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 7:5">Josh 7:5</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 21:7">Ezek 21:7</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ nĩũkariganĩrwo nĩ mathĩĩna maku,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmaririkanage o ta maaĩ marĩkĩtie gũtherera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 37:6">Thab 37:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 5:20">Isa 5:20</ref></char>
    </note>Mũtũũrĩre waku nĩũgacangarara gũkĩra mũthenya barigici,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo nduma ĩgaatuĩka o ta rũciinĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 3:5">Thab 3:5</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 26:6">Alaw 26:6</ref></char>
    </note>Ũgũtũũra ũrĩ na mwĩhoko tondũ ũrĩ na ũgitĩri,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũkehũgũraga harĩa ũrĩ, na ũkahurũka ũtarĩ na ũgwati.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩũgakomaga, gũtarĩ na mũndũ ũngĩtũma wĩtigĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao andũ aingĩ nĩmakeyendithagia harĩ we.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:65">Gũcook 28:65</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 2:14">Amos 2:14</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, maitho ma andũ arĩa aaganu nĩmakaaga kuona,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matikoona gwa kũũrĩra;</para>
  <para style="q1">naguo ũndũ ũrĩa meriragĩria ũgaatuĩka mũcaayo wa gĩkuũ.”</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:8">Ayub 15:8</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 17:10">17:10</ref></char>
    </note>“Hatirĩ nganja inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ andũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũũgĩ ũgaathiranĩra na inyuĩ rĩrĩa mũgaakua!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:2">Ayub 13:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 15:9">15:9</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, ndĩ na ũmenyo o ta inyuĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtirĩ oogĩ kũngĩra.</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũtooĩ maũndũ macio mothe?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 91:15">Thab 91:15</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 6:29">Ayub 6:29</ref></char>
    </note>“Nduĩkĩte mũndũ wa gũthekererwo nĩ arata akwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtuĩka nĩndakaĩire Ngai nake akĩnjigua:</para>
  <para style="q2">niĩ nduĩkĩte mũndũ wa gũthekererwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtuĩka ndĩ mũthingu na ndirĩ ũcuuke!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 123:4">Thab 123:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Andũ arĩa maikaraga megangarĩte manyũrũragia mũtino,</para>
  <para style="q2">makona ta ũndũ ũcio ũkoraga o andũ arĩa magũrũ mao matenderũkaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:24">Ayub 9:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hema cia atunyani nĩcio ciikaraga igaacĩire,</para>
  <para style="q2">na andũ arĩa marakaragia Mũrungu nĩo maikaraga na thayũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o acio makuuaga ngai yao na moko.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:26">Math 6:26</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:20">Arom 1:20</ref></char>
    </note>“No ta kĩũrie nyamũ, na nĩigũkũruta ũhoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũrie nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ, na nĩigũkwĩra;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>kana warĩrie thĩ, na nĩĩgũkũruta ũhoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũkĩarĩrie thamaki cia iria-inĩ, nacio nĩigũkũhe ũhoro.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩ irĩkũ cia icio ciothe itooĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ nĩ guoko kwa Jehova gwĩkĩte ũndũ ũyũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 5:23">Dan 5:23</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 17:28">Atũm 17:28</ref></char>
    </note>Mĩoyo ya ciũmbe ciothe ĩrĩ guoko-inĩ gwake,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na mĩhũmũ ya andũ othe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Githĩ gũtũ gũtithuuranagia ciugo</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa rũrĩmĩ rũcamaga irio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 4:2">1Ath 4:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 32:7">Ayub 32:7</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 32:9">9</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ ũũgĩ ndũkoragwo na andũ arĩa akũrũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Githĩ gũtũũra mũno gũtirehaga ũmenyo?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 21:30">Thim 21:30</ref>; <ref loc="JER 32:19">Jer 32:19</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 1:17">Dan 1:17</ref></char>
    </note>“Ũũgĩ na hinya nĩ cia Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q2">mataaro na ũmenyo nĩ ciake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 13:16">Gũcook 13:16</ref>; <ref loc="REV 3:7">Kũg 3:7</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩrĩa amomoraga gĩtingĩakwo rĩngĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũndũ ũrĩa aahingĩra njeera gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩmuohora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ahingagĩrĩria maaĩ, gũkaaga mbura;</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ aamarekereria makaananga bũrũri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 18:22">2Maũ 18:22</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:11">Arom 2:11</ref></char>
    </note>Hinya na ũtooria nĩ ciake;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũheenio na mũheenania eerĩ no ake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Aheani kĩrĩra amatongoragia matarĩ nguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agatua aciirithania irimũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 116:16">Thab 116:16</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 5:27">Isa 5:27</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩohoraga mĩnyororo ĩrĩa athamaki moohaga andũ nayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">akamooha mũcibi njohero.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nguo cia kuohera njohero ihumbĩre thoni no cio ngombo cietĩkĩrĩtio kwĩhumba.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:15">Gũcook 24:15</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 1:52">Luk 1:52</ref></char>
    </note>Athĩnjĩri-Ngai amatongoragia marutĩtwo nguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akangʼaũrania andũ arĩa mehaandire tene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩakiragia mĩromo ya aheani kĩrĩra arĩa meehoketwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao athuuri akamatunya ũhoro wa gũkũũrana maũndũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 34:12">Isa 34:12</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 3:15">Ayub 3:15</ref></char>
    </note>We nĩagagĩra arĩa atĩĩku bata,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa marĩ na hinya nĩamatunyaga indo ciao cia mbaara.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 4:5">1Akor 4:5</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 2:22">Dan 2:22</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩaguũragia maũndũ marĩa mariku ma nduma,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nduma nene ya gĩkuũ akamiumĩria ũtheri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 2:1">Thab 2:1</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 9:3">Isa 9:3</ref></char>
    </note>Anenehagia ndũrĩrĩ, agacooka agaciananga;</para>
  <para style="q2">aingĩhagia ndũrĩrĩ, agacooka agacihurunja.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nĩagaagagia meciiria ma atongoria a gũkũ thĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">akamaingata, morũũrage werũ-inĩ mũtheri ũtarĩ njĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:29">Gũcook 28:29</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 24:20">Isa 24:20</ref></char>
    </note>Mahambaataga nduma-inĩ kũrĩa gũtarĩ ũtheri;</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ atũmaga matũgũũge ta mũndũ mũrĩĩu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Atĩrĩrĩ, maitho makwa nĩmonete maũndũ macio mothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">matũ makwa nĩmamaiguĩte na magataũkĩrwo nĩmo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 12:3">Ayub 12:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũrĩa mũũĩ o na niĩ nĩnjũũĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtirĩ oogĩ kũngĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>No niĩ ndĩrenda kwaria na Mwene-Hinya-Wothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngerirĩria gũciira na Mũrungu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 119:69">Thab 119:69</ref>; <ref loc="JER 8:22">Jer 8:22</ref></char>
    </note>No inyuĩ-rĩ, mũranjigĩrĩra ndeto cia maheeni;</para>
  <para style="q2">inyuothe mũrĩ athondekani a tũhũ!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 17:28">Thim 17:28</ref>; <ref loc="JDG 18:19">Atiir 18:19</ref></char>
    </note>Naarĩ korwo mwakira ki!</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũndũ ũcio ũngĩtuĩka ũũgĩ harĩ inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, thikĩrĩriai kĩhooto gĩakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">iguai gũthaithana kwa mĩromo yakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Kaĩ mũngĩaria ũũru mũkĩarĩrĩria Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ mũngĩaria maheeni igũrũ rĩake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:15">Alaw 19:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kaĩ mũngĩmuonia kĩmenyano?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ mũgũciirĩrĩra Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Angĩmũtuĩria inyuĩ-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio no ũtuĩke mwega?</para>
  <para style="q2">No mũmũheenie ta ũrĩa mũngĩheenia mũndũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 19:7">2Maũ 19:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ no amũrũithie</para>
  <para style="q2">mũngĩtuĩka a kuonania kĩmenyano na hitho.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 31:23">Ayub 31:23</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 3:6">Thaam 3:6</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩ, riiri wake ndũngĩmũmakia?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũtingĩnyiitwo nĩ guoya nĩ ũndũ wake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NEH 4:2-3">Neh 4:2-3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mĩario yanyu ya ũũgĩ nĩ thimo hũthũ o ta mũhu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ihooto cianyu no ta kwĩgitĩra na rĩũmba.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Kirai ki, mũreke njarie;</para>
  <para style="q2">o ũrĩa ndĩrĩona-rĩ, rekei nyone.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩ kĩĩ gĩgũtũma ndĩtoonyie ũgwati-inĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngaiga muoyo wakwa moko-inĩ makwa?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 23:4">Thab 23:4</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 14:32">Thim 14:32</ref></char>
    </note>O na angĩnjũraga-rĩ, niĩ nowe ndĩrĩĩhokaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">na ti-itherũ nĩ ngatetera mĩthiĩre yakwa hau mbere yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 30:5">Thab 30:5</ref>; <ref loc="JDG 1:19">Atiir 1:19</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:8">Kĩam 3:8</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ, ũndũ ũyũ noguo ũgaatuĩka wa kũũhonokia,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo mũndũ ũtooĩ Ngai ndangĩũmĩrĩria gũũka mbere yake!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Thikĩrĩriai wega ũhoro wakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">matũ manyu nĩmakĩigue ũrĩa nguuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 23:4">Ayub 23:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ nĩhaarĩirie ciira wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩnjũũĩ nĩ nguoneka ndĩ wa kĩhooto.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũũthitanga?</para>
  <para style="q2">Angĩkorwo nĩ kũrĩ-rĩ, no gũkira ngũkira ngue.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>“Wee Ngai, ta kĩĩhe o maũndũ maya meerĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndigũcooka gũkwĩhitha:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 9:3">Thaam 9:3</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:31">Ahib 10:31</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩ, eheria guoko gwaku, gũikare kũraya na niĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũtige kũũmakia na imakania ciaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 14:15">Ayub 14:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ ũnjĩte na nĩngwĩtĩka,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũkĩreke njarie, nawe ũnjookerie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 26:18">1Sam 26:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ mahĩtia na mehia maigana niĩ njĩkĩte?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nyonia ihĩtia na rĩĩhia rĩakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Ũraahitha ũthiũ waku nĩkĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkandua thũ yaku?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 26:36">Alaw 26:36</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 13:3">Hos 13:3</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩũngĩnyamaria ithangũ rĩrahurutwo nĩ rũhuho?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩũgũtengʼerania na maragara momũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 25:7">Thab 25:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩ wandĩkĩte maũndũ marũrũ ma kũnjũkĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkaangaĩra igai rĩa mehia ma ũnini wakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 33:11">Ayub 33:11</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 16:24">Atũm 16:24</ref></char>
    </note>Wohaga magũrũ makwa na mĩnyororo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrangagĩra njĩra ciakwa ciothe</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndũ wa gũcora njoro makinya ma magũrũ makwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 2:21">Mar 2:21</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:2">Jak 5:2</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũndũ amocaga ta kĩndũ kĩbuthĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">agathira ta nguo ĩrĩĩtwo nĩ memenyi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Mũndũ ũciarĩtwo nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">aikaraga o matukũ manini, namo makaiyũrwo nĩ mathĩĩna.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 103:15">Thab 103:15</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 40:6-8">Isa 40:6-8</ref></char>
    </note>Akũraga ta ihũa na agacooka akooma;</para>
  <para style="q2">ahĩtũkaga na ihenya ta kĩĩruru, na ndatũũraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 8:4">Thab 8:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũndũ ta ũcio wakĩmũkũũrĩra maitho?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũndũ ta ũcio wamũrehe mbere yaku aciirithio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 2:1-3">Atũm 2:1-3</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 9:30">Ayub 9:30</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ ũngĩhota kũruta kĩndũ gĩtheru kuuma harĩ kĩndũ kĩrĩa gĩtarĩ gĩtheru?</para>
  <para style="q2">Gũtirĩ o na ũmwe!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 17:26">Atũm 17:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Matukũ ma mũndũ nĩ matare;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩũtuĩte mũigana wa mĩeri yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩũmũigĩire mĩhaka ĩrĩa ataangĩkĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio tiga kũmũrora, tigana nake,</para>
  <para style="q2">nginya arĩĩkie mĩthenya yake ta mũthũkũmi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:1">Isa 11:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũtĩ-rĩ, nĩwĩrĩgagĩrĩrwo atĩ ũngĩtemwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ũthethũke rĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atĩ mathethũka maguo matikaaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>O na mĩri yaguo ĩngĩkũrĩra thĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na gĩthukĩ kĩaguo kĩũmĩre tĩĩri-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 17:8">Jer 17:8</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 10:1">Zek 10:1</ref></char>
    </note>ũngĩkaguucia maaĩ-rĩ, nĩũgathethũka</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũrute honge ta mũtĩ wa kũhaandwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>No mũndũ akuuaga agathikwo;</para>
  <para style="q2">aatuĩkana-rĩ, ndacookaga kuonwo rĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 14:14">2Sam 14:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O ta ũrĩa maaĩ mahũũaga kũu iria-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ta ũrĩa mũtaro wa rũũĩ ũngʼaraga ũkooma-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 21:1">Kũg 21:1</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:21">Atũm 3:21</ref></char>
    </note>ũguo noguo mũndũ akomaga na ndacookaga gũũkĩra rĩngĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">o nginya rĩrĩa igũrũ rĩgaathira-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ matirĩ hĩndĩ magookĩra kana maarahũrwo mookĩre.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Naarĩ korwo wahitha thĩinĩ wa mbĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũnjige hitho-inĩ nginya rĩrĩa marakara maku magaathira!</para>
  <para style="q1">Naarĩ korwo wanduĩra gĩathĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũgaacooka kũndirikana hĩndĩ ĩyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Mũndũ akua-rĩ, nĩagatũũra muoyo rĩngĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Matukũ makwa mothe ma wĩra mũritũ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngweterera ihinda rĩakwa rĩa kwerũhĩrio hinya rĩkinye.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:22">Ayub 13:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee ũgetana, na niĩ nĩngagwĩtĩka;</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩũkeerirĩria kĩũmbe gĩkĩ wombire na moko maku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩũgatara makinya makwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ndũkarũmbũiya mehia makwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 32:10">Jer 32:10</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 32:34">Gũcook 32:34</ref></char>
    </note>Mahĩtia makwa meekĩrĩtwo mondo-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩkoohwo na ĩkahũũrwo mũhũũri; nĩũkahumbĩra mehia makwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 38:20">Ezek 38:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“No rĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa kĩrĩma kĩenjekaga na gĩkamomoka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na o ta ũrĩa rwaro rwa ihiga rũeheragio handũ ha ruo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>na o ta ũrĩa maaĩ mamuthũraga mahiga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na o ta ũrĩa mbura nene ĩtwaraga tĩĩri-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũguo noguo wanangaga kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩa mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 4:20">Ayub 4:20</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:10">Jak 1:10</ref></char>
    </note>Wee ũmũtooragia o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, nake agathira;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũgarũraga gĩthiithi gĩake ũrĩa kĩhaana, na ũkamũingata.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Ariũ ake mangĩheo gĩtĩĩo, ndangĩmenya ũhoro ũcio;</para>
  <para style="q2">mangĩconorithio, we ndoonaga ũndũ ũcio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 38:7">Thab 38:7</ref>; <ref loc="JER 4:19">Jer 4:19</ref></char>
    </note>We no ruo rwa mwĩrĩ wake aiguaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake atũũraga o ecaayagĩra.”</para>
  <chapter number="15" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Elifazu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani akĩũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 41:6">Kĩam 41:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũndũ mũũgĩ no acookie ũhoro na kwĩgereria,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana aiyũrie nda yake na rũhuho ruumĩte na irathĩro?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NEH 4:2-3">Neh 4:2-3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No eciirĩrĩre na ciugo cia tũhũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana na mĩario ĩtarĩ bata?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>No wee-rĩ, nĩũracambia ũhoro wa gwĩtigĩra Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkagirĩrĩria ũhoro wa andũ kwĩrutĩra Mũrungu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 11:6">Ayub 11:6</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 16:23">Thim 16:23</ref></char>
    </note>Mehia maku nĩmo mataaraga kanua gaku;</para>
  <para style="q2">nawe ũthuurĩte kwaria na rũrĩmĩ rwa mũndũ mwara.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:2">Thab 10:2</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 19:22">Luk 19:22</ref></char>
    </note>Kanua gaku wee mwene nĩko karagũtuĩra ciira, ti gakwa:</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩromo yaku wee mwene ĩkaaria ũira wa gũgũũkĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 90:2">Thab 90:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wee nĩwe mũndũ wa mbere gũciarwo?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee-rĩ, waciarirwo mbere ya irĩma igĩe ho?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 11:34">Arom 11:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee nĩũthikagĩrĩria ndundu ya Ngai?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee wiki-rĩ, nowe ũrigĩtie na ũũgĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩ atĩa ũũĩ ithuĩ tũtooĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ ũmenyo ũrĩkũ ũrĩ naguo ithuĩ tũtarĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 10:6">2Maũ 10:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tũrĩ na athuuri marĩ na mbuĩ na arĩa akũrũ mũno,</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ akũrũ o na gũkĩra thoguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 37:35">Kĩam 37:35</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 1:13">Zek 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="JER 15:16">Jer 15:16</ref></char>
    </note>Ndũiganĩtwo nĩ ũhoorerania wa Mũrungu,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ũhoro ũcio warĩirio na ũhooreri?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ngoro yaku ĩgũteete nĩkĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ kĩĩ kĩratũma ũikare ũkiunaga maitho,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 29:11">Thim 29:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nĩguo werekerie marakara maku kũrĩ Mũrungu,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ũgaitũrũra ciugo ta icio kuuma kanua gaku?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>“Mũndũ akĩrĩ kĩ, atĩ no ahote gũtuĩka mũtheru,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na mũndũ ũciarĩtwo nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja nake akĩrĩ kĩĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ no ahote gũtuĩka mũthingu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo Ngai ndangĩhota kwĩhoka andũ arĩa ake aamũre-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kũngĩkorwo o na igũrũ ti gũtheru maitho-inĩ make-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 5:2">Alaw 5:2</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 19:28">Thim 19:28</ref></char>
    </note>mũndũ akĩrĩ kĩ atĩ amwĩhoke?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũndũ nĩ mwaganu na nĩ kĩmaramari, anyuuaga waganu ta maaĩ!</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>“Wee ta thikĩrĩria na nĩngũgũtaarĩria;</para>
  <para style="q2">reke ngwĩre ũrĩa nyonete,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:7">Gũcook 32:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>ngwĩre ũrĩa andũ arĩa oogĩ moigĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">matekũhitha ũndũ o na ũmwe wa ũhoro ũrĩa maaheirwo nĩ maithe mao,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 12:1">Kĩam 12:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>(o acio oiki maaheetwo bũrũri</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩrĩa gũtaarĩ mũndũ wa kũngĩ watuĩkanagia gatagatĩ-inĩ kao):</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Atĩrĩ, mũndũ mwaganu akoragwo na mĩnyamaro matukũ make mothe.</para>
  <para style="q2">Matukũ mothe ma ũcio ũtarĩ tha-rĩ, maigĩirwo o mĩnyamaro.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 6:25">Jer 6:25</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 5:3">1Athe 5:3</ref></char>
    </note>Aiguaga o mĩgambo ya kũmakania mũno;</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maũndũ mothe moneka ta marĩ mega-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">atunyani makamũtharĩkĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ndarĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro gĩa gwĩthara kuuma nduma-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">etereirio kũũragwo na rũhiũ rwa njora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 109:10">Thab 109:10</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:37">Luk 17:37</ref></char>
    </note>Orũũraga agĩcaragia irio, oragie atĩrĩ, ‘Irĩ na kũ?’</para>
  <para style="q2">Aikaraga amenyete atĩ mũthenya wa nduma ũrĩ o hakuhĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Mĩnyamaro na ruo rwa ngoro nĩcio imũmakagia;</para>
  <para style="q2">imũtooragia taarĩ mũthamaki wĩhaarĩirie kũmũtharĩkĩra,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 36:9">Ayub 36:9</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 3:16">Isa 3:16</ref></char>
    </note>nĩ ũndũ ainainagĩria Mũrungu ngundi,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akangʼathĩria Mwene-Hinya-Wothe,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 44:16">Jer 44:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>akamũguthũkĩra angʼathĩtie,</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩ na ngo yake mata ya hinya.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 3:17">Atiir 3:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“O na gũtuĩka ũthiũ wake nĩ mũnoru,</para>
  <para style="q2">na njohero yake ĩkaneneha nĩ kũnora-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>agaatũũraga matũũra maanangĩku,</para>
  <para style="q2">na aikarage nyũmba itatũũragwo nĩ mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nyũmba itigairie o kũmomoka ituĩke ihumbu cia mahiga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Ndagacooka gũkorwo arĩ mũtongu, naguo ũtonga wake ndũgatũũra,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana indo ciake itheereme kũu bũrũri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Ndakahota kũũrĩra nduma;</para>
  <para style="q2">rũrĩrĩmbĩ nĩrũkahoohia thuuna ciake,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩhũmũ ya kanua ka Ngai nĩĩkamweheria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 59:7">Isa 59:7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 6:19">Math 6:19</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 3:4">Mik 3:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩatige kwĩheenia na ũndũ wa kwĩhoka maũndũ ma tũhũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo gũtirĩ kĩndũ makaamũrehere.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Ihinda rĩake rĩtanakinya-rĩ, nĩakarĩhio mũigana wake wothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na honge ciake itikarura.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HAB 3:17">Hab 3:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Agaatuĩka ta mũthabibũ ũhũrũrĩtwo thabibũ ciaguo itarĩ njĩru,</para>
  <para style="q2">ahaane ta mũtamaiyũ ũraita kĩro kĩaguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:27">Ahib 10:27</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 23:8">Thaam 23:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo andũ a thiritũ ya arĩa matooĩ Ngai matũũraga marĩ thaata,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mwaki nĩũgaacina hema cia arĩa mendete mahaki.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Magĩaga nda cia mathĩĩna, na magaciara waganu;</para>
  <para style="q2">nda ciao ithugundaga o maheeni.”</para>
  <chapter number="16" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:20">Thab 69:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩnjiguĩte maũndũ maingĩ ta macio;</para>
  <para style="q2">inyuothe mũrĩ ahoorerania a kũnyamarania!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Mĩario ĩyo yanyu mĩingĩ ya mũhũhũtĩko-rĩ, ndĩrĩĩthira?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ kĩĩ kĩramũthĩĩnia, gĩgatũma mũtinde mũgĩkararania?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 19:21">2Ath 19:21</ref>; <ref loc="JER 48:27">Jer 48:27</ref></char>
    </note>O na niĩ no njarie ta inyuĩ, korwo nĩ inyuĩ mũrĩ harĩa ndĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">niĩ no njarie mĩario mĩega ya kũmũciirithia na ndĩmũinainĩrie mũtwe.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">16:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Kũinainĩria mũndũ mũtwe kuonanagia kũnyarara mũndũ ũcio, na kũu kwarĩ kũmũruma.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 37:35">Kĩam 37:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, kanua gakwa no kamũũmĩrĩrie;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũhoorerania uumĩte mĩromo-inĩ yakwa no ũmũhoorerie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>“No o na ndaaria-rĩ, ruo rwakwa rũtirathira;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ndegirĩrĩria kwaria-rĩ, rũtiranjeherera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 8:5">Atiir 8:5</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:3">Ayub 7:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ, Wee Ngai nĩũũnogeetie;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩũharaganĩtie nyũmba yakwa yothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 19:20">Ayub 19:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee nĩũnjoheete, naguo ũndũ ũcio ũgatuĩka ũira;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũhĩnju ũyũ ndĩ naguo nĩwambararĩte ũkaanyumbũra ũrĩa ndariĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 35:16">Thab 35:16</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 13:24">Ayub 13:24</ref></char>
    </note>Ngai nĩandooretie na akandembũranga nĩ ũrĩa arakarĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">akaahagaranĩria magego;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũcio thũ yakwa nĩangũũrĩire maitho.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:13">Thab 22:13</ref>; <ref loc="LAM 3:30">Maca 3:30</ref></char>
    </note>Andũ nĩmathamĩtie tũnua twao maathekerere;</para>
  <para style="q2">mangũthaga rũthĩa makĩĩnyũrũragia,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makanyiitana hamwe manjũkĩrĩre.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Mũrungu nĩandekereirie kũrĩ andũ arĩa ooru,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akanjikia mĩtego-inĩ ya arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:17">Ayub 9:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Niĩ ndaikarĩte wega, nowe agĩĩthethera;</para>
  <para style="q2">aanyiitire mũmero, akĩĩhehenja.</para>
  <para style="q1">We anduĩte cabaa wake wa kũrathagwo;</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>aikia a mĩguĩ ake nĩmandigiicĩirie.</para>
  <para style="q1">Aratheeca higo ciakwa atarĩ na tha,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agaita maaĩ makwa ma nyongo thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Aatharĩkagĩra maita maingĩ maingĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">anguthũkagĩra ta njamba ya ita.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 37:34">Kĩam 37:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ndumĩire gĩkonde gĩakwa kĩa mwĩrĩ nguo ya ikũnia,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngahitha thiithi wakwa rũkũngũ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Ũthiũ wakwa nĩũtunĩhĩte nĩkũrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">nduma nene ĩgakĩhumbĩra maitho makwa;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 55:7">Isa 55:7</ref>; <ref loc="ZEP 3:13">Zef 3:13</ref></char>
    </note>no rĩrĩ, moko makwa matirĩ ũndũ wa ũhinya mekĩte</para>
  <para style="q2">namo mahooya makwa nĩ matheru.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 4:10">Kĩam 4:10</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 66:18-19">Thab 66:18-19</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee thĩ-rĩ, ndũkahumbĩre thakame yakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩrĩro gĩakwa kĩroaga gũkaahuurũkio!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:9">Arom 1:9</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 11:10">Mar 11:10</ref></char>
    </note>O na rĩu-rĩ, mũira wakwa arĩ igũrũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũcio mũnjiirĩrĩri arĩ o igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Mũũthaithanĩrĩri nĩ mũrata wakwa</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa maitho makwa maraita maithori harĩ Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 8:45">1Ath 8:45</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 9:4">Thab 9:4</ref></char>
    </note>nĩathaithanagĩrĩra mũndũ kũrĩ Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa mũndũ athaithanagĩrĩra mũratawe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>“No mĩaka mĩnini ĩgũthira,</para>
  <para style="q2">thiĩ rũgendo rũrĩa mũndũ athiiaga na ndacooke.</para>
  <chapter number="17" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 38:12">Isa 38:12</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 88:3-4">Thab 88:3-4</ref></char>
    </note>Roho wakwa nĩmũthuthĩku,</para>
  <para style="q2">matukũ makwa nĩmathirĩte, mbĩrĩra nĩyo ĩnjetereire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 11:3">Ayub 11:3</ref>; <ref loc="JER 20:7">Jer 20:7</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ thiũrũrũkĩirio nĩ andũ a kũũnyũrũria;</para>
  <para style="q2">maitho makwa no nginya meerorere rũmena rwao.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 6:1">Thim 6:1</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 38:14">Isa 38:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee Ngai-rĩ, ta kĩĩhe kĩndũ gĩa kũrũgamĩrĩra thiirĩ wakwa kĩrĩa ũretia,</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩ ũngĩĩtĩkĩra kũruta kĩndũ gĩake kĩĩndũgamĩrĩre?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Wee nĩwaagithĩtie meciiria mao ũmenyo;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndũngĩmetĩkĩria mahootane.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:15">Thaam 22:15</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 11:20">Ayub 11:20</ref></char>
    </note>Mũndũ angĩkaana arata ake nĩ ũndũ wa kĩheo-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">maitho ma ciana ciake nĩmakoora.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 9:7">1Ath 9:7</ref>; <ref loc="JER 15:4">Jer 15:4</ref></char>
    </note>“Ngai nĩanduĩte mũndũ wa kuunwo thimo nĩ andũ othe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nduĩkĩte mũndũ wa gũtuagĩrwo mata ũthiũ nĩ andũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Maitho makwa nĩ maroora nĩ gwĩthikĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciĩga ciakwa ciothe ihũthĩte o ta kĩĩruru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 4:14">Thaam 4:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Andũ arĩa arũngĩrĩru nĩmagegetio nĩ ũhoro ũcio;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ arĩa matarĩ na ũũru mekĩte nĩmarahũkĩte mokĩrĩre andũ arĩa matooĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 4:18">Thim 4:18</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 2:4">1Sam 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>O na kũrĩ ũguo-rĩ, arĩa athingu nĩmarĩrũmagia njĩra ciao,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa marĩ moko matheru nĩmarĩongagĩrĩrwo hinya.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩ, ta gĩũkei inyuothe, geriai o rĩngĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Niĩ ndirĩ ndĩrona mũndũ mũũgĩ gatagatĩ kanyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 3:13">Ayub 3:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Matukũ makwa nĩ mathiru, mĩbango yakwa nĩmĩharaganie,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na merirĩria ma ngoro yakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Andũ aya magarũraga ũtukũ makaũtua mũthenya;</para>
  <para style="q2">nduma yamakinyĩrĩra moigaga atĩrĩ, ‘Ũtheri ũrĩ o hakuhĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 139:8">Thab 139:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Angĩkorwo mũciĩ ũrĩa njĩrĩgĩrĩire no mbĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">angĩkorwo ingĩara ũrĩrĩ wakwa o nduma-inĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>angĩkorwo no njĩĩre ũhoro wa kũbutha atĩrĩ, ‘Wee nĩwe baba,’</para>
  <para style="q2">na njĩĩre kĩgunyũ atĩrĩ, ‘Wee nĩwe maitũ’ kana ‘Nĩwe mwarĩ wa maitũ-rĩ’,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 31:22">Thab 31:22</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 37:11">Ezek 37:11</ref></char>
    </note>mwĩhoko wakwa ũkĩrĩ kũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũngĩnyonera mwĩhoko?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JON 2:6">Jon 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mwĩhoko nĩũharũrũkĩte nginya ihingo-inĩ cia gĩkuũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩtũgũgĩikũrũkania hamwe rũkũngũ-inĩ?”</para>
  <chapter number="18" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Bilidadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Bilidadi ũrĩa Mũshuhi agĩcookia, akĩũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Ũrĩĩtiga kwaria mĩario ĩno rĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Gĩa na ũũgĩ nĩguo o na ithuĩ tũhote kwaria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 73:22">Thab 73:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ kĩĩ kĩratũma ũtuone tũhaana ta ngʼombe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na tũgatuuo irimũ maitho-inĩ maku?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:14">Ayub 13:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee ũrehanyũrũra nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa ũrakarĩte-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">thĩ no ĩthaamwo nĩ ũndũ waku?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kana no nginya ndwaro cia mahiga cieherio harĩa itũire?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 13:9">Thim 13:9</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:8">Math 25:8</ref></char>
    </note>“Tawa wa mũndũ mwaganu nĩmũhorie;</para>
  <para style="q2">rũrĩrĩmbĩ rwa mwaki wake nĩrũtigĩte gwakana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ũtheri ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa hema yake ũtuĩkĩte nduma;</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo tawa ũrĩa ũrĩ hakuhĩ nake ũkahora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 5:13">Ayub 5:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hinya wa mũkinyũkĩrie wake nĩmũhũthie;</para>
  <para style="q2">namo mathugunda make makamũgũithia thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 9:15">Thab 9:15</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 7:2">Mik 7:2</ref></char>
    </note>Makinya make mamũikagia wabu-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake akoorũraga thĩinĩ wa marima mayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mũtego ũmũnyiitĩire ndiira-inĩ ya kũgũrũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtego ũgakĩmũrũmia biũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 5:20">Isa 5:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ahithĩirwo kĩana kĩa rũrigi tĩĩri-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">akaambĩrwo mũtego njĩra-inĩ yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 55:4">Thab 55:4</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 22:18">Isa 22:18</ref></char>
    </note>Imakania imuumagĩrĩra na mĩena yothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ikamũtengʼeragia harĩa hothe aagerera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Mũtino nĩũmũhũũtĩire;</para>
  <para style="q2">mwanangĩko wetereire agwe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 12:12">Ndar 12:12</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 14:12">Zek 14:12</ref></char>
    </note>Mũtino ũrĩĩaga icunjĩ cia gĩkonde gĩake;</para>
  <para style="q2">narĩo irigithathi rĩa gĩkuũ rĩgatambuuranga ciĩga ciake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Aguucĩtio, akarutwo ũgitĩri-inĩ wa hema yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agatwarwo kũrĩ mũthamaki wa imakania.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 19:24">Kĩam 19:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mwaki nĩguo ũtũũraga hema-inĩ yake;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũbiriti ũgwakana nĩũhurunjĩtwo gĩikaro gĩake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Mĩri yake yũmagĩra tĩĩri-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio honge ciake ikahooha na igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:26">Gũcook 32:26</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 10:7">Thim 10:7</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩririkano gĩake nĩ gĩgaathira thĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndarĩ rĩĩtwa bũrũri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Akaarutũrũrwo ũtheri-inĩ atwarwo nduma-inĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩakaingatwo oime thĩ ĩno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 22:30">Jer 22:30</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 14:22">Isa 14:22</ref></char>
    </note>Ndarĩ ciana kana njiaro thĩinĩ wa andũ ao,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ndarĩ mũndũ wake ũgaatigara kũrĩa aatũũraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Andũ a mwena wa ithũĩro nĩmakagegio nĩ maũndũ marĩa mamũkorete;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ a mwena wa irathĩro manyiitwo nĩ kĩmako.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 21:28">Ayub 21:28</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 4:5">1Ath 4:5</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ ũguo nĩguo gĩikaro kĩa mũndũ mwaganu gũkahaana;</para>
  <para style="q2">kũndũ kwa mũndũ ũrĩa ũtooĩ Mũrungu-rĩ, gwake kũhaana ũguo.”</para>
  <chapter number="19" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Ayubu akĩũria atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Mũkũũnyariira nginya-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũkĩĩhehenjaga na ciugo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 31:7">Kĩam 31:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 6:9">Ayub 6:9</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩu mũrĩ kũndetia maita ikũmi;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũũtharĩkĩire mũtarĩ na thoni.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo nĩ ma atĩ nĩhĩtĩtie njĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">ihĩtia rĩakwa rĩgũikara rĩrĩ thĩĩna wakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 35:26">Thab 35:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũngĩkorwo ti-itherũ nĩmũgwĩtũũgĩria igũrũ rĩakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mũgĩe na mweke wa kũnjũkĩrĩra nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo njonorithĩtio,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 18:8">Ayub 18:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>no kĩmenyei atĩ Ngai nĩwe ũũhĩtĩirie,</para>
  <para style="q2">akandigiicĩria na wabu wake.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:2">Thab 22:2</ref>; <ref loc="HAB 1:2-4">Hab 1:2-4</ref></char>
    </note>“O na gũtuĩka nĩngayaga ngoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Ndĩĩmũhĩtĩrie!’ Niĩ ndirĩ ũndũ njookagĩrio;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtuĩka nĩhooyaga ndeithio, gũtirĩ kĩhooto nyonaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LAM 3:7">Maca 3:7</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 6:4">Koh 6:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩahingĩire njĩra na niĩ ndingĩhota kũhĩtũka;</para>
  <para style="q2">tũcĩra twakwa nĩatwĩkĩrĩte nduma.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 43:28">Kĩam 43:28</ref>; <ref loc="LAM 5:16">Maca 5:16</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩanjaũrĩte gĩtĩĩo gĩakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akanduta thũmbĩ mũtwe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Andarũrangaga kuuma mbarĩ ciothe nginya ngathira;</para>
  <para style="q2">amunyaga mwĩhoko wakwa o ta mũtĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 16:9">Ayub 16:9</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 13:24">Ayub 13:24</ref></char>
    </note>Marakara make nĩmanjakanĩire;</para>
  <para style="q2">andaraga hamwe na thũ ciake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Mbũtũ ciake cia ita injerekagĩra na hinya;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciakaga ihumbu cia kũnjũkĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">igathiũrũrũkĩria hema yakwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:8">Thab 69:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩanyamũranĩtie na ariũ a baba makaahutatĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ arĩa tũyaine nao nĩmeĩndigithĩtie biũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 15:12">2Sam 15:12</ref>; <ref loc="JER 20:10">Jer 20:10</ref></char>
    </note>Andũ a mbarĩ ciitũ nĩmathiĩte makandiga;</para>
  <para style="q2">arata akwa nĩmariganĩirwo nĩ niĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 14:14">Kĩam 14:14</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 2:7">Koh 2:7</ref></char>
    </note>Ageni akwa na ndungata ciakwa cia andũ-a-nja matuaga ta matanjũũĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">maanyonaga ta ndĩ mũndũ uumĩte kũndũ kũngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Njĩtaga ndungata yakwa, no ndĩngĩnjĩtĩka,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ndĩmĩthaithĩte na kanua gakwa niĩ mwene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 38:5">Thab 38:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mĩhũmũ ya kanua gakwa nĩmĩnungu harĩ mũtumia wakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">nduĩkĩte wa kũmenwo harĩ ariũ a maitũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 2:23">2Ath 2:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O na tũhĩĩ tũrĩa tũnini nĩtũũnyararĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa ndatuumĩrĩra no gũũthekerera tũũthekagĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 55:12-13">Thab 55:12-13</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:18">Joh 13:18</ref></char>
    </note>Arata akwa arĩa manguhĩrĩirie othe nĩmathũire;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ arĩa nyendeete nĩmahutatĩire makaanjũkĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Niĩ thirĩte ngatigara o gĩkonde na mahĩndĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">niĩ ndigarĩirwo no kĩni kĩa magego giiki.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>“Njiguĩrai tha, inyuĩ arata akwa, iguai tha,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo guoko kwa Ngai nĩkũngũthĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:26">Thab 69:26</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 53:4">Isa 53:4</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthingatanaga na niĩ o ta ũrĩa Mũrungu aathingataga nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũtirĩ mũraiganwo nĩ nyama ciakwa?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 17:14">Thaam 17:14</ref>; <ref loc="JER 17:1">Jer 17:1</ref></char>
    </note>“Naarĩ korwo ciugo ciakwa nĩciandĩkĩtwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">igakĩandĩkwo ibuku-inĩ rĩa gĩkũnjo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>igakarwo na karamu ga kĩgera igũrũ rĩa ngocorai,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana igakururwo rwaro-inĩ rwa ihiga itũũre nginya tene!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 78:35">Thab 78:35</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 16:19">Ayub 16:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩnjũũĩ atĩ Mũngũũri arĩ muoyo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atĩ marigĩrĩrio-inĩ nĩwe ũkaarũgama thĩ ĩno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:8">Math 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 13:12">1Akor 13:12</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:2">1Joh 3:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nakĩo gĩkonde gĩkĩ gĩakwa kĩarĩkia gũthira,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mwĩrĩ ũyũ wa nyama ũkorwo ũtarĩ ho,</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩ ngoona Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>niĩ mwene nĩngamwĩonera na maitho,</para>
  <para style="q2">niĩ mwene, ti mũndũ ũngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ĩ ngoro yakwa ndĩkĩrĩ na wendo mũnene!</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“Mũngiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Ĩ nĩtũthingatane nake,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuona atĩ nĩwe kĩhumo gĩa thĩĩna ũyũ,’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:22">Ayub 15:22</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 3:17">Koh 3:17</ref></char>
    </note>inyuĩ ene nĩmwagĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩtigĩra rũhiũ rwa njora;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo mangʼũrĩ nĩmakarehithia kũherithanio na rũhiũ rwa njora,</para>
  <para style="q2">na hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩmũkamenya atĩ nĩ kũrĩ ũtuanĩri wa ciira.”</para>
  <chapter number="20" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Zofaru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Zofaru ũrĩa Mũnaamathi agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 42:5">Thab 42:5</ref>; <ref loc="LAM 1:20">Maca 1:20</ref></char>
    </note>“Meciiria makwa nĩ mathĩĩnĩku, na nĩkĩo ngũcookia,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ nĩndangĩkĩte mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ndĩraigua irũithia rĩa kũnjonorithia,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũmenyo wakwa nĩũranjĩkĩra hinya wa gũcookia.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 4:32">Gũcook 4:32</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ti-itherũ nĩũũĩ ũrĩa gũtũire kuuma tene</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa mũndũ aigirwo gũkũ thĩ ĩno,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 37:35-36">Thab 37:35-36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>atĩ kũrũũhia kwa arĩa aaganu no gwa kahinda,</para>
  <para style="q2">o nakĩo gĩkeno kĩa andũ arĩa matooĩ Ngai no gĩa kahinda kanini.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 11:4">Kĩam 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="OBA 1:3-4">Obad 1:3-4</ref></char>
    </note>O na gũtuĩka mwĩtĩĩo wake nĩ ũkinyaga o igũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo mũtwe wake ũkahutia matu-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 4:20">Ayub 4:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>agaathira nginya tene o ta mai make mwene;</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa manamuona mooragie atĩrĩ, ‘Kaĩ aathiire kũ?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 5:3">Koh 5:3</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 17:14">Isa 17:14</ref></char>
    </note>Airagĩria ta kĩroto, akaaga kuoneka rĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">akaingatwo ta kĩoneki kĩa ũtukũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Riitho rĩrĩa rĩamuonaga rĩtikamuona rĩngĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">harĩa aaikaraga hatikamuona rĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 5:4">Ayub 5:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ciana ciake ikaageragia kwĩiguithania na athĩĩni;</para>
  <para style="q2">moko make mwene no nginya magaacookia ũtonga wake kũrĩa aaũrutire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Hinya wa wĩthĩ ũrĩa ũiyũrĩte mahĩndĩ-inĩ make</para>
  <para style="q2">ũgaakoma hamwe nake rũkũngũ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:7">Thab 10:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“O na gũtuĩka ũũru ũrĩ mũrĩo ũrĩ kanua gake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩaũhithaga rungu rwa rũrĩmĩ rwake,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>o na gũtuĩka ndangĩhota kũũrekia</para>
  <para style="q2">na aũigaga kanua gake-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 20:17">Thim 20:17</ref>; <ref loc="REV 19:9">Kũg 19:9</ref></char>
    </note>irio ciake nĩikarũra irĩ nda yake;</para>
  <para style="q2">igaatuĩka ũrũrũ wa nduĩra thĩinĩ wake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 18:25">Alaw 18:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩagatahĩka ũtonga ũrĩa ameretie;</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũrungu nĩagatũma aũtahĩke.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩakoonga thumu wa nyoka;</para>
  <para style="q2">magego ma nyoka nĩmo makaamũũraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:13">Gũcook 32:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ndagakenera tũrũũĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">njũũĩ iria ithereraga ũũkĩ na ngorono.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Kĩndũ kĩrĩa anogeire no nginya agagĩcookia atakĩrĩte;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndagakenera uumithio wa wonjoria wake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nĩahinyĩrĩirie athĩĩni, akamatiga matarĩ na kĩndũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩatunyanĩte nyũmba iria ataakire.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 5:12">Koh 5:12</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:15">Luk 12:15</ref></char>
    </note>“Ti-itherũ merirĩria make matingĩthira;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndangĩĩhonokia na indo iria eigĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ kĩndũ atigĩirio gĩa kũrĩa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtonga wake ndũgatũũra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 2:15">Atiir 2:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aiganĩire nĩ ũndũ wa kũingĩhia indo, mĩnyamaro nĩĩkamũnyiita;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũkĩa nĩũkamũkora na nditi nene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LAM 4:11">Maca 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 88:15-16">Thab 88:15-16</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aiyũrĩtie nda yake-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo Ngai akaarekereria marakara make mahiũ mamũkore</para>
  <para style="q2">na amuurĩrie mahũũra make.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 24:18">Isa 24:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O na angĩũrĩra indo cia mbaara cia kĩgera,</para>
  <para style="q2">akaarathwo na mũguĩ wa gĩcango.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Aũcomoraga kuuma ngʼongʼo wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtheece ũcio mũkengu akaũcomora kuuma ini-inĩ rĩake.</para>
  <para style="q1">Imakania nĩikamũkorerera;</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 21:9">Thab 21:9</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 18:15">Ayub 18:15</ref></char>
    </note>nduma nene nĩyetereire igĩĩna ciake.</para>
  <para style="q1">Mwaki ũtarĩ mũhurutĩre nĩũkamũcina,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũniine kĩrĩa gĩtigaire thĩinĩ wa hema yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 31:28">Gũcook 31:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Igũrũ nĩrĩkaguũria wĩhia wake;</para>
  <para style="q2">thĩ nayo nĩĩkarahũka ĩmũũkĩrĩre.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:26-27">Math 7:26-27</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 5:18">Amos 5:18</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩguũ nĩgĩgathereria nyũmba yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">indo cia nyũmba yake ithererio nĩ kĩguũ mũthenya ũcio wa mangʼũrĩ ma Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Ũcio nĩguo ũndũ ũrĩa Ngai agayagĩra arĩa aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">igai rĩrĩa maathĩrĩirwo nĩ Mũrungu.”</para>
  <chapter number="21" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:17">Ayub 13:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Thikĩrĩriai wega ciugo ciakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">rekei ũndũ ũyũ ũtuĩke nĩguo mũkũũhooreria naguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ngirĩrĩriai na niĩ njarie,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndaarĩkia kwaria-rĩ, mũgĩcooke mũũnyũrũrie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>“Niĩ-rĩ, kaĩ mateta makwa meerekeirio mũndũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ngũkĩaga kũremwo nĩ gũkirĩrĩria nĩkĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 18:19">Atiir 18:19</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 45:3">Kĩam 45:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ta ndorai mũgege;</para>
  <para style="q2">mwĩnyiite tũnua twanyu na moko nĩ kũmaka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ndĩciiragia ũhoro ũyũ ngamaka mũno;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngethithimũkwo nĩ mwĩrĩ, ngambĩrĩria kũinaina.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 73:3">Thab 73:3</ref>; <ref loc="MAL 3:15">Mal 3:15</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩ, andũ arĩa aaganu marekagwo matũũre muoyo nĩkĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">magakũra o na magakĩrĩrĩria kũgĩa na ũhoti?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 17:14">Thab 17:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩmeonagĩra ciana ciao ikĩgaacĩra kũu marĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">makoona rũciaro rwao rũkĩĩhaanda mbere ya maitho mao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mĩciĩ yao ĩikaraga ĩgitĩirwo na ĩtarĩ na guoya;</para>
  <para style="q2">naruo rũthanju rwa Ngai rũtimahũũraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 23:26">Thaam 23:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ndegwa ciao itiagaga kũgwatia;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngʼombe ciao iciaraga, na itihunaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Moimagaragia twana twao tũingĩ o ta rũũru;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciana icio ciao ikaina igĩtũrũhaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nao o ene mainaga makĩhũũraga tũhembe na inanda cia mũgeeto;</para>
  <para style="q2">mekenagia na mũgambo wa mũtũrirũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:1-12">Thab 10:1-12</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 14:15">Isa 14:15</ref></char>
    </note>Matũũraga mĩaka yao magaacĩire,</para>
  <para style="q2">na magathiĩ mbĩrĩra-inĩ marĩ na thayũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:15">Gũcook 32:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na no-o meeraga Mũrungu atĩrĩ, ‘Thiĩ! Tigana na ithuĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Tũtikwenda kũmenya njĩra ciaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 34:9">Ayub 34:9</ref>; <ref loc="JER 9:6">Jer 9:6</ref></char>
    </note>Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩwe ũ, atĩ nĩguo tũmũtungatagĩre?</para>
  <para style="q2">Tũkũgunĩka nakĩ tũngĩmũhooya?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, kũgaacĩra kwao gũtirĩ moko-inĩ mao ene,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio niĩ njikaraga haraaya na kĩrĩra kĩa andũ arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 18:5">Ayub 18:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Na rĩrĩ, nĩ maita maigana tawa wa arĩa aaganu ũhoragio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ maita maigana makoragwo nĩ mũtino,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ maita maigana Ngai amagayagĩra ruo nĩ kũmarakarĩra?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩ maita maigana matuĩkaga ta nyeki nyũmũ ĩkũhurutwo nĩ rũhuho,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ta maragara marĩa mombũragwo nĩ kĩhuhũkanio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 20:5">Thaam 20:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 25:14">Jer 25:14</ref></char>
    </note>Kuugagwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ngai aigagĩra ciana iherithia rĩa ithe wao.’</para>
  <para style="q2">No rĩrĩ, nĩ kaba Ngai aherithie mũndũ ũcio we mwene,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo amenye nĩehĩtie!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 16:22">Ndar 16:22</ref>; <ref loc="JER 25:15">Jer 25:15</ref></char>
    </note>Maitho make nĩmeyonere mwanangĩko wake mwene;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩarekwo akunde mangʼũrĩ ma Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, anga no eetangaga ha ũhoro wa andũ ake</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa agaatiga na thuutha, matukũ make maathira?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 40:13-14">Isa 40:13-14</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 82:1">Thab 82:1</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũngĩhota kũruta Mũrungu atĩ nĩguo agĩe na ũmenyo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuona atĩ Mũrungu nĩwe ũtuanagĩra ciira, o na agatuĩra arĩa atũũgĩirie mũno?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 15:15">Kĩam 15:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ ũkuuaga arĩ na hinya wake wothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩ mũgitĩre wega biũ, na arĩ na thayũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>mwĩrĩ wake ũheetwo irio wega,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mahĩndĩ ma mĩthiimo yake marĩ o maigũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũngĩ agakua arĩ na marũrũ ma ngoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">atarĩ aakenera kĩndũ kĩega o na kĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 24:20">Ayub 24:20</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 9:2-3">Koh 9:2-3</ref></char>
    </note>Makomaga o ro ũndũ ũmwe tĩĩri-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na eerĩ-rĩ, igunyũ ikamahumbĩra.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>“Niĩ nĩnjũũĩ wega ũrĩa mũreciiria,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngamenya mathugunda manyu maakũhĩtĩria namo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Mũrooria atĩrĩ, ‘Rĩu nyũmba ya mũndũ ũrĩa mũnene ĩkĩrĩ ha,</para>
  <para style="q2">na hema ĩrĩa andũ aaganu maratũũraga-rĩ, ĩkĩrĩ ha?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Kaĩ mũtarĩ muoria andũ arĩa mathiiaga ngʼendo?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ mũtarũmbũyagia ũrĩa mamwĩraga:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 31:3">Ayub 31:3</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 2:9">2Pet 2:9</ref></char>
    </note>atĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwaganu nĩ aiguagĩrwo tha mũthenya wa mũtino,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ nĩahonokagio mũthenya wa mangʼũrĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nũũ ũreganaga na mĩtugo ya mũndũ mwaganu maitho-inĩ make?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũmũrĩhagia kũringana na maũndũ marĩa aaneka?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Atwaragwo mbĩrĩra-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mbĩrĩra yake ĩkarangagĩrwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 3:19">Ayub 3:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tĩĩri wa gĩtuamba nĩũrĩ mũrĩo harĩ we;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ othe nĩwe marũmagĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kĩrĩndĩ gĩtangĩtarĩka gĩgathiiaga mbere yake.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>“Mwakĩhota atĩa kũũhooreria na ndeto cia tũhũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Hatirĩ kĩndũ gĩtigaru harĩ macookio manyu tiga o maheeni!”</para>
  <chapter number="22" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Elifazu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 17:10">Luk 17:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũndũ aahota kũguna Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q2">O na mũndũ mũũgĩ-rĩ, akĩhota kũmũguna?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 1:11">Isa 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 9:12">Thim 9:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ gĩkeno kĩrĩkũ ũthingu waku ũngĩrehere Mwene-Hinya-Wothe?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ uumithio ũrĩkũ angĩgĩa naguo angĩkorwo mĩthiĩre yaku ndĩrĩ ũcuuke?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>“Arakũrũithia na agagũthitanga</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ wa wĩtigĩri Ngai waku?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Githĩ waganu waku ti mũnene?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mehia maku-rĩ, makĩrĩ mũthia?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:26">Thaam 22:26</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 24:12-13">Gũcook 24:12-13</ref></char>
    </note>Wetirie ũgitĩri kuuma kũrĩ ariũ a thoguo hatarĩ gĩtũmi;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩwaũrire andũ nguo, ũkĩmatiga njaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:42">Math 10:42</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 18:7">Ezek 18:7</ref></char>
    </note>Arĩa anogu ndwamaheire maaĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩwaimire arĩa ahũtu irio,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>o na gũtuĩka warĩ mũndũ ũrĩ hinya, ũrĩ na mĩgũnda:</para>
  <para style="q2">mũndũ ũheetwo gĩtĩĩo, na watũũraga kuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 24:3">Ayub 24:3</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 24:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 1:17">Isa 1:17</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩwaingatire atumia a ndigwa matarĩ na kĩndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkĩniina hinya wa arĩa matarĩ na maithe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩkĩo ũthiũrũrũkĩirio nĩ mĩtego,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩkĩo thĩĩna wa narua ũkũmakagia,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 5:14">Ayub 5:14</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 69:1-2">Thab 69:1-2</ref></char>
    </note>nĩkĩo ũtumanĩirwo nĩ nduma, ũkaremwo nĩkuona,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nokĩo mũiyũro wa maaĩ ũkũhubanĩirie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 11:8">Ayub 11:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Githĩ Ngai ndarĩ o kũu igũrũ o igũrũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">O na ta kĩone ũrĩa njata iria irĩ igũrũ mũno itũũgĩrĩte!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:11">Thab 10:11</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:12">Aef 6:12</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, wee ũroiga atĩrĩ, ‘Mũrungu nĩ atĩa angĩmenya?</para>
  <para style="q2">No atuanĩre ciira nduma-inĩ ta ĩno?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 97:2">Thab 97:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 40:22">Isa 40:22</ref></char>
    </note>Matu matumanu nĩmamũhumbĩrĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndangĩtuona rĩrĩa egũceera kũu igũrũ gacũmbĩrĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ũgũtũũra ũgeraga o njĩra ya tene</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩrĩa andũ aaganu managerera?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:32">Ayub 15:32</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 7:23">Kĩam 7:23</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩmahuririo ihinda rĩao rĩtanakinya,</para>
  <para style="q2">mĩthingi yao ĩgĩthererio nĩ mũiyũro wa maaĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nao meerire Mũrungu atĩrĩ, ‘Tigana na ithuĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Mwene-Hinya-Wothe-rĩ, angĩtwĩka atĩa?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, nĩwe waiyũririe nyũmba ciao na indo njega,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio niĩ njikaraga haraaya na kĩrĩra kĩa andũ arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 58:10">Thab 58:10</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 107:42">Thab 107:42</ref></char>
    </note>“Andũ arĩa athingu nĩmeyonagĩra mwanangĩko wa acio aaganu, magakena;</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa matarĩ na ũũru mekĩte mamanyũrũragia makiugaga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>‘Ti-itherũ thũ ciitũ nĩnyanange,</para>
  <para style="q2">mwaki nĩũcinĩte ũtonga wao.’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 26:3">Isa 26:3</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:6">1Pet 5:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Athĩkĩra Ngai ũikare ũrĩ na thayũ nake,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo ũgaakũrehere ũgaacĩru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ĩtĩkĩra ũrutani wa kanua gake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũige ciugo ciake ngoro-inĩ yaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 19:2">Isa 19:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 11:14">Ayub 11:14</ref></char>
    </note>Ũngĩcookerera ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩegũkwamũkĩra; ũngĩeheria waganu kũraya na hema yaku,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 19:10">Thab 19:10</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 58:14">Isa 58:14</ref></char>
    </note>na ũte ngũmba ciaku cia thahabu rũkũngũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na thahabu yaku ya Ofiri ũmĩte na kũu ndwaro-inĩ cia mahiga kũu mũkuru-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>hĩndĩ ĩyo ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe agaatuĩka thahabu yaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atuĩke betha ĩrĩa njega mũno harĩ we.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 27:10">Ayub 27:10</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 58:14">Isa 58:14</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ, hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩũkona gĩkeno thĩinĩ wa ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩũgatiirĩra Ngai ũthiũ waku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 86:7">Thab 86:7</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 30:2">Ndar 30:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩũkamũhooya, nake nĩagakũigua,</para>
  <para style="q2">nawe nĩũkahingia mĩĩhĩtwa yaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Ũrĩa watua wĩkwo nĩguo ũrĩkagwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũtheri nĩ ũkaara njĩra-inĩ ciaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">22:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 23:12">Math 23:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ angĩ manyiihio, nawe ũkoiga, ‘Nĩmatũũgĩrio!’</para>
  <para style="q2">Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩakahonokia arĩa makuĩte ngoro.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nĩakahonokia o na ũrĩa ũrĩ na ũcuuke,</para>
  <para style="q2">ahonokio nĩ ũndũ wa ũtheru wa moko maku.”</para>
  <chapter number="23" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:3">Ayub 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 21:7">Ezek 21:7</ref></char>
    </note>“O na ũmũthĩ gũteta gwakwa no kũrũrũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">guoko gwake nĩkũnditũhĩire o na ngĩcaayaga ũguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Naarĩ korwo nĩnjũũĩ kũrĩa ingĩmuona;</para>
  <para style="q2">Naarĩ korwo no hote gũthiĩ kũrĩa aikaraga!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ingĩĩyarĩrĩria harĩ we,</para>
  <para style="q2">njiyũrie kanua gakwa ihooto.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>No nyende kũmenya ũrĩa angĩĩnjookeria,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩcũũranie ũrĩa angĩnjĩĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:4">Ayub 9:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No anjũkĩrĩre na ũhoti wake mũnene?</para>
  <para style="q2">Aca, ndangĩhatĩrĩria na thitango.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 3:8">Kĩam 3:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hau-rĩ, mũndũ mũrũngĩrĩru no atware ciira wake mbere yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ njohorithio kuuma kũrĩ mũnjiirithia nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩ, ingĩthiĩ mwena wa irathĩro, we ndarĩ kuo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ingĩthiĩ mwena wa ithũĩro, ndiramuona.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa arĩ wĩra-inĩ mwena wa gathigathini, ndimuonaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa athiĩ mwena wa gũthini, ndimuonaga o na hanini.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 139:1-3">Thab 139:1-3</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:7">1Pet 1:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nowe-rĩ, nĩooĩ njĩra ĩrĩa ngeragĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">aarĩkia kũngeria, ngoima haana o ta thahabu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 44:18">Thab 44:18</ref>; <ref loc="JER 11:20">Jer 11:20</ref></char>
    </note>Magũrũ makwa moimĩte makinya make thuutha;</para>
  <para style="q2">nũmagĩrĩra njĩra yake itekwahũka na mwena.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:32">Joh 4:32</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 4:34">34</ref></char>
    </note>Niĩ nditiganĩirie maathani ma mĩromo yake;</para>
  <para style="q2">njĩkĩrĩire ciugo cia kanua gake gũkĩra irio ciakwa cia o mũthenya.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩ, arũgamaga arĩ o wiki; nũũ ũngĩhota kũregana nake?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ekaga o ũrĩa ekwenda.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 3:3">1Athe 3:3</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 4:12">1Pet 4:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ahingagia ũndũ ũrĩa anduĩrĩire,</para>
  <para style="q2">na arĩ o na mĩbango mĩingĩ ta ĩyo anjigĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 45:3">Kĩam 45:3</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 24:14">Josh 24:14</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩu nĩkĩo gĩtũmĩte nyiitwo nĩ kĩmako ndĩ mbere yake;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndeciiria maũndũ macio mothe-rĩ, ngamwĩtigĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 20:3">Gũcook 20:3</ref>; <ref loc="REV 6:16">Kũg 6:16</ref></char>
    </note>Mũrungu nĩatũmĩte ngoro yakwa yũrwo nĩ hinya;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩatũmĩte nyiitwo nĩ guoya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">23:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 19:8">Ayub 19:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, ndikirĩtio nĩ nduma,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩĩ nduma ĩyo ndumanu ĩhumbĩrĩte ũthiũ wakwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Nĩ kĩĩ kĩgiragia Mwene-Hinya-Wothe araarĩrie mahinda ma ciira?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga arĩa mamũũĩ meterere mĩthenya ta ĩyo o tũhũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 19:14">Gũcook 19:14</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:15">Thaam 20:15</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrĩ andũ meeheragia mahiga ma mũhaka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makarĩithia ndũũru cia mahiũ iria maiyĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Moyaga ndigiri ya mwana wa ngoriai,</para>
  <para style="q2">na magakuua ndegwa ya mũtumia wa ndigwa ĩtuĩke ya kũrũgamĩrĩra thiirĩ wao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 29:16">Ayub 29:16</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 28:12">Thim 28:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ meeheragia andũ arĩa abatari njĩra-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makahatĩrĩria athĩĩni othe a bũrũri magatũma mathiĩ makehithe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 16:12">Kĩam 16:12</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 104:23">Thab 104:23</ref></char>
    </note>O ta njagĩ cia werũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">noguo andũ arĩa athĩĩni marokagĩra wĩra wa kũhaara kĩndũ gĩa kũrĩa;</para>
  <para style="q2">kũu bũrũri ũrĩa ũtagĩaga kĩndũ nĩkuo marutaga irio cia kũhe ciana ciao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Monganagia ngaragatha mĩgũnda-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makahaara matigari mĩgũnda ya mĩthabibũ ya arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:27">Thaam 22:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Maraaraga njaga nĩ kwaga nguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">matirĩ kĩndũ gĩa kwĩhumbĩra rĩrĩa kwagĩa heho.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LAM 4:5">Maca 4:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Maconjoragio nĩ mbura ya irĩma-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao makenyiitĩrĩra mahiga nĩ ũndũ wa kwaga ha kwĩyũa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mahuragia mwana wa ngoriai kuuma nyondo-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nako gakenge ka mũthĩĩni gatahagwo nĩ ũndũ wa thiirĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:12-13">Gũcook 24:12-13</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 19:9">Alaw 19:9</ref></char>
    </note>Mathiiaga njaga nĩ kwaga nguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">makuuaga itĩĩa cia ngano, no magatigwo marĩ o ahũtu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HAG 2:16">Hag 2:16</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 6:15">Mik 6:15</ref></char>
    </note>Mahihagĩra ndamaiyũ mĩtaro-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩo makinyangaga ihihĩro cia ndibei o magĩkuaga nĩ nyoota.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Mũcaayo wa arĩa marakua nĩũraiguuo ũkiuma itũũra inene,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩoyo ya arĩa agurarie no gũkaya ĩrakaya ĩkĩenda ũteithio.</para>
  <para style="q2">No Ngai gũtirĩ mũndũ aratuĩra ciira nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩka ũũru.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:19-20">Joh 3:19-20</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 5:20">Isa 5:20</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ kũrĩ andũ arĩa mareganaga na ũtheri,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matiũĩ njĩra ciaguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana magaikara tũcĩra-inĩ twaguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 10:9">Thab 10:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa gwatuka-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũũragani ookagĩra akooraga athĩĩni na abatari;</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ ũtukũ agatuĩka ta mũici.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 7:8-9">Thim 7:8-9</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 10:11">Thab 10:11</ref></char>
    </note>Riitho rĩa gĩtharia rĩetagĩrĩra kũgĩe mairia;</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩĩraga atĩrĩ, ‘Gũtirĩ riitho o na rĩmwe rĩngĩnyona,’</para>
  <para style="q2">na gĩgaikara kĩĩhithĩte ũthiũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:2">Thaam 22:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa kũrĩ nduma-rĩ, nĩguo andũ matuaga nyũmba,</para>
  <para style="q2">no mũthenya magatinda mehingĩire;</para>
  <para style="q2">matiendaga ũndũ wa ũtheri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo andũ acio othe-rĩ, nduma ĩrĩa ndumanu nĩyo rũciinĩ rwao;</para>
  <para style="q2">magĩaga ũrata na imakania cia nduma.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:26">Ayub 9:26</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 57:20">Isa 57:20</ref></char>
    </note>“No rĩrĩ, o nĩ mũhũũyũ ũrĩa ũrerete igũrũ rĩa maaĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">igai rĩao bũrũri-inĩ nĩ irume,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ ũndũ ũcio gũtirĩ mũndũ ũthiiaga mĩgũnda-inĩ ya mĩthabibũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:17">Ayub 6:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O ta ũrĩa riũa na ũrugarĩ iniinaga maaĩ ma tharunji-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũguo noguo mbĩrĩra ĩhuragia arĩa mehĩtie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nayo nda ĩrĩa yamaciarire ĩkariganĩrwo nĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">igunyũ nacio ikamarĩa;</para>
  <para style="q1">andũ arĩa aaganu maticookaga kũririkanwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">no moinangagwo ta mũtĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:9">Ayub 22:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Marĩĩaga indo cia mũtumia thaata na ũrĩa ũtarĩ kaana,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matiiguagĩra mũtumia wa ndigwa tha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>No Ngai, nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoti wake, nĩakururagia arĩa marĩ hinya;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na mangĩĩhaanda wega-rĩ, matirĩ na mwĩhoko atĩ nĩmagatũũra muoyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="AMO 6:1">Amos 6:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 16:9">2Maũ 16:9</ref></char>
    </note>We no ametĩkĩrie maikare mahurũkĩte makĩĩiguaga ta matarĩ na ũgwati,</para>
  <para style="q2">no maitho make nĩmacũthagĩrĩria njĩra ciao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 16:9">2Ath 16:9</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 37:10">Thab 37:10</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo matũũgagĩrio o kahinda kanini, magacooka makeehera;</para>
  <para style="q2">maikũrũkagio na magakua o ta andũ arĩa angĩ othe;</para>
  <para style="q2">makeeheragio o ta igira cia ngano.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">24:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:28">Ayub 6:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Akorwo ũguo tiguo gũtariĩ-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩonania atĩ nĩndaheenania,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agĩtue ciugo ciakwa cia tũhũ?”</para>
  <chapter number="25" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Bilidadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Bilidadi ũrĩa Mũshuhi agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:4">Ayub 9:4</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 20:6">2Maũ 20:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Wathani na gwĩtigĩrwo nĩ cia Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩwe ũhaandaga watho kũu igũrũ o igũrũ mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:17">Jak 1:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mbũtũ ciake no itarĩke?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũtaaragĩrwo nĩ ũtheri wake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mũndũ aakĩhota atĩa gũkorwo arĩ mũthingu mbere ya Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũndũ ũciarĩtwo nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja-rĩ, akĩhota atĩa gũtuĩka mũtheru?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 31:26">Ayub 31:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Angĩkorwo o na mweri ti mũcangararu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na njata ti theru maitho-inĩ make-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">25:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 80:17">Thab 80:17</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 2:1">Ezek 2:1</ref></char>
    </note>mũndũ na no ta kĩgunyũ, o we mũrũ wa mũndũ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndakĩrĩ mũnyiihĩre mũno makĩrĩa!”</para>
  <chapter number="26" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:12">Ayub 6:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Kaĩ ũrĩ gũteithia ũrĩa ũtarĩ na ũhoti-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Kaĩ ũrĩ kũhonokia guoko kũrĩa gũtarĩ na hinya-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Kaĩ ũrĩ gũtaara mũndũ ũtarĩ na ũũgĩ-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Na atĩrĩ, kaĩ nĩwonanĩtie ũmenyo mũnene-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 22:24">1Ath 22:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nũũ wagũteithia kwaria ciugo icio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Na nĩ roho waũ waria na kanua gaku?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Arĩa akuũ marĩ na ruo rũnene,</para>
  <para style="q2">o acio marĩ rungu rwa maaĩ na kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩtũũraga kuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 139:8">Thab 139:8</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 15:11">Thim 15:11</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩkuũ nĩkĩguũranie mbere ya Ngai;</para>
  <para style="q2">mwanangĩko ũikarĩte ũtarĩ mũhumbĩre.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:8">Ayub 9:8</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 40:22">Isa 40:22</ref></char>
    </note>Atambũrũkagia matu ma mwena wa gathigathini igũrũ rĩa kũndũ gũtarĩ kĩndũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo thĩ ndarĩ kĩndũ amĩcunjurĩtie nakĩo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 30:4">Thim 30:4</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 1:2">Kĩam 1:2</ref></char>
    </note>Athayaga maaĩ thĩinĩ wa matu make,</para>
  <para style="q2">no matu macio matingĩtembũrwo nĩ ũritũ wamo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ahumbagĩra ũthiũ wa mweri rĩrĩa waiganana,</para>
  <para style="q2">agatambũrũkia matu make igũrũ rĩaguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 8:27">Thim 8:27</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 38:8-11">Ayub 38:8-11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩekĩrĩte rũkiriri igũrũ rĩa maaĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">rũkahakania ũtheri na nduma.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Itugĩ iria itiirĩrĩire igũrũ nĩ ithingithaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">ikagegearaga nĩ ũndũ wa ikũũmana rĩake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 14:21">Thaam 14:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩoirugire maaĩ ma iria na ũndũ wa hinya wake;</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake nĩatinaangirie Rahabu tũcunjĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 27:1">Isa 27:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mĩhũmũ yake nĩyo yathakaririe igũrũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">guoko gwake nĩ gwatheecire nyoka ĩrĩa ĩnyororokaga na ihenya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">26:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HAB 3:2">Hab 3:2</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 13:12">1Akor 13:12</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, ĩno no mĩthia ya mawĩra make;</para>
  <para style="q2">kaĩ no kamũheehũ kanini tũiguaga ka ũhoro wake-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũngĩgĩtaũkĩrwo nĩ marurumĩ ma ũhoti wake?”</para>
  <chapter number="27" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nake Ayubu agĩthiĩ na mbere na mĩario yake, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 45:9">Isa 45:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ti-itherũ o ta ũrĩa Mũrungu atũũraga muoyo, o we ũnyimĩte kĩhooto,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, ũrĩa ũtũmĩte ngĩe na ũrũrũ ngoro-inĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 33:4">Ayub 33:4</ref></char>
    </note>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yothe niĩ ngũtũũra muoyo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩhũmũ ya Ngai ĩrĩ maniũrũ-inĩ makwa,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>mĩromo yakwa ndĩkaaria maũndũ ma waganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na rũrĩmĩ rwakwa rũtikaaria maheeni.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Niĩ ndigetĩkĩra atĩ nĩ inyuĩ mũrĩ na kĩhooto;</para>
  <para style="q2">nginya rĩrĩa ngaakua, ndigakaana ũkindĩrĩku wakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 119:121">Thab 119:121</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:15">Arom 2:15</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngũtũũria ũthingu wakwa na ndikaũrekia;</para>
  <para style="q2">thamiri yakwa ndĩkanjiirithia rĩrĩa rĩothe ngũtũũra muoyo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Thũ ciakwa irogĩtuĩka ta arĩa aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa marĩ muku na niĩ marotuĩka ta arĩa matarĩ kĩhooto!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 16:22">Ndar 16:22</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:20">Luk 12:20</ref></char>
    </note>Tondũ-rĩ, kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩa ũrĩa ũtarĩ mwĩtigĩri Ngai gĩkĩrĩ kĩrĩkũ akua,</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Ngai ooya muoyo wake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 1:45">Gũcook 1:45</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 8:18">1Sam 8:18</ref></char>
    </note>Mũrungu nĩakĩiguaga gũkaya gwake</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa akorwo nĩ mĩnyamaro?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:26">Ayub 22:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩakenagĩra ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩakayagĩra Ngai mahinda mothe?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>“Nĩngũmũruta ũhoro wĩgiĩ ũhoti wa Mũrungu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndikũhitha njĩra cia Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Inyuothe nĩmwĩoneire maũndũ macio.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ĩkĩrĩ yakĩ mĩario ĩno ĩtarĩ kĩene?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 20:29">Ayub 20:29</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ũũ nĩguo Mũrungu aathagĩrĩria arĩa aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩrĩo igai rĩrĩa mũndũ ũrĩa ũtarĩ tha aamũkagĩra kuuma kũrĩ Mwene-Hinya-Wothe:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>O na ciana ciake ciaingĩha atĩa, ciathĩrĩirio rũhiũ rwa njora;</para>
  <para style="q2">rũciaro rwake rũtikoona irio cia kũrũigana.</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 78:64">Thab 78:64</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũthiro nĩguo ũkaaninũkia arĩa agaatiga thuutha wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atumia ao a ndigwa matikamarĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>O na angĩonganĩrĩria betha ta rũkũngũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agĩe na nguo nyingĩ ta hĩba cia rĩũmba,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 2:26">Koh 2:26</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 28:8">Thim 28:8</ref></char>
    </note>kĩrĩa egũcookanĩrĩria gĩkehumbwo nĩ ũrĩa mũthingu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na arĩa matarĩ mahĩtia nĩo makaagayana betha yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nyũmba ĩrĩa aakaga no ta nyũmba ya kĩĩhuruta,</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ no ta gĩthũnũ gĩakĩtwo nĩ mũrangĩri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Agaakoma arĩ mũtongu, no ndagacooka gwĩka ũguo rĩngĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">akaahingũra maitho akore gũtirĩ kĩndũ arĩ nakĩo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:21">Ayub 15:21</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 20:8">Ayub 20:8</ref></char>
    </note>Imakania imũkoragĩrĩra ta mũiyũro wa maaĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩhuhũkanio gĩkaamũhuria ũtukũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Rũhuho rwa mwena wa Irathĩro rũmuoyaga akabuĩria;</para>
  <para style="q2">rũmweheragia kũrĩa atũũraga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 13:14">Jer 13:14</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 5:11">Ezek 5:11</ref></char>
    </note>Rũmũhurutaga rũtarĩ na tha</para>
  <para style="q2">o rĩrĩa aroorĩra hinya waruo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">27:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 24:10">Ndar 24:10</ref>; <ref loc="NAM 3:19">Nahu 3:19</ref></char>
    </note>Rũhũũraga hĩ rũkamũkenerera,</para>
  <para style="q2">na rũkagamba ta nyoka rũkamũruta kũrĩa atũũraga.”</para>
  <chapter number="28" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 12:6">Thab 12:6</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 11:35">Dan 11:35</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ kũrĩ handũ harĩa betha yenjagwo</para>
  <para style="q2">o na nĩ harĩ handũ harĩa thahabu ĩtheragĩrio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Kĩgera kĩrutagwo kuuma tĩĩri-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakĩo gĩcango kĩrutagwo mahiga-inĩ gĩgatwekio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 1:13">Koh 1:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũndũ nĩkũniina aniinaga nduma;</para>
  <para style="q2">acaragia mahiga macio nginya kũrĩa kũriku mũno,</para>
  <para style="q2">o kũu nduma ĩrĩ ndumanu mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 5:8">2Sam 5:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũndũ atũrĩkagia irima thĩ kũraya na kũrĩa andũ matũũraga,</para>
  <para style="q2">agakinya kũndũ kũrĩa mũndũ aariganĩirwo nĩgũthiiaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">kũu kũraihanĩrĩirie na andũ nĩkuo acunjuuraga akĩereeraga.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">28:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Enji a marima magĩcaria tũhiga twa goro maikaragĩra itĩ ciacunjuuragio na mĩkanda.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:14">Thab 104:14</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 145:15">145:15</ref></char>
    </note>Thĩ nĩkuo kuumaga irio,</para>
  <para style="q2">no na kũu thĩinĩ mũhuro kũgarũrũkĩte gũkahaana ta gũcinĩtwo na mwaki;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 54:11">Isa 54:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>mahiga-inĩ ma thĩ nĩkuo kuumaga yakuti ĩrĩa ya bururu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mũthanga wayo ũkoragwo na ngũmba cia thahabu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ nyoni ndĩa-nyama yũĩ gacĩra kau kahithe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na gatirĩ konwo nĩ riitho rĩa hũngũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 35:9">Isa 35:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nyamũ iria ciĩtĩĩaga itirĩ ciagathiĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtirĩ mũrũũthi ũkageragĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 8:15">Gũcook 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="JON 2:6">Jon 2:6</ref></char>
    </note>Guoko kwa mũndũ gũtharĩkagĩra gũkanyiita ihiga rĩa nyaigĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na gũkaguũria itina cia irĩma.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Enjaga mungu ũgatũrĩkia rwaro rwa ihiga;</para>
  <para style="q2">maitho make makĩonaga igĩĩna ciaruo ciothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ethaga itwe cia njũũĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na indo iria hithe agaciumĩria ũtheri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 7:24">Koh 7:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“No ũũgĩ-rĩ, ũngĩoneka kũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũmenyo ũtũũraga kũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 3:15">Thim 3:15</ref>; <ref loc="JER 11:19">Jer 11:19</ref></char>
    </note>Mũndũ ndangĩmenya thogora wa ũũgĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndũngĩoneka bũrũri wa arĩa marĩ muoyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Kũrĩa kũriku mũno kuugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Ndũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa’;</para>
  <para style="q2">narĩo iria rĩkoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Ndũrĩ gũkũ gwakwa.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 3:13-14">Thim 3:13-14</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 8:20">Atũm 8:20</ref></char>
    </note>Ndũngĩgũrĩka na thahabu ĩrĩa therie mũno,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana thogora waguo ũthimwo na betha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 10:29">Kĩam 10:29</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 24:10">Thaam 24:10</ref></char>
    </note>Ndũngĩgũrĩka na thahabu ya Ofiri,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũgũrĩke na onigithi ĩrĩa ĩrĩ goro mũno,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana yakuti ĩrĩa ya bururu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Thahabu kana icicio-rĩ, itingĩhota kũgerekanio naguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana ũkũũranio na mathaga ma thahabu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 27:16">Ezek 27:16</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:11">Kũg 21:11</ref></char>
    </note>Maricani kana ngenyekenyi iria cia goro itiagĩrĩire kũgwetanio naguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">thogora wa ũũgĩ ũkĩrĩte wa ruru ĩrĩa ndune.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Yakuti ya Kushi ndĩngĩigananio naguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ndũngĩgũrĩka na thahabu ĩrĩa therie mũno.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>“Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, ũũgĩ ũngĩkiuma nakũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũmenyo ũtũũraga kũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩmũhithe kũrĩ maitho ma ciũmbe ciothe iria itũũraga muoyo,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũkahithwo o na nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 20:26">Ayub 20:26</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 8:32-36">Thim 8:32-36</ref></char>
    </note>Mwanangĩko na gĩkuũ ciugaga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘No mũhuhu waguo ũkinyĩte matũ-inĩ maitũ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 3:11">Koh 3:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ngai nĩooĩ njĩra ya gũthiĩ kũrĩa ũrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nowe wiki ũũĩ kũrĩa ũtũũraga,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 3:11">Josh 3:11</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 4:13">Ahib 4:13</ref></char>
    </note>nĩgũkorwo nĩonaga mũthia wa thĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩonaga maũndũ marĩa mothe marĩ rungu rwa igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa aathimĩire rũhuho nditi yaruo,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na agĩthima maaĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 36:28">Ayub 36:28</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 35:7">Isa 35:7</ref></char>
    </note>rĩrĩa aarutĩire mbura watho ĩrũmagĩrĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agĩtemera rũheni na marurumĩ njĩra-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>nake nĩonire ũũgĩ na akĩũthima;</para>
  <para style="q2">aũrũmirie na akĩũthuthuuria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">28:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 4:6">Gũcook 4:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Agĩcooka akĩĩra andũ atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Gwĩtigĩra Mwathani-rĩ, ũcio nĩguo ũũgĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">Nakuo gũtheemaga ũũru nĩ ũmenyo.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="29" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu nĩathiire na mbere kwaria, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 31:30">Kĩam 31:30</ref>; <ref loc="JER 1:12">Jer 1:12</ref></char>
    </note>“Naarĩ korwo no haane ũrĩa ndaatariĩ mĩeri ĩrĩa ya tene,</para>
  <para style="q2">matukũ-inĩ marĩa Ngai aamenyagĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>rĩrĩa tawa wake wamũrĩkaga igũrũ rĩa mũtwe wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndũ wa ũtheri wake ngatuĩkanagĩria nduma-inĩ!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 25:14">Thab 25:14</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 3:32">Thim 3:32</ref></char>
    </note>Korwo ndariĩ ũrĩa ndatariĩ matukũ-inĩ marĩa ndagaacĩire biũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kuumĩrania ngoro na Ngai kwarathimaga nyũmba yakwa,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 127:3-5">Thab 127:3-5</ref>; <ref loc="RUT 4:1">Ruth 4:1</ref></char>
    </note>rĩrĩa Mwene-Hinya-Wothe aarĩ hamwe na niĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ciana ciakwa ikandigiicĩria,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 20:17">Ayub 20:17</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 81:16">Thab 81:16</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 32:13">Gũcook 32:13</ref></char>
    </note>rĩrĩa gacĩra gakwa kaihũgĩtio nĩ kĩrimũ kĩa iria,</para>
  <para style="q2">naruo rwaro rwa ihiga rũgaatherũkagĩra tũrũũĩ twa maguta ma mũtamaiyũ!</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Rĩrĩa ndaathiiaga kĩhingo-inĩ kĩa itũũra inene,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngaikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩakwa hau kĩaraho-inĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 5:1">1Tim 5:1</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 19:32">Alaw 19:32</ref></char>
    </note>aanake maanyonaga makeehera,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao athuuri makarũgama,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 18:19">Atiir 18:19</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 30:32">Thim 30:32</ref></char>
    </note>andũ arĩa anene maatigaga kwaria,</para>
  <para style="q2">makahumbĩra tũnua twao na moko;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 137:6">Thab 137:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>mĩgambo ya andũ arĩa marĩ igweta ĩgakirio,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio nĩmĩ ciao ikanyiitana na karakara.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ũrĩa wothe wanjiguaga ngĩaria aaragia wega igũrũ rĩakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa maanyonaga makangaathĩrĩria,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 24:4">Ayub 24:4</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 72:12">Thab 72:12</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 21:3">Thim 21:3</ref></char>
    </note>nĩ ũndũ nĩndahatũraga arĩa athĩĩni maakaya mateithio,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na arĩa mataarĩ na maithe maagĩte mũndũ wa kũmateithia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Mũndũ agĩkua nĩandaathimaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩndatũmaga ngoro ya mũtumia wa ndigwa ĩine.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 8:15">2Sam 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:14">Aef 6:14</ref></char>
    </note>Ndehumbaga ũthingu ta nguo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciira wa kĩhooto nĩguo warĩ nguo yakwa ya igũrũ, o na kĩremba gĩakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 10:31">Ndar 10:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ niĩ ndaarĩ maitho ma arĩa atumumu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na magũrũ ma arĩa ithua.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Ndaarĩ ithe wa arĩa abatari;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩndaciiragĩrĩra o na mũndũ itooĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 3:7">Thab 3:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ nĩndoinangaga magego ma arĩa aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngahuria arĩa maarĩ magego-inĩ mao.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 30:6">Thab 30:6</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 3:1-2">Thim 3:1-2</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndeciiragia atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ngaakuĩra gwakwa nyũmba,</para>
  <para style="q2">matukũ makwa marĩ maingĩ ta mũthanga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Mĩri yakwa ĩgataamba ĩkinye maaĩ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">narĩo ireera rĩkoragwo honge-inĩ ciakwa ũtukũ wothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 18:34">Thab 18:34</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 49:24">Kĩam 49:24</ref></char>
    </note>Riiri wakwa ũgũtũũra werũhagio thĩinĩ wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũta wakwa ũtũũre ũrĩ mwerũ guoko-inĩ gwakwa.’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>“Andũ maathikagĩrĩria marĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro,</para>
  <para style="q2">meetagĩrĩra kĩrĩra gĩakwa makirĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">29:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:2">Gũcook 32:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ndaarĩkia kwaria-rĩ, matiacookaga kwaria;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciugo ciakwa ciatoonyaga matũ mao kahora ihooreire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Maanjetagĩrĩra ta andũ metereire mbura,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makanyua ciugo ciakwa o ta mbura ĩrĩa ya kũrigĩrĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Ndaamathekathekagia moorĩtwo nĩ hinya makaaga gwĩtĩkia;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtheri wa ũthiũ wakwa warĩ wa bata mũno kũrĩ o.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩ niĩ ndamoonagia njĩra, ngaikaraga ta ndĩ mũnene wao;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndatũũraga ta mũthamaki arĩ gatagatĩ ga ita rĩake;</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ ndaatariĩ ta mũndũ ũrĩa ũhooragĩria arĩa maracakaya.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="30" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:14">Ayub 6:14</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 56:10">Isa 56:10</ref></char>
    </note>“No rĩu-rĩ, andũ ethĩ kũngĩra nĩmaanyũrũragia,</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa o na itangĩendire gũturanĩra maithe mao</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngui ciakwa cia rũũru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Hinya wa moko mao ũngĩangʼunire nakĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuona atĩ hinya wao nĩwamehereire?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 8:21">Isa 8:21</ref>; <ref loc="JER 17:6">Jer 17:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩmathĩnĩkĩte nĩ ũndũ wa wagi na ngʼaragu,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtukũ-rĩ, moorũũraga bũrũri mũngʼaru,</para>
  <para style="q2">bũrũri mwanangĩku ũkirĩte ihooru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 39:6">Ayub 39:6</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 19:4">1Ath 19:4</ref></char>
    </note>Maahaaraga nyeni cia mahuti ma cumbĩ kuuma ihinga-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na irio ciao ciarĩ mĩri ya mũtĩ wa kĩhaato.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nĩmaingatirwo kuuma kũrĩ mũingĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">makiugĩrĩrio ta maarĩ aici.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 2:19">Isa 2:19</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 10:8">Hos 10:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩmahatĩrĩirio maikarage mĩkuru-inĩ ya tũrũũĩ tũhũu,</para>
  <para style="q2">kũu ndwaro-inĩ cia mahiga na marima-inĩ marĩa marĩ thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Maanagia ta nyamũ kũu ihinga-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">makahatĩkanagĩra kũu mahuti-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 9:4">Atiir 9:4</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 18:18">Ayub 18:18</ref></char>
    </note>Rũciaro rũtarĩ kĩene na rũtarĩ rĩĩtwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ rwarutũrũrirwo ruume kũu bũrũri-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:11">Thab 69:11</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 17:6">Ayub 17:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Na rĩu ariũ ao maraanyũrũria na rwĩmbo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngagĩtuĩka wa kuunagwo thimo nĩo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 25:9">Gũcook 25:9</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:67">Math 26:67</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩmathũire na magaikaraga haraihu na niĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">matiĩtigagĩra kũnduĩra mata ũthiũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ rĩu Ngai nĩaregeretie ũta wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akandeehera mathĩĩna-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">matirĩ ũndũ merigagĩrĩria gwĩka marĩ harĩa ndĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 3:1">Zek 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 140:4-5">Thab 140:4-5</ref></char>
    </note>Mwena wakwa wa ũrĩo kũrĩ rũrĩrĩ rũratharĩkĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">maigagĩra magũrũ makwa mĩtego,</para>
  <para style="q2">na magaaka ihumbu ciao cia gũũtharĩkĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Maharaganagia njĩra yakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">mahotaga kũnyũnũha o na gũtarĩ na mũndũ ũramateithia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Mokĩte ta matoonyeire mwanya-inĩ mwariĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">mokĩire gatagatĩ ga kũu kwanangĩku, makaamomokera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 3:6">Thaam 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 3:25">Ayub 3:25</ref></char>
    </note>Imakania nĩcihootete;</para>
  <para style="q2">gĩtĩĩo gĩakwa kĩũmbũrĩtwo ta kĩhurutĩtwo nĩ rũhuho,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũgitĩri wakwa ũkabuĩria ta itu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Na rĩu muoyo wakwa nĩũrathirĩrĩkĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">matukũ ma thĩĩna nĩmanyiitĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:35">Gũcook 28:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũtukũ ũtheecangaga mahĩndĩ makwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ruo rwa gũthegenya rũtindigithagĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ngai angũnjakũnjaga ta nguo na ũndũ wa ũhoti wake mũnene;</para>
  <para style="q2">aanyiitaga ta kanjũ yakwa ngingo-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 40:2">Thab 40:2</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:19">Kĩam 3:19</ref></char>
    </note>Anjikĩtie ndoro-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngatuĩka ta rũkũngũ na ta mũhu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 8:52">1Ath 8:52</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 4:9">Mik 4:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩwe ndĩrakaĩra, o Wee Ngai, no ndũranjĩtĩka;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩrarũgama, no wee no kũndora ũrandora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 6:23">Jer 6:23</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 6:14">Ezek 6:14</ref></char>
    </note>Wee nĩũngarũrũkĩte ũtarĩ na tha;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũtharĩkĩire na hinya wa guoko gwaku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:12">Jud 1:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩũũhurĩtie, ũkaandindĩka mbere ya rũhuho;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũũnyugutanĩtie kĩhuhũkanio-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nĩnjũũĩ nĩũkanginyia o gĩkuũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũndware kũrĩa gwathĩrĩirwo arĩa othe marĩ muoyo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>“Ti-itherũ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũkagĩrĩra mũndũ ũthuthĩkĩte ngoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">hĩndĩ ĩrĩa egũkaya ateithio arĩ mĩnyamaro-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 19:41">Luk 19:41</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 35:13-14">Thab 35:13-14</ref></char>
    </note>Niĩ-rĩ, githĩ ndianarĩrio nĩ arĩa marĩ na thĩĩna?</para>
  <para style="q2">Githĩ ngoro yakwa ndĩanaiguĩra arĩa athĩĩni kĩeha?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, rĩrĩa ndeerĩgagĩrĩra wega, ũũru ũgĩũka;</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa ndaacaragia ũtheri-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩyo nduma ĩgĩũka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 38:8">Thab 38:8</ref>; <ref loc="LAM 2:11">Maca 2:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nda yakwa ndĩtigaga kũruruma;</para>
  <para style="q2">matukũ ma thĩĩna nĩmanginyĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Thiiaga njirĩte biũ, no ti ũndũ wa kũhĩa nĩ riũa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngarũgama kĩũngano-inĩ ngakaya ndeithio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 34:13">Isa 34:13</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 1:8">Mik 1:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nduĩkĩte mũrũ wa nyina na mbwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngatuĩka mũthiritũ wa ndundu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">30:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 102:3">Thab 102:3</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 28:35">Gũcook 28:35</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩkonde gĩakwa nĩkĩgarũrũkĩte, gĩgathita na gĩkoonũka;</para>
  <para style="q2">mwĩrĩ wakwa ũhiũhĩte nĩ ũrugarĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Kĩnanda gĩakwa kĩa mũgeeto kĩrutaga o mũgambo wa gũcakaya,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo mũtũrirũ wakwa ũkaruta o mũgambo wa kĩrĩro.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="31" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 2:14">2Pet 2:14</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:28">Math 5:28</ref></char>
    </note>“Niĩ nĩtwarĩĩkanĩire na maitho makwa</para>
  <para style="q2">ndikanarore mũirĩtu ndĩmwĩrirĩrie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, kaĩ rũgai rwa mũndũ kuuma igũrũ kwa Ngai rũkĩrĩ kĩĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Igai rĩake nĩ rĩrĩkũ kuuma kũrĩ ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ũrĩ igũrũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 21:30">Ayub 21:30</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:9">Arom 2:9</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ ti kwanangwo kwa arĩa aaganu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mũtino kũrĩ arĩa meekaga maũndũ mooru?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 16:9">2Maũ 16:9</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 4:37">Dan 4:37</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ we ndonaga njĩra ciakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agatara o ikinya o ikinya rĩakwa?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Ingĩkorwo thiiaga na njĩra itarĩ cia ma-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana kũgũrũ gwakwa gũkahiũha thiĩ ngaheenanie-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:36">Alaw 19:36</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 6:9">Kĩam 6:9</ref></char>
    </note>Ngai nĩathime na ratiri cia kĩhooto,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake nĩekũmenya atĩ niĩ ndirĩ ũcuuke;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 23:11">Ayub 23:11</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 7:3">Thab 7:3</ref></char>
    </note>makinya makwa mangĩkorwo nĩmahũkĩte makoima njĩra-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo ngoro yakwa ĩngĩkorwo nĩĩtongoretio nĩ maitho makwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana moko makwa makorwo nĩmathaahĩtio-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>hĩndĩ ĩyo kĩrĩa haandĩte kĩrorĩĩo nĩ andũ angĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio irio cia mĩgũnda yakwa iromunywo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 11:16">Gũcook 11:16</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:14">Jak 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Ngoro yakwa ĩngĩkorwo yanaheenererio nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngorwo ndanaceema mũrango-inĩ wa mũndũ wa itũũra,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 16:21">Atiir 16:21</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 28:30">Gũcook 28:30</ref></char>
    </note>hĩndĩ ĩyo mũtumia wakwa arothĩa ngano ya mũndũ ũngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na arũme angĩ tiga niĩ marokoma nake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 6:32-33">Thim 6:32-33</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 8:4-5">Josh 8:4-5</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo ũndũ ũcio nĩ ũmaramari wa thoni,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ rĩĩhia rĩa gũtuĩrwo ciira nĩ kĩama.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Tondũ ũcio nĩ mwaki ũrĩa ũcinaga nginya ũkaananga;</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩũngĩamunyĩte magetha makwa mothe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 24:14-15">Gũcook 24:14-15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ingĩkorwo nĩnyimĩte ndungata ciakwa cia arũme na cia andũ-a-nja kĩhooto</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa manateta nĩ ũndũ wakwa-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 6:32-33">Thim 6:32-33</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:4-5">Joh 8:4-5</ref></char>
    </note>niĩ ngeeka atĩa rĩrĩa Mũrungu akaanjũkĩrĩra?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ngaacookia atĩa rĩrĩa ngeetwo ndĩĩtetere ũhoro-inĩ ũcio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Githĩ ũcio wanyũũmbire kũu nda ya maitũ to we wamoombire?</para>
  <para style="q2">Githĩ tiwe watũthondekire tũrĩ kũu nda cia aa maitũ?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:9">Ayub 22:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ingĩkorwo ndanaima athĩĩni kĩrĩa maanerirĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngareka maitho ma mũtũmia wa ndigwa morwo nĩ hinya-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>ingĩkorwo ndĩĩaga irio ciakwa nyiki,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngaaga kũgayana na ũrĩa ũtarĩ ithe-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>(no niĩ kuuma ũnini wakwa, mwana ta ũcio ndaamũreraga o ta ũrĩa angĩarerirwo nĩ ithe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kuuma gũciarwo gwakwa ndũire ndongoragia mũtumia wa ndigwa)</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>ingĩkorwo ndanoona mũndũ agĩkua nĩ ũndũ wa kwaga nguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngoona mũndũ mũbatari atarĩ kĩndũ gĩa kwĩhumba,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 29:13">Ayub 29:13</ref>; <ref loc="JDG 6:37">Atiir 6:37</ref></char>
    </note>na ngoro yake ndĩandathimire nĩ ũndũ wa kũmũiguithia ũrugarĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na guoya wa ngʼondu ciakwa-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>ingĩkorwo ndanoya guoko gwakwa ngookĩrĩra mwana ũtarĩ ithe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩkũmenya atĩ no nyone wa kũndeithia kwagĩa ciira igooti-inĩ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 38:15">Ayub 38:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>hĩndĩ ĩyo guoko gwakwa kũroahũkĩra kĩande-inĩ kũgwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">kũroinĩkĩra o irũngo-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ nĩndetigagĩra mwanangĩko uumĩte kũrĩ Mũrungu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra riiri wake, ndingĩekire maũndũ ta macio.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>“Ingĩkorwo nĩnjigĩte mwĩhoko wakwa harĩ thahabu,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngeera thahabu ĩrĩa therie mũno atĩrĩ, ‘Wee nĩwe ũgitĩri wakwa,’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 62:10">Thab 62:10</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 28:5">Ezek 28:5</ref></char>
    </note>ingĩkorwo ndanakenera ũtonga wakwa mũnene,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngakenera uumithio ũrĩa moko makwa mecarĩirie-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>ingĩkorwo ndanarũmbũiya riũa rĩarĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana mweri ũgĩthiĩ ũcangararĩte,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 11:16">Gũcook 11:16</ref>; <ref loc="JER 8:2">Jer 8:2</ref></char>
    </note>na ngoro yakwa ĩkĩheenererio nĩcio na hitho,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana guoko gwakwa gũgĩcikinyĩria kĩmumunyano gĩa gũcitĩĩa-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 17:2-7">Gũcook 17:2-7</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 11:20">Ndar 11:20</ref></char>
    </note>o na macio mangĩtuĩka mehia ma gũtuĩrwo ciira,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo ingĩtuĩkĩte mũndũ ũtarĩ mwĩhokeku harĩ Mũrungu ũrĩa ũrĩ igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 14:1">Ndar 14:1</ref>; <ref loc="OBA 1:12">Obad 1:12</ref></char>
    </note>“Ingĩkorwo ndaanakena nĩ thũ yakwa kuona mũtino,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngĩmĩthekerera rĩrĩa thĩĩna wamĩkora,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>no niĩ ndirĩ ndetĩkĩra kanua gakwa keehie</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndũ wa kũhoera muoyo wayo kĩrumi,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:7">Ayub 22:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>kũngĩkorwo andũ a nyũmba yakwa matirĩ moiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Nũũ ũtarĩ warĩa nyama cia Ayubu akahũũna?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 19:2-3">Kĩam 19:2-3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 12:14">Arom 12:14</ref></char>
    </note>no gũtirĩ mũgeni wanaraara njĩra-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ mũrango wa mũciĩ wakwa ũtũire ũhingũrĩirwo mũgendi,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>ingĩkorwo ndaanahitha mehia makwa, ta ũrĩa andũ meekaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndũ wa kũhitha mahĩtia ngoro-inĩ yakwa</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 23:2">Thaam 23:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 32:3">Thab 32:3</ref></char>
    </note>tondũ wa gwĩtigĩra kĩrĩndĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gwĩtigĩra kũmenwo nĩ mĩhĩrĩga</para>
  <para style="q2">ngagĩkira ki na ndiume nja-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>(“Naarĩ korwo ndaarĩ na mũndũ wa kũnjigua!</para>
  <para style="q2">Rĩu nĩndekĩra rũũri rwa kwĩyarĩrĩria:</para>
  <para style="q2">reke Mwene-Hinya-Wothe anjookerie ũhoro;</para>
  <para style="q2">reke mũũthitangi andĩke marũa ma thitango yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 28:12">Thaam 28:12</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 29:14">Ayub 29:14</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ marũa macio ingĩmaigĩrĩra kĩande,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩmehumbe taarĩ thũmbĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Njooke ndĩmũhe ũhoro wakwa ikinya gwa ikinya;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩmũkuhĩrĩrie ta ndĩ mũnene.)</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 4:10">Kĩam 4:10</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 65:10">Thab 65:10</ref></char>
    </note>“Korwo mũgũnda wakwa wakaya, ũnjũkĩrĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mĩtaro yaguo yothe ĩkorwo ĩkĩrĩra maithori,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 21:19">1Ath 21:19</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:4">Jak 5:4</ref></char>
    </note>ingĩkorwo ndanarĩa maciaro maguo iteekũrĩha,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngoraga ngoro cia ene guo-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">31:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 3:18">Kĩam 3:18</ref>; <ref loc="ZEP 2:9">Zef 2:9</ref></char>
    </note>hĩndĩ ĩyo congʼe ũrokũra kuo handũ ha ngano,</para>
  <para style="q2">na riya handũ ha cairi.”</para>
  <para style="p">Ndeto cia Ayubu nĩciathira.</para>
  <chapter number="32" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Elihu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio andũ acio atatũ nĩmatigire gũcookeria Ayubu, nĩ ũndũ eeyonaga arĩ mũthingu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">32:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 22:21">Kĩam 22:21</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, Elihu mũrũ wa Barakeli ũrĩa Mũbuzi, wa nyũmba ya Ramu, nĩarakaririo mũno nĩ Ayubu nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtua aarĩ na kĩhooto gũkĩra Ngai. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ningĩ nĩarakarĩtio nĩ arata acio atatũ tondũ nĩmagĩte ũndũ mangĩcookeria Ayubu, o na gũtuĩka nĩmamũtuĩrĩire ciira. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">32:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 19:32">Alaw 19:32</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, Elihu aambĩte gweterera acio angĩ maarie atanaaria na Ayubu, tondũ o maarĩ akũrũ kũmũkĩra. <verse number="5" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa onire atĩ andũ acio atatũ matiarĩ na ũndũ ũngĩ wa kuuga-rĩ, agĩakanwo nĩ marakara.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:10">Ayub 15:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Elihu, mũrũ wa Barakeli ũcio Mũbuzi, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Niĩ ndĩ na mĩaka mĩnini,</para>
  <para style="q2">na inyuĩ mũrĩ akũrũ;</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩkĩo ngwĩtigagĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngaaga ũũmĩrĩru wa kũmwĩra ũrĩa njũũĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CH 29:15">1Maũ 29:15</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 10:6">2Maũ 10:6</ref></char>
    </note>Ndeciiragia atĩrĩ, ‘Ũkũrũ nĩwaagĩrĩire warie;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũingĩ wa mĩaka nĩwaagĩrĩire kũrutana ũũgĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>No nĩ roho ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o yo mĩhũmũ ya Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, ũheaga mũndũ ũmenyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 1:26">1Akor 1:26</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 4:12">1Tim 4:12</ref></char>
    </note>To arĩa akũrũ oiki oogĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na to arĩa akũrũ mamenyaga ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 33:1">Ayub 33:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nguuga atĩrĩ, ‘Thikĩrĩriai;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na niĩ nĩngũmwĩra ũrĩa njũũĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩngwetereire rĩrĩa mũkwaragia,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndathikĩrĩria ihooto cianyu;</para>
  <para style="q1">rĩrĩa mũgũcaragia ciugo-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>nĩngũmũtegeire matũ biũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">No gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu wonanirie mahĩtia ma Ayubu;</para>
  <para style="q2">gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu ũmũcookeirie mĩario yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ECC 9:11">Koh 9:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tigai kuuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩtũgĩĩte na ũũgĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">rekei Mũrungu amũkararie, no ti mũndũ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, Ayubu ti niĩ ekwerekeirie ciugo ciake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ ndikũmũcookeria kũringana na mĩario yanyu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>“Nĩmamakĩte, na matirĩ na ũndũ ũngĩ mangiuga;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩmarigĩtwo nĩ atĩa mangiuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>no nginya njeterere, nĩ ũndũ rĩu nĩmakirĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ atĩ rĩu marũgamĩte hau matarĩ na macookio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>O na niĩ nĩngwaria;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na niĩ nĩnguuga ũrĩa njũũĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 4:20">Atũm 4:20</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:14">2Akor 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo njiyũrĩtwo nĩ ciugo,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo roho ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa nĩũrandindĩkĩrĩria;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 20:9">Jer 20:9</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 9:17">Math 9:17</ref></char>
    </note>thĩinĩ wakwa haana ta ndibei ĩrĩ cuba ngunĩke,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngahaana ta mondo njerũ ya ndibei ĩkirie gũtuthũka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>no nginya njarie hũũcũke,</para>
  <para style="q2">no nginya ndumũre mĩromo yakwa njookie ũhoro.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">32:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:15">Alaw 19:15</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 22:16">Math 22:16</ref></char>
    </note>Ndigũtĩĩra mũndũ o na ũ maũthĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ngaathĩrĩrie mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ tũhũ;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>nĩ ũndũ korwo ndĩ mwara na kũgaathĩrĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũnyũũmbi no anjeherie narua.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="33" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“No rĩu Ayubu-rĩ, thikĩrĩria ciugo ciakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">tega matũ ũigue ũrĩa wothe nguuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Ndĩ hakuhĩ gũtumũra kanua gakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciugo ciakwa irĩ o rũrĩmĩ-inĩ rwakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 3:6">1Ath 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 6:28">Ayub 6:28</ref></char>
    </note>Ciugo ciakwa ciumĩte ngoro nũngĩrĩru;</para>
  <para style="q2">mĩromo yakwa yaragia ĩtarĩ na ũhinga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:2">Kĩam 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 16:22">Ndar 16:22</ref></char>
    </note>Roho wa Mũrungu nĩwe ũnyũmbĩte;</para>
  <para style="q2">mĩhũmũ ya Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩyo ĩĩheaga muoyo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nawe njookeria, akorwo nĩũkũhota;</para>
  <para style="q2">wĩhaarĩrie ũũngʼethere.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Niĩ haana o tawe maitho-inĩ ma Mũrungu;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na niĩ ndombirwo na rĩũmba.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:34">Ayub 9:34</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 2:4">2Akor 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>Kwĩĩndigĩra gũtigakũmakie,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana guoko gwakwa gũkũritũhĩre.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>“No rĩrĩ, nĩuugĩte ngĩiguaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngaigua ciugo icio ũkiuga atĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 10:7">Ayub 10:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>‘Ndĩ mũtheru na ndirĩ na mehia;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndiĩkĩte ũũru, na ndirĩ na mahĩtia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>No Ngai nĩanyonete na mahĩtia;</para>
  <para style="q2">anduĩte thũ yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:27">Ayub 13:27</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 30:21">Isa 30:21</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩanjohaga magũrũ na mĩnyororo;</para>
  <para style="q2">arangagĩra njĩra ciakwa ciothe.’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“No ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ, ũhoro-inĩ ũyũ wee ndũrĩ na kĩhooto,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo Ngai nĩ mũnene gũkĩra mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 45:9">Isa 45:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũramũtetia nĩkĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ ndacookagia kiugo kĩa mũndũ o na kĩmwe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 62:11">Thab 62:11</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 4:12">Ayub 4:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo Mũrungu nĩaaragia,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩmwe na njĩra ĩmwe, na rĩngĩ akaaria na njĩra ĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtuĩka mũndũ no aage gũkũũrana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 4:13">Ayub 4:13</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 15:1">Kĩam 15:1</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩmwe akaaragia kĩroto-inĩ na kĩoneki-inĩ gĩa ũtukũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa andũ mahĩtĩtwo nĩ toro mũnene marĩ ũrĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 36:10">Ayub 36:10</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 36:15">15</ref></char>
    </note>no amaarĩrie matũ-inĩ mao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na amamakie nĩguo amakaanie,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>nĩguo agarũre mũndũ atige kũhĩtia,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atigane na mwĩtĩĩo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 28:1">Thab 28:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:52">Math 26:52</ref></char>
    </note>nĩguo agitĩre roho wake kuuma gĩkuũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agitĩre muoyo wake ndũkaniinwo na rũhiũ rwa njora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 17:1">Kĩam 17:1</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 38:13">Isa 38:13</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ mũndũ no arũithio na gũkomio ũrĩrĩ wa ruo,</para>
  <para style="q2">akorwo na thĩĩna wa mahĩndĩ ũtathiraga,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>o nginya ngoro yake ĩgathũũra irio,</para>
  <para style="q2">na roho wake ũgathũũra irio iria njega mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 16:8">Ayub 16:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nyama cia mwĩrĩ wake ihĩnjaga igathirĩrĩkĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mahĩndĩ make marĩa mataroonekaga makoimĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Roho wake ũgakuhĩrĩria mbĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na muoyo wake ũgakuhĩrĩria arĩa mareehage gĩkuũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 3:19">Agal 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 6:8">Mik 6:8</ref></char>
    </note>“No rĩrĩ, angĩkorwo harĩ na mũraika mwena wake arĩ mũiguithania,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmwe harĩ ngiri, wa kwĩra mũndũ ũndũ ũrĩa ũmwagĩrĩire,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>nake amũkinyĩrie wega wake na oige atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Mũhonokie ndagatuĩke wa gũikũrũka mbĩrĩra-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩnyonete gĩa kũmũkũũra nakĩo,’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 103:5">Thab 103:5</ref>; <ref loc="2KI 5:14">2Ath 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>hĩndĩ ĩyo nyama cia mwĩrĩ wake igeethĩha ta cia mwana;</para>
  <para style="q2">igaacooka ta ũrĩa ciarĩ matukũ-inĩ ma wĩthĩ wake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ahooyaga Ngai ageekwo wega nĩwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">oonaga ũthiũ wa Ngai akaanĩrĩra nĩ gũkena;</para>
  <para style="q2">agacookio ũthingu-inĩ wake nĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 15:21">Luk 15:21</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:21">Arom 6:21</ref></char>
    </note>Nake agacooka agathiĩ kũrĩ andũ akameera atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Nĩndehirie, na ngĩogomia ũndũ ũrĩa warĩ wa ma,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ndiigana kũherithio ũrĩa ndaagĩrĩirwo nĩkũherithio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Nĩakũũrire roho wakwa ndũkaharũrũkio mbĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ ngũtũũra ngenagĩra ũtheri ũcio.’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:11">Aef 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:13">Afil 2:13</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũrungu nĩekaga mũndũ maũndũ macio mothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">maita meerĩ o na kana matatũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 56:13">Thab 56:13</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 60:1">Isa 60:1</ref></char>
    </note>nĩguo agarũre roho wake ndũkaharũrũkio mbĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha ũtheri ũcio wa muoyo ũmũtherere.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 23:18">Jer 23:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Atĩrĩrĩ Ayubu, tega matũ na ũũthikĩrĩrie;</para>
  <para style="q2">kira ki na niĩ njarie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Wakorwo ũrĩ na ũndũ wa kuuga-rĩ, njĩĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">aria, nĩgũkorwo ingĩenda woneke ndwĩhĩtie.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">33:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 32:10">Ayub 32:10</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 10:8">Thim 10:8</ref></char>
    </note>No akorwo ti ũguo-rĩ, wee gĩthikĩrĩrie;</para>
  <para style="q2">kira ki, na nĩngũkũruta ũũgĩ.”</para>
  <chapter number="34" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Elihu akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Iguai ciugo ciakwa, inyuĩ andũ aya oogĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">thikĩrĩriai, inyuĩ amenyi a maũndũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 12:11">Ayub 12:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo gũtũ gũthuuranagia ciugo</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa rũrĩmĩ rũcamaga irio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 5:14">Ahib 5:14</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 5:21">1Athe 5:21</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩtwĩkũũranĩrei ithuĩ ene ũndũ ũrĩa wagĩrĩire;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩtwĩrute tũrĩ hamwe ũndũ ũrĩa mwega.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Ayubu aroiga atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ndihĩtĩtie,</para>
  <para style="q2">no Mũrungu nĩanjagithĩtie kĩhooto gĩakwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:28">Ayub 6:28</ref>; <ref loc="JER 10:19">Jer 10:19</ref></char>
    </note>O na gũtuĩka ndĩraria ũrĩa kũrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩratuuo mũheenania;</para>
  <para style="q1">o na gũtuĩka ndirĩ na mahĩtia,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũguĩ wake ũngurarĩtie kĩronda gĩtangĩhona.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:16">Ayub 15:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ mũndũ ũrĩkũ ũhaana ta Ayubu,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũndũ ũnyuuaga kĩnyũrũri taarĩ maaĩ aranyua?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Atwaranaga na andũ arĩa mekaga ũũru;</para>
  <para style="q2">agĩĩaga thiritũ na andũ arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo oigaga atĩrĩ, ‘Gũtirĩ uumithio mũndũ onaga</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa arageria gũkenia Ngai.’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 32:10">Ayub 32:10</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 18:25">Kĩam 18:25</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio gĩĩthikĩrĩriei, inyuĩ andũ aya mũrĩ na ũtaũku.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũhoro wa kwĩhia ũroaga kuoneka harĩ Mũrungu,</para>
  <para style="q2">Mwene-Hinya-Wothe aroaga gwĩka ũũru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:27">Math 16:27</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 33:20">Ezek 33:20</ref></char>
    </note>Arĩhaga mũndũ kũringana na ũrĩa ekĩte;</para>
  <para style="q2">akamũrehere o kĩrĩa kĩringaine na mĩthiĩre yake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 6:18">Ahib 6:18</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 8:3">Ayub 8:3</ref></char>
    </note>Gũtingĩhoteka atĩ Mũrungu no eeke mahĩtia,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ ũrĩa Mwene-Hinya-Wothe no ogomie kĩhooto.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 1:2">Ahib 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 40:14">Isa 40:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ wamũtuire mũrori wa thĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ wamũtuire mũrũgamĩrĩri wa thĩ yothe?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 6:3">Kĩam 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 16:22">Ndar 16:22</ref></char>
    </note>Korwo aagĩa na muoroto</para>
  <para style="q2">wa kweheria roho wake na mĩhũmũ-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 3:6">Mal 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 90:10">Thab 90:10</ref></char>
    </note>andũ othe mangĩthiranĩra hamwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake mũndũ acooke rũkũngũ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Akorwo ũrĩ mũndũ ũrĩ na ũtaũku-rĩ, igua ũhoro ũyũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">thikĩrĩria ũrĩa nguuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 23:3-4">2Sam 23:3-4</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 3:5-6">Arom 3:5-6</ref></char>
    </note>Mũndũ ũthũire kĩhooto-rĩ, no ahote gwathana?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũrĩa ũrĩ kĩhooto, o Ũcio kĩhoti-rĩ, no ũmũtue mwĩhia?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:28">Thaam 22:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Githĩ ti we wĩraga athamaki atĩrĩ, ‘Inyuĩ mũtirĩ kĩene,’</para>
  <para style="q2">na akeera arĩa marĩ igweta atĩrĩ, ‘Inyuĩ mũrĩ aaganu,’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>o ũcio ũtatĩagĩra anene maũthĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndendaga arĩa atongu gũkĩra arĩa athĩĩni,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo othe nĩ wĩra wa moko make?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 11:4">Thaam 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 12:19">Ayub 12:19</ref></char>
    </note>Makuuaga o rĩmwe, o ũtukũ gatagatĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ mainainaga magakua;</para>
  <para style="q2">arĩa marĩ hinya meeheragio matahutĩtio nĩ guoko kwa mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 32:19">Jer 32:19</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 4:13">Ahib 4:13</ref></char>
    </note>“Maitho make maikaraga macũthĩrĩirie mĩthiĩre ya andũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩonaga mĩthiĩre yao yothe.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ handũ harĩ nduma, kana handũ harĩ kĩĩruru kĩnene,</para>
  <para style="q2">hangĩĩhithwo nĩ arĩa meekaga ũũru.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Mũrungu ndabatairio nĩgũthuthuuria ndeto cia andũ makĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ nĩguo moke mbere yake maciirithio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 2:21">Dan 2:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ahehenjaga arĩa marĩ ũhoti atekũũria mũndũ</para>
  <para style="q2">na akarũgamia andũ angĩ ithenya rĩao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Tondũ we nĩamenyaga maũndũ marĩa meekaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">amangʼaũranagia ũtukũ magathuthĩka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 6:5">Kĩam 6:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 44:5">Jer 44:5</ref></char>
    </note>Amaherithagĩria waganu wao</para>
  <para style="q2">makĩonagwo nĩ mũndũ o wothe,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 14:3">Thab 14:3</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 15:11">1Sam 15:11</ref></char>
    </note>tondũ nĩmagarũrũkire magĩtiga kũmũrũmĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matirũmbũyagia njĩra yake o na ĩrĩkũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 22:23">Thaam 22:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩmatũmire kĩrĩro kĩa arĩa athĩĩni gĩkinye hau mbere yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩigua kĩrĩro kĩa arĩa abatari.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 28:1">Thab 28:1</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:34">Arom 8:34</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, angĩikara akirĩte-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩmũtua muhĩtia?</para>
  <para style="q2">Angĩhitha ũthiũ wake-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩmuona?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nowe arĩ igũrũ rĩa mũndũ na igũrũ rĩa rũrĩrĩ o ũndũ ũmwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>nĩguo agirie mũndũ ũtarĩ na ũngai gwathana,</para>
  <para style="q2">amũgirie kũigĩra kĩrĩndĩ mĩtego.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 15:21">Luk 15:21</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 1:8">1Joh 1:8</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 1:10">10</ref></char>
    </note>“Korwo mũndũ no ere Mũrungu atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Nĩnjĩhĩtie no ndikehia rĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 33:13">Thaam 33:13</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 19:8">Luk 19:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nduta menye ũrĩa itarahota kuona;</para>
  <para style="q2">ingĩkorwo nĩnjĩkĩte ũũru-rĩ, ndigacooka gwĩka ũguo rĩngĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 17:13">2Ath 17:13</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 17:23">Thim 17:23</ref></char>
    </note>Ngai-rĩ, no agĩkũrĩhe kũringana na ũrĩa wee ũkwenda</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa ũregete kwĩrira?</para>
  <para style="q1">No nginya we ũtue itua, no ti niĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio kĩnjĩĩre ũrĩa ũũĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>“Andũ arĩa marĩ na ũtaũku maroiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao andũ acio oogĩ maiguĩte ngĩaria manjĩĩrĩte atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 35:16">Ayub 35:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>‘Ayubu aaragia atarĩ na ũmenyo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciugo ciake nĩciagĩte ũũgĩ.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">34:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 22:15">Ayub 22:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩ, naarĩ korwo Ayubu aagerio nginya mũthia,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ macookio make nĩ ta ma mũndũ mwaganu!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nĩongereire ũremi harĩ mehia make;</para>
  <para style="q2">atũhũũragĩra hĩ cia kĩnyũrũri,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akaingĩhia ciugo ciake cia gũũkĩrĩra Mũrungu.”</para>
  <chapter number="35" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Elihu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Elihu akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Nĩũgwĩciiria ũhoro ũyũ nĩ wa kĩhooto?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũroiga atĩrĩ, ‘Mũrungu nĩekũnjarĩrĩria atue ndiĩhĩtie.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:29-31">Ayub 9:29-31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, wee no ũramũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Kũrĩ na uumithio ũrĩkũ harĩ niĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngũgunĩka nakĩ ndaaga kwĩhia?’</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>“No nyende gũgũcookeria ũhoro,</para>
  <para style="q2">wee hamwe na arata aku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 15:5">Kĩam 15:5</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 19:1-4">Thab 19:1-4</ref></char>
    </note>Ta rora igũrũ wone;</para>
  <para style="q2">ta cũthĩrĩria matu macio marĩ igũrũ rĩaku kũraya mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ũngĩĩhia-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio ũngĩhutia Ngai atĩa?</para>
  <para style="q2">Mehia maku mangĩingĩha mũno-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio ũngĩmwĩka atĩa?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 11:35">Arom 11:35</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 22:2-3">Ayub 22:2-3</ref></char>
    </note>Ũngĩkorwo ũrĩ mũthingu-rĩ, ũngĩmũhe kĩĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana nĩ kĩĩ aamũkagĩra kuuma guoko-inĩ gwaku?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Waganu waku ũhutagia o mũndũ tawe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũthingu waku ũkahutia o ciana cia andũ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 2:23">Thaam 2:23</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 12:19">Ayub 12:19</ref></char>
    </note>“Andũ makayaga nĩ icooki rĩa kũhinyĩrĩrio;</para>
  <para style="q2">mathaithanaga mateithũrwo guoko-inĩ kwa ũcio ũrĩ hinya mũingĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 4:17">Ayub 4:17</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 16:25">Atũm 16:25</ref></char>
    </note>No gũtirĩ mũndũ uugaga atĩrĩ, ‘Ngai ũrĩa wanyũũmbire arĩ ha,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa ũheaga mũndũ nyĩmbo ũtukũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>ũrĩa ũtũrutaga maũndũ gũkĩra ũrĩa arutaga nyamũ cia werũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na agatũhe ũũgĩ gũkĩra nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ?’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 8:18">1Sam 8:18</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 66:18">Thab 66:18</ref></char>
    </note>Ndacookagia rĩrĩa andũ maakaya</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ wa mwĩtũũgĩrio wa andũ arĩa aaganu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 1:45">Gũcook 1:45</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 15:8">Thim 15:8</ref></char>
    </note>Ti-itherũ, Mũrungu ndathikagĩrĩria mathaithana mao ma tũhũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ndarũmbũyagia mathaithana macio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Githĩ ndakaaga gũthikĩrĩria mũno makĩria</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa ũkuuga atĩ ndũramuona,</para>
  <para style="q1">na atĩ ciira waku ũrĩ mbere yake,</para>
  <para style="q2">na no nginya ũmweterere,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:24">Ayub 9:24</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 7:2">Hos 7:2</ref></char>
    </note>na makĩria ma ũguo ũkoiga atĩ marakara make matiherithanagia</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndarũmbũyagia waganu o na hanini!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">35:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="TIT 1:10">Tit 1:10</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 34:35">Ayub 34:35</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 34:37">37</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Ayubu atumũrĩte kanua gake akaaria ũhoro wa tũhũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩarĩĩtie ndeto nyingĩ atarĩ na ũmenyo.”</para>
  <chapter number="36" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Elihu agĩthiĩ na mbere kwaria, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Ngirĩrĩria hanini, na nĩngũkuonia</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ harĩ maũndũ mangĩ mangiugwo ma gũciirĩrĩra Ngai.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:28">Ayub 6:28</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 4:17">4:17</ref></char>
    </note>Ũmenyo wakwa ndĩũrutĩte kũraihu;</para>
  <para style="q2">niĩ ngũtũũgĩria kĩhooto kĩa ũcio Mũnyũũmbi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Menya wega atĩ ndeto ciakwa ti cia maheeni;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũyũ mũrĩ nake arĩ na ũmenyo mũkinyanĩru.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 5:2">Thab 5:2</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:29">Arom 11:29</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũrungu nĩwe mwene hinya, no ndairaga andũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">we nĩ mwene hinya, na nĩarũmagia muoroto wake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ndatũũragia arĩa aaganu muoyo,</para>
  <para style="q2">no nĩaheaga arĩa anyariire kĩhooto kĩao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 11:11">Ayub 11:11</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 6:18">Math 6:18</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 2:7-8">1Sam 2:7-8</ref></char>
    </note>Ndeheragia maitho make harĩ arĩa athingu;</para>
  <para style="q2">amaikaragĩria gĩtĩ kĩa ũnene hamwe na athamaki,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akamatũũgĩria nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 3:34">2Sam 3:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, andũ mangĩkorwo mohetwo na mĩnyororo,</para>
  <para style="q2">makanyiitio na mĩhĩndo ya mĩnyamaro,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>we nĩameeraga ũrĩa mekĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ mehĩtie na ũtũrĩka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 33:16">Ayub 33:16</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 5:22">1Athe 5:22</ref></char>
    </note>We nĩatũmaga mathikĩrĩrie ũtaaro,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akamaatha merire ũũru wao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 26:33">Alaw 26:33</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 8:22">Thaam 8:22</ref></char>
    </note>Mangĩmwathĩkĩra na mamũtungatĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">megũtũũra matukũ mao marĩa matigaru magaacĩire,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mĩaka yao o maiganĩire.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 15:22">Ayub 15:22</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:18">Aef 4:18</ref></char>
    </note>No mangĩaga kũigua,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩmakaniinwo na rũhiũ rwa njora,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makue matarĩ na ũmenyo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Arĩa matarĩ na Ngai ngoro-inĩ meiigagĩra marakara;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na rĩrĩa aramooha na mĩnyororo, matikayaga mateithio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 23:17">Gũcook 23:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Makuuaga marĩ ethĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">magakua hamwe na arũme arĩa maraya ma mahooero-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>No arĩa mathĩĩnĩkaga, nĩamakũũraga kuuma thĩĩna-inĩ wao;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩamaragĩria marĩ mĩnyamaro-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HOS 2:14">Hos 2:14</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 17:1">Kĩam 17:1</ref></char>
    </note>“We-rĩ, nĩarakũguucĩrĩria uume magego-inĩ ma mĩnyamaro,</para>
  <para style="q2">agũtware handũ haariĩ hatarĩ na ũkunderu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na agũtware akũhurũkie metha-inĩ yaku ĩiyũrĩte irio iria njega.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>No rĩu-rĩ, ũtitikithĩtio ituĩro rĩrĩa rĩagĩrĩire arĩa aaganu;</para>
  <para style="q2">ituĩro rĩa ciira na kĩhooto nĩcigũkumbatĩte.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 23:18">Thaam 23:18</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 34:33">Ayub 34:33</ref></char>
    </note>Wĩmenyerere mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ndakanakũheenererie na ũtonga;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndũgetĩkĩrie ihaki inene rĩkũhĩtithie njĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ũtonga waku o na kana kĩyo gĩaku kĩnene-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">no ikũnyiitĩrĩre nĩguo ndũgatoonye mĩnyamaro-inĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Tiga kwĩrirĩria ũtukũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo ũguucũrũrie andũ kuuma kwao mĩciĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 66:18">Thab 66:18</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 11:25">Ahib 11:25</ref></char>
    </note>Wĩmenyerere ndũkeerekere ũũru-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ ũkuoneka taarĩ guo wendete gũkĩra gũthĩĩnĩka.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>“Mũrungu nĩatũgĩrĩtio nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoti wake.</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ mũrutani take?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 34:13">Ayub 34:13</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 18:25">Kĩam 18:25</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ ũmwathĩrĩire njĩra ciake,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana akamwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Wee nĩwĩkĩte ũũru’?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 92:5">Thab 92:5</ref>; <ref loc="REV 15:3">Kũg 15:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ririkanaga gwĩkĩrĩra wĩra wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa andũ manakumia na rwĩmbo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Andũ othe nĩmawonete;</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ mawĩroragĩra marĩ o kũraya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 13:12">1Akor 13:12</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 1:12">Ahib 1:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ĩ Mũrungu ndakĩrĩ mũnene; nĩ mũnene gũkĩra ũmenyi witũ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũigana wa mĩaka yake ndũngĩtuĩrĩka.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 1:21">2Sam 1:21</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 55:10">Isa 55:10</ref></char>
    </note>“Ambatagia matata ma maaĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">marĩa macookaga gũtaatĩra tũrũũĩ ta mbura;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 65:10">Thab 65:10</ref>; <ref loc="JOL 2:23">Joel 2:23</ref></char>
    </note>matu magaita ũigũ wamo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mbura nyingĩ ĩkoirĩra andũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 10:13">Jer 10:13</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 40:22">Isa 40:22</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ ũngĩmenya ũrĩa atambũrũkagia matu,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũhoro wa marurumĩ marĩa moimaga hema-inĩ yake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Kĩone ũrĩa ahurunjaga rũheni rwake rũkamũthiũrũrũkĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">agathambia iria kũrĩa kũriku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">36:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 37:13">Ayub 37:13</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 14:17">Atũm 14:17</ref></char>
    </note>Ũũ nĩguo aathaga ndũrĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na akaheana irio nyingĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Akumbatagĩria rũheni na moko make,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akarwatha rũringe kĩrĩa kĩorotetwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Marurumĩ make nĩmanagĩrĩra kĩhuhũkanio kĩrĩa kĩroka;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ngʼombe nĩimenyithanagia atĩ kũrĩ kĩhuhũkanio kĩroka.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="37" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 38:10">Thab 38:10</ref>; <ref loc="HAB 3:16">Hab 3:16</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndaigua ũguo ngoro yakwa ĩgatumatuuma,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩkambarara ĩkoima handũ hayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Thikĩrĩria! Thikĩrĩria mũraramo wa mũgambo wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũrurumo ũrĩa uumaga kanua gake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 22:13">2Sam 22:13</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:24">Luk 17:24</ref></char>
    </note>Arekagĩrĩria rũheni rwake rungu rwa igũrũ guothe</para>
  <para style="q2">na akarũtũma nginya ituri cia thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:10">1Sam 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:19">Thaam 20:19</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha waruo gũũkaga mũgambo wa mũraramo wake;</para>
  <para style="q2">arurumaga na mũgambo wake mũkaru.</para>
  <para style="q1">Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũgambo wake waiguuo-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ndarigagĩrĩria heni.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 12:29">Joh 12:29</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 5:9">Ayub 5:9</ref></char>
    </note>Mũgambo wa Mũrungu ũrurumaga na njĩra ya magegania;</para>
  <para style="q2">ekaga maũndũ manene tũtangĩhota kũmenya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 38:22">Ayub 38:22</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 7:4">Kĩam 7:4</ref></char>
    </note>Eeraga tharunji atĩrĩ, ‘Gwa thĩ,’</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo mbura ya rũthuthuũ akamĩĩra atĩrĩ, ‘Tuĩka mbura nene.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩatigithagia mũndũ o wothe wĩra wake</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha andũ othe ombĩte mamenye wĩra wake.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:22">Thab 104:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nyamũ nacio nĩciĩhithaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">ciikaraga imamo-inĩ ciacio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Kĩhuhũkanio kiumaga gĩikaro gĩakĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">heho nayo ĩkoima rũhuho-inĩ rũkĩhurutana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Mĩhũmũ ya Mũrungu nĩĩthondekaga mbarabu,</para>
  <para style="q2">namo maaĩ harĩa maaramĩire makanyiitana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩaiyũragia matu na ũigũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ahurunjaga rũheni rũkamatũrĩkia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 147:16">Thab 147:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mathiiaga magĩthiũrũrũkaga</para>
  <para style="q2">o kũrĩa angĩmeerekeria thĩ yothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">mageeke o ũrĩa wothe angĩmaatha.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 9:22-23">Thaam 9:22-23</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 18:45">1Ath 18:45</ref></char>
    </note>Arehaga matu macio nĩguo aherithie andũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana aihũgie thĩ yake na onanie wendani wake.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>“Ayubu, thikĩrĩria ũhoro ũyũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">tithĩria hau wĩcũũranie ũhoro wa magegania ma Mũrungu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Wee nĩũũĩ ũrĩa Ngai aathaga matu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũrĩa atũmaga rũheni rwake rũhenũke?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 36:4">Ayub 36:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee nĩũũĩ ũrĩa matu macio macuurĩtio wega,</para>
  <para style="q2">magegania macio ma ũrĩa ũrĩ ũmenyo mũkinyanĩru?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 27:13">Atũm 27:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee ũringĩkaga nĩ ũrugarĩ wa nguo ciaku</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa bũrũri ũkirĩte ki hĩndĩ ya rũhuho rwa gũthini-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:23">Gũcook 28:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>no ũhote kũruta wĩra nake ũhoro-inĩ wa gũtambũrũkia matu mairũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o macio momĩte o ta gĩcicio gĩa gĩcango?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>“Ta twĩre ũrĩa twagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũmwĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">tũtingĩhota gwĩciirĩra nĩ ũndũ wa nduma iitũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩagĩrĩire kwĩrwo atĩ nĩngwenda kwaria?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ o na ũ ũngiuga amerio?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 5:31">Atiir 5:31</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 22:11">Atũm 22:11</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũrora riũa,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩcangararĩte kũu igũrũ</para>
  <para style="q2">thuutha wakuo kũhaatwo nĩ rũhuho gũgathera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Okaga kuuma mwena wa gathigathini arĩ na riiri ukengeete ta wa thahabu;</para>
  <para style="q2">Ngai okaga arĩ na ũkaru wa gwĩtigĩrwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 6:16">1Tim 6:16</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 18:23">Ezek 18:23</ref></char>
    </note>Ũcio Mwene-Hinya-Wothe-rĩ, tũtingĩhota kũmũkinyĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩatũũgĩrĩtio nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoti wake;</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ wa ũrĩa arĩ wa kĩhooto na ũthingu mũnene-rĩ, ndahinyanagĩrĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">37:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 22:12">Kĩam 22:12</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 5:13">Ayub 5:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio andũ nĩmamũtĩĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ githĩ ndarũmbũyagia arĩa meyonaga ta marĩ oogĩ na ngoro ciao?”</para>
  <chapter number="38" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Jehova</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 14:21">Thaam 14:21</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 40:6">Ayub 40:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jehova agĩcookeria Ayubu ũhoro arĩ kĩhuhũkanio-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Nũũ ũyũ ũrekĩra kĩrĩra gĩakwa nduma</para>
  <para style="q2">na ciugo itarĩ na ũmenyo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 40:7">Ayub 40:7</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 11:29">Mar 11:29</ref></char>
    </note>Wĩhotore ta mũndũ mũrũme;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngũkũũria ciũria, nawe ũkĩnjookerie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:8">1Sam 2:8</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 30:4">Thim 30:4</ref></char>
    </note>“Warĩ kũ rĩrĩa ndaakire mũthingi wa thĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Njĩĩra akorwo ũrĩ na ũũgĩ wa kũmenya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 102:25">Thab 102:25</ref>; <ref loc="JER 31:37">Jer 31:37</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ wathimire mũigana wayo? Ti-itherũ wee nĩũũĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ watambũrũkirie rũrigi rwa gũthima igũrũ rĩayo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 26:7">Ayub 26:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mĩthingi yayo yahandirwo igũrũ rĩa kĩĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana nũũ wahaandire ihiga rĩayo rĩa koine,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njata cia rũciinĩ ciainire hamwe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na araika othe makĩanĩrĩra nĩ gũkena?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 8:29">Thim 8:29</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 1:9-10">Kĩam 1:9-10</ref></char>
    </note>“Nũũ wahingĩrĩirie iria na mĩrango</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa rĩatumũkire kuuma nda,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>rĩrĩa ndatuire matu nguo ciarĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngĩrĩoha nduma nene ta taama warĩo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 28:25">Ayub 28:25</ref>; <ref loc="NEH 3:3">Neh 3:3</ref></char>
    </note>rĩrĩa ndarĩkĩrĩire mĩhaka, na ngĩrĩhingĩra na mĩrango yarĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngĩĩkĩra mĩgĩĩko handũ hayo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 89:9">Thab 89:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>rĩrĩa ndoigire atĩrĩ, ‘Ũkinyage o haha na ndũkanahakĩre;</para>
  <para style="q2">makũmbĩ maku macio metĩĩi-rĩ, hau nĩho marĩĩkinyaga’?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 57:8">Thab 57:8</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 5:8">Amos 5:8</ref></char>
    </note>“Kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria-rĩ, ũrĩ waathana atĩ rũciinĩ rũgĩe ho,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũkĩonereria ũtheri wa rũciinĩ harĩa ũkuumĩrĩra,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>nĩguo ũhote kũnyiita thĩ na mĩthia yaguo,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao arĩa aaganu maribaribwo moime kuo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 28:11">Thaam 28:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thĩ ĩhaanaga ta rĩũmba rĩhũrĩtwo mũhũũri;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũonekere wayo ũtariĩ ta mũhianĩre wa nguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:29">Gũcook 28:29</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 17:14">Kĩam 17:14</ref></char>
    </note>Andũ arĩa aaganu nĩmaimagwo ũtheri wao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na guoko kwao kũrĩa kuoetwo na igũrũ gũkoinwo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Ũrĩ wathiĩ rũgendo nginya kũrĩa iria rĩtherũkagĩra,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũgaceera itwe-inĩ cia ndia kũrĩa kũriku mũno?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:18">Math 16:18</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:9">Ayub 7:9</ref></char>
    </note>Ũrĩ wonio ihingo cia gĩkuũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũrĩ wona ihingo cia kĩĩruru gĩa gĩkuũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ũrĩ wamenya ũnene wa wariĩ wa thĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Njĩĩra akorwo nĩũũĩ maũndũ macio mothe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:4">Kĩam 1:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Njĩra ya gũthiĩ kũrĩa ũtheri ũtũũraga nĩĩrĩkũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nayo nduma ĩikaraga kũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>No ũcitware gwacio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩũũĩ tũcĩra twa gũthiĩ kũrĩa itũũraga?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Ti-itherũ wee nĩũũĩ, nĩgũkorwo warĩ mũciare!</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee-rĩ, nĩũtũũrĩte mĩaka mĩingĩ!</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 37:6">Ayub 37:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ũrĩ watoonya makũmbĩ kũrĩa tharunji ĩigĩtwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũkĩona makũmbĩ kũrĩa mbura ya mbembe ĩigĩtwo,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 30:30">Isa 30:30</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 13:13">Ezek 13:13</ref></char>
    </note>o icio njigĩte nĩ ũndũ wa mahinda ma thĩĩna,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngaciiga nĩ ũndũ wa matukũ ma mbaara na ma kũrũa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Njĩra ya gũthiĩ kũrĩa ũtheri ũgayanagĩrio nĩĩrĩkũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ya gũthiĩ kũrĩa rũhuho rwa irathĩro rũhurunjagĩrwo gũkũ thĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nũũ wenjagĩra mbura ya kĩboboto mũtaro wa kũgerera,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana agatemera mbura ya marurumĩ njĩra,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 36:27">Ayub 36:27</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 41:18">Isa 41:18</ref></char>
    </note>nĩguo mbura yure bũrũri ũtatũũraga mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na yure werũ kũrĩa gũtarĩ mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:14">Thab 104:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>nĩguo ĩhũũnagie kũu gũtiganĩrie gũgakira ihooru,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩtũme kũmere nyeki?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Mbura nĩĩrĩ ithe?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ mũciari wa matata ma ime?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Tharunji yumaga nda ya ũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũciaraga mbaa ĩrĩa yumaga igũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>rĩrĩa maaĩ momaga ta ihiga,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa maaĩ marĩa marĩ igũrũ wa iria magwatana?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:9">Ayub 9:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wee-rĩ, wahota kuohania njata iria thaka cia Kĩrĩmĩra?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wahota kuohora mĩkanda ya njata iria ciĩtagwo Karaũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 23:5">2Ath 23:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 19:13">Jer 19:13</ref></char>
    </note>Wahota kuumagaragia njata iria ciĩtagwo Mazarothu o mahinda maacio maakinya,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana wahota gũtongoria Nduba na ciana ciayo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nĩũũĩ mawatho ma igũrũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">No ũhote kũhaanda wathani wa Ngai ũrũme gũkũ thĩ?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 5:10">Ayub 5:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wahota kwanĩrĩra nginya mũgambo waku ũkinye matu-inĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo kuure wĩhumbĩre na kĩguũ kĩa maaĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Wee nĩwe ũtũmaga heni ithiĩ na njĩra ciacio?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩikũrehagĩra ũhoro igakwĩra atĩ, ‘Tũrĩ haha’?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:5">Jak 1:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nũũ waheire ngoro ũũgĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana akĩhe meciiria ũmenyo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nũũ ũrĩ na ũũgĩ wa gũtara matu?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũngĩhota kũinamia ndigithũ cia maaĩ cia igũrũ</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 26:19">Alaw 26:19</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 18:45">1Ath 18:45</ref></char>
    </note>rĩrĩa rũkũngũ rwatondora,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo ndoro ĩkooma ĩkanyiitana?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 49:9">Kĩam 49:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Nĩwe ũguĩmagĩra mũrũũthi wa mũgoma wone gĩa kũrĩa,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana nĩwe ũniinagĩra mĩrũũthi ngʼaragu</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>rĩrĩa ĩkomereire imamo-inĩ ciayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana rĩrĩa ĩikaraga yoheirie nyamũ ihinga-inĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">38:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 6:26">Math 6:26</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 8:7">Kĩam 8:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ ũheaga ihuru irio</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa tũcui twarĩo tũgũkaĩra Mũrungu</para>
  <para style="q2">tũkĩũrũũraga nĩ kwaga irio?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="39" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 14:5">Gũcook 14:5</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 49:21">Kĩam 49:21</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee nĩũũĩ rĩrĩa mbũri cia irĩma-inĩ iciaraga?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee nĩwĩroragĩra rĩrĩa thwariga ĩgũciara kaana kayo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 31:7-9">Kĩam 31:7-9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wee nĩũtaraga mĩeri ĩrĩa ciikaraga ingĩgaaciara?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩũũĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa iciaraga?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ciĩthunaga igaciara twana twacio;</para>
  <para style="q2">ruo rwacio rwa gũciara rũgathira.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Twana twacio twagĩraga mwĩrĩ, tũgakũra tũrĩ na hinya o kũu gĩthaka-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">tũkinyaga ihinda rĩa kwehera na tũticookaga.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Nũũ warekereirie njagĩ ĩthiiage ĩtarĩ mũũria?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ wamĩohorire mĩhĩndo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 24:5">Ayub 24:5</ref>; <ref loc="JER 14:6">Jer 14:6</ref></char>
    </note>Ndaamĩheire werũ ũtuĩke mũciĩ wayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo bũrũri wa cumbĩ ũtuĩke gĩtũũro kĩayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Ĩthekagĩrĩra inegene rĩrĩ thĩinĩ wa itũũra;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩiguaga mũkaĩrĩrio wa mũtwarithia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 32:20">Isa 32:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ĩrimũthagĩra irĩma-inĩ ĩgĩetha gwa kũrĩa,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩkahaara kahuti o gothe karuru.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 23:22">Ndar 23:22</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 21:6">Thaam 21:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Mbogo ya njamba-rĩ, yetĩkĩra gũgũtungata?</para>
  <para style="q2">No ĩkindĩrie mũharatĩ-inĩ waku ũtukũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>No ũhote kũmĩoha matandĩko ĩrĩme na mũraũ?</para>
  <para style="q2">No ĩkuume thuutha ituamba-inĩ ĩkĩrĩmaga na mũraũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>No ũmĩĩhoke nĩ ũndũ atĩ ĩrĩ na hinya mũingĩ?</para>
  <para style="q2">No ũmĩtigĩre wĩra waku mũritũ ĩrutage?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>No ũmĩĩhoke ĩkũrehere ngano yaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩmĩcookanĩrĩrie kĩhuhĩro-inĩ gĩaku?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 5:9">Zek 5:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mathagu ma nyaga mabatabataga nĩ gũkena,</para>
  <para style="q2">no matingĩgerekanio na mathagu na njoya cia njũũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ĩrekagĩria matumbĩ mayo tĩĩri-inĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩkamatiga mũthanga-inĩ magwate ũrugarĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 14:9">2Ath 14:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>ĩtegwĩciiria atĩ no makinywo na magũrũ makue,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana marangwo nĩ nyamũ ya gĩthaka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LAM 4:3">Maca 4:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ĩĩkaga ciana ciayo ũũru ta itarĩ ciayo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩmakaga atĩ wĩra wayo no ũtuĩke wa tũhũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>nĩgũkorwo Ngai ndaamĩheire ũũgĩ</para>
  <para style="q2">kana akĩmĩhe igai rĩa mwĩciirĩrie mwega.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 5:22">Ayub 5:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, rĩrĩa yatambũrũkia mathagu ĩhanyũke,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩthekagĩrĩra mbarathi na mũmĩhaici.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>“Wee nĩwe ũheaga mbarathi hinya wayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũkamĩhumba ngingo na mũreera?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Wee nĩwe ũtũmaga ĩrũũge ta ngigĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩkahahũra andũ na mũtiihĩre wayo wa mwĩtĩĩo?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Ĩhuragia thĩ na ũcamba ĩgĩkenagĩra hinya wayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩkaguthũka ĩtoonyete mbaara-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ĩthekagĩrĩra guoya, ĩtarĩ ũndũ ĩngĩtigĩra;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩmakagio nĩ rũhiũ rwa njora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 5:28">Isa 5:28</ref>; <ref loc="NAM 3:3">Nahu 3:3</ref></char>
    </note>Thiaka wa mũmĩhaici ũbocabocaga mbaru-inĩ ciayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">hamwe na itimũ rĩkũhenia na mĩcengi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 10:9">Ndar 10:9</ref>; <ref loc="JER 4:5">Jer 4:5</ref>, <ref loc="JER 4:19">19</ref></char>
    </note>Irĩĩaga tĩĩri nĩ ũrũme;</para>
  <para style="q2">ndĩngĩrũgama ĩkindĩirie hĩndĩ ĩrĩa karumbeta kagamba.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa karumbeta kagamba ĩgatiiha, ‘Hĩ!’</para>
  <para style="q2">Ĩnyiitaga thaaha wa mbaara ĩrĩ o haraaya,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩkaigua kayũ ka anene a mbaara, o na mbugĩrĩrio ya mbaara.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 8:7">Jer 8:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Rwĩgĩ-rĩ, nĩwe ũrũhotithagia kũmbũka na ũũgĩ waku,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana gũtambũrũkia mathagu maruo rwerekeire mwena wa gũthini?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="OBA 1:4">Obad 1:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nderi nĩwe ũmĩathaga yũmbũke na igũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩkeyakĩra gĩtara kĩayo igũrũ mũno?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Ĩtũũraga kĩharũrũka-inĩ kĩa ihiga, na nĩ ho ĩraaraga;</para>
  <para style="q2">rũhĩa-inĩ rwa ihiga iraaya mũno nĩ ho mwĩgitio wayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Ĩrĩ hau nĩguo ĩcaragĩria gĩa kũrĩa;</para>
  <para style="q2">maitho mayo moonaga irio irĩ o kũraya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">39:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:28">Math 24:28</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 17:37">Luk 17:37</ref></char>
    </note>Tũcui twayo tũnyuuaga thakame,</para>
  <para style="q2">na handũ harĩa arĩa moragĩtwo marĩ, hau nĩ ho ĩkoragwo.”</para>
  <chapter number="40" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Jehova akĩĩra Ayubu atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 13:3">Ayub 13:3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:20">Arom 9:20</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũndũ ũrĩa ũrũaga na Mwene-Hinya-Wothe-rĩ, no amũrute mahĩtia?</para>
  <para style="q2">Ũcio ũkararagia Ngai-rĩ, nĩakĩmũcookerie!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nake Ayubu agĩcookeria Jehova, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 18:19">Atiir 18:19</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 29:9">Ayub 29:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Niĩ ndiagĩrĩire o na hanini; ndaakĩhota atĩa gũgũcookeria?</para>
  <para style="q2">Nĩndehumbĩra kanua na guoko.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nĩndaririe rĩmwe, no ndirĩ na macookio;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ngĩaria rĩa keerĩ, no ndirĩ na ũndũ ũngĩ nguuga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 14:21">Thaam 14:21</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 38:1">Ayub 38:1</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jehova akĩarĩria Ayubu arĩ kĩhuhũkanio-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 38:3">Ayub 38:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wĩhotore ta mũndũ mũrũme;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngũkũũria ciũria, nawe ũkĩnjookerie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:3">Arom 3:3</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 2:3">Ayub 2:3</ref></char>
    </note>“Gũtua ciira gwakwa na kĩhooto-rĩ, githĩ no ũkũmenererie?</para>
  <para style="q2">Githĩ no ũndue mwĩhia nĩgeetha wee ũtuĩke ndwĩhĩtie?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Wee-rĩ, ũrĩ na guoko ta kwa Mũrungu?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee wahota kũruruma na mũgambo ta wake?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:1">Thab 104:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ta kĩĩgemie na riiri na ũkengi,</para>
  <para style="q2">na wĩhumbe gĩtĩĩo na ũnene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEP 1:18">Zef 1:18</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 2:11">Isa 2:11</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 2:12">12</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 2:17">17</ref></char>
    </note>Rekereria marakara mahiũ ma mangʼũrĩ maku,</para>
  <para style="q2">wone mũndũ o wothe mwĩtĩĩi ũmũharũrũkie,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:7">1Sam 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 10:5">Zek 10:5</ref></char>
    </note>rora mũndũ o wothe mwĩtĩĩi na ũmũnyiihie,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmemende andũ arĩa aaganu o harĩa marũngiĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 16:31-34">Ndar 16:31-34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mathike othe hamwe tĩĩri-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmoohe mothiũ na nduma kũu mbĩrĩra-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 15:6">Thaam 15:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 41:10">Isa 41:10</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo niĩ mwene nĩngetĩkania nawe</para>
  <para style="q2">atĩ guoko gwaku mwene kwa ũrĩo no gũkũhonokie.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>“Ta rora nyamũ ĩrĩa ĩtagwo Behemothu,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">40:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ĩno yarĩ nyamũ ĩmwe ya iria ciatũũraga thĩ tene. (O na 41:1)</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">ĩyo ndoombire hamwe nawe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩrĩĩaga nyeki ta ndegwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 39:11">Ayub 39:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ hinya ũigana atĩa ĩrĩ naguo njohero,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩ ũhoti mũnene atĩa ũrĩ mĩkiha-inĩ yayo ya nda!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ĩinagia mũtingʼoe wayo ta mũtarakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">nga cia ciero ciayo ciohanĩtio hamwe ta mĩhĩndo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Mahĩndĩ mayo mahaana ta mĩberethi ya gĩcango,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ciĩga ciayo cihaana ta irungʼo cia kĩgera.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 41:33">Ayub 41:33</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:24">Kĩam 3:24</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩyo nyamũ ya mbere harĩ ciũmbe cia Mũrungu,</para>
  <para style="q2">no rĩrĩ, Mũũmbi wayo nowe ũngĩmĩkuhĩrĩria na rũhiũ rwake rwa njora.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:14">Thab 104:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Irĩma ĩmĩheaga maciaro maacio,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nyamũ ciothe cia gĩthaka itũũhagĩra gũkuhĩ na kũu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 41:2">Kĩam 41:2</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 8:11">Ayub 8:11</ref></char>
    </note>Ĩkomaga rungu rwa mahũa ma maaĩ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩĩhithĩte thĩinĩ wa ithanjĩ kũrĩa kũrĩ mũtondo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Mahũa macio ma maaĩ-inĩ makamĩhitha;</para>
  <para style="q2">nakĩo kĩĩruru kĩa mĩtĩ ya irura hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia karũũĩ gĩkamĩthiũrũrũkĩria.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 8:7">Isa 8:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 3:1">Josh 3:1</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa rũũĩ ruoka na nditi, ndĩmakaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngitĩre, o na Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani rũngĩmĩiyũrĩrĩra nginya kanua.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">40:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 19:28">2Ath 19:28</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kũrĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũmĩnyiita rĩrĩa ĩĩhũũgĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana amĩtege, amĩtũrĩkie iniũrũ na amĩĩkĩre kĩana kĩa rũrigi?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter number="41" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 3:8">Ayub 3:8</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 4:2">Amos 4:2</ref></char>
    </note>“No ũhote kũguucũrũria nyamũ ĩrĩa ĩĩtagwo Leviathani na ndwano,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana wohe rũrĩmĩ rwayo na mũkanda?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 19:4">Ezek 19:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No ũhote kũmĩtoonyia rũrigi iniũrũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũmĩtũrĩkanie rũthĩa na ndwano?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>No ĩtinde ĩgĩgũthaitha ũmĩiguĩre tha?</para>
  <para style="q2">No ĩkwarĩrie na ciugo cia ũhooreri?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 21:6">Thaam 21:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No ĩrĩkanĩre nawe ũthiĩ nayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩtũũre ĩrĩ ngombo yaku nginya tene?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>No ũhote kũmĩhooreria ta nyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũmĩoherere handũ nĩguo airĩtu aku mamĩmeemagie?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Onjoria no mamĩkũũranie na indo ciao?</para>
  <para style="q2">No mamĩgayanie kũrĩ onjorithia?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 40:24">Ayub 40:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No ũhote gũtheecanga rũũa rwayo na mĩcengi,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana ũtheecange mũtwe wayo na mĩcengi ĩrĩa ĩtegaga thamaki?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ũngĩmĩhutia na guoko,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũngĩtũũra ũririkanaga kĩgiano kĩu, na ndũngĩgacookera!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mwĩrĩgĩrĩro wa atĩ no ũmĩtoorie nĩ kwĩheenia;</para>
  <para style="q2">o kũmĩona tu nĩkũiganĩte gũtũma mũndũ amake, orwo nĩ hinya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CH 20:6">2Maũ 20:6</ref>; <ref loc="JER 50:44">Jer 50:44</ref></char>
    </note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrĩ ũcamba mũiganu wa kũmĩarahũra.</para>
  <para style="q2">Nũũ ũngĩkĩhota kwĩĩndiiria niĩ?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 11:35">Arom 11:35</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 10:26">1Akor 10:26</ref></char>
    </note>Nũũ ũngĩnandũra kĩndũ atĩ nĩguo ndĩmũrĩhe?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kĩndũ gĩothe kĩrĩ rungu rwa igũrũ nĩ gĩakwa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“Ndikwaga kwaria ũhoro wa ciĩga ciayo,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na wa hinya wayo, na wa ũthaka wayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nũũ ũngĩhota kũmĩaũra nguo yayo ya igũrũ?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nũũ ũngĩmĩkuhĩrĩria amĩĩkĩre matamu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:13">Thab 22:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nũũ ũngĩũmĩrĩria kũmĩathamia kanua,</para>
  <para style="q2">kau kaiyũrĩte magego ma kũmakania?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Mũgongo wayo ũrĩ na ngo ciĩiganĩrĩire mĩhari,</para>
  <para style="q2">ikomanĩire ikanyiitana;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>o ĩmwe ĩnyiitanĩte na ĩrĩa ĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũũ atĩ gũtirĩ rĩera rĩngĩtoonyera gatagatĩ ga cio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Igwatanĩtio hamwe irĩ nũmu;</para>
  <para style="q2">inyiitanĩte hamwe ũndũ itangĩtigithũkana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 3:9">Ayub 3:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Gũtiiha kwayo kũmenũkagia ũtheri;</para>
  <para style="q2">maitho mayo nĩ ta mĩrũri ya rũciinĩ gũgĩthererũka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 10:6">Dan 10:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Imũrĩ cia mwaki ciumaga kanua-inĩ kayo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩrathũkagia thandĩ cia mwaki.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ĩrutaga ndogo na maniũrũ</para>
  <para style="q2">taarĩ nyũngũ ĩratherũka ĩhagĩrĩtwo igũrũ rĩa mwaki wa ithanjĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:4">Isa 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="JER 4:4">Jer 4:4</ref></char>
    </note>Mĩhũmũ yayo ĩgwatagia makara mwaki,</para>
  <para style="q2">naruo rũrĩrĩmbĩ rũkoima kanua kayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ngingo-inĩ yayo nĩho hinya wayo ũkoragwo,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa ũmakagia kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩtũnganaga nayo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Mĩgũtha ya nyama ciayo nĩmĩnyiitanu mũno;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ mĩrũmu ũũ atĩ ndĩngĩenyenyeka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 18:6">Math 18:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ngoro yayo yũmĩte ta ihiga,</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩkooma ta ihiga rĩa gũthĩa rĩa na thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa yarahũka, arĩa marĩ hinya nĩmamakaga;</para>
  <para style="q2">mooraga ĩtanamahũũra.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 8:18">Josh 8:18</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 40:24">Ayub 40:24</ref></char>
    </note>Gũtirĩ rũhiũ rwa njora rũngĩmĩĩka ũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana itimũ, kana mũguĩ, kana mĩcengi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Harĩ Leviathani-rĩ, kĩgera no ta nyeki nyũmũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakĩo gĩcango no ta gĩcunjĩ kĩbuthu kĩa mũtĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 91:5">Thab 91:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mĩguĩ ndĩngĩtũma yũre;</para>
  <para style="q2">mahiga ma kĩgũtha no ta mũũngũ harĩ yo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Harĩ yo njũgũma no ta gacunjĩ ka rũnyeki rũmũ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩthekagĩrĩra kũbĩrĩrĩka gwa itimũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 28:27">Isa 28:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nda yayo nĩ ta rũgĩo rũrĩ na mageca;</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩtigaga ngururo ndaka-inĩ ta cia ngaari iria ikonyoraga ngano.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:14">1Sam 2:14</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 32:2">Ezek 32:2</ref></char>
    </note>Ĩtũmaga iria kũrĩa kũriku gũtherũke ta nyũngũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩkoiruga iria ta nyũngũ ya maguta ma kwĩhaka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Harĩa yagerera ĩtigaga mũhari ũkũhenia;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũndũ no eciirie atĩ ndia ĩrĩ na mbuĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ kĩndũ kĩngĩigananio nayo gũkũ thĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ kĩũmbe gĩtarĩ guoya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">41:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 18:27">Thab 18:27</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 6:17">Thim 6:17</ref></char>
    </note>Ĩnyũrũragia kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩĩtũũgagĩria;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩyo mũthamaki wa kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩĩtĩĩaga.”</para>
  <chapter number="42" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mĩario ya Ayubu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ Ayubu agĩcookeria Jehova, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 18:14">Kĩam 18:14</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 4:28">Atũm 4:28</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩnjũũĩ atĩ wahota gwĩka maũndũ mothe;</para>
  <para style="q2">gũtirĩ mũbango waku ũngĩgirĩrĩka.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nĩworirie atĩrĩ, ‘Nũũ ũyũ ũrahithania kĩrĩra gĩakwa nĩ kwaga ũmenyo?’</para>
  <para style="q2">Ti-itherũ ndaaririe maũndũ itaamenyete,</para>
  <para style="q2">maũndũ ma magegania itangĩmenya.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 38:3">Ayub 38:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Woigire atĩrĩ, ‘Thikĩrĩria rĩu, na niĩ njarie;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngũkũũria ciũria, nawe nĩũkũnjookeria.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 10:17">Arom 10:17</ref>; <ref loc="JDG 13:22">Atiir 13:22</ref></char>
    </note>Matũ makwa nĩmaiguĩte ũhoro waku</para>
  <para style="q2">no rĩu maitho makwa nĩgũkuona makuonete.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 40:4">Ayub 40:4</ref>; <ref loc="EZR 9:6">Ezar 9:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩngwĩmena niĩ mwene,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndĩrire, ndĩhurĩrie rũkũngũ na mũhu.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ndeto cia Kũrĩkĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 1:7">Josh 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha wa Jehova kwĩra Ayubu maũndũ macio-rĩ, nĩerire Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani atĩrĩ, “Nĩndakarĩtio nĩwe na arata aku eerĩ, tondũ mũtiarĩtie ũhoro wakwa ũrĩa wagĩrĩire, ta ũrĩa ndungata yakwa Ayubu ĩĩkĩte. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">42:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 23:1">Ndar 23:1</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:15-16">Jak 5:15-16</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 20:7">Kĩam 20:7</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, rĩu oyai ndegwa mũgwanja na ndũrũme mũgwanja, mũthiĩ kũrĩ ndungata yakwa Ayubu, mũkarute igongona rĩa njino nĩ ũndũ wanyu inyuĩ ene. Ndungata yakwa Ayubu nĩĩkamũhoera, na niĩ nĩngetĩkĩra mahooya make, na ndikamwĩka kũringana na ũrimũ wanyu. Mũtiarĩtie ũhoro wakwa ũrĩa wagĩrĩire ta ũrĩa ndungata yakwa Ayubu ĩĩkĩte.” <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">42:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 19:21">Kĩam 19:21</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 14:14">Ezek 14:14</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Elifazu ũrĩa Mũtemaani, na Bilidadi ũrĩa Mũshuhi, na Zofaru ũrĩa Mũnaamathi magĩĩka o ta ũrĩa Jehova aameerire; nake Jehova nĩetĩkĩrire ihooya rĩa Ayubu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">42:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 30:3">Gũcook 30:3</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:8-9">Afil 2:8-9</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha wa Ayubu kũhoera arata ake-rĩ, Jehova nĩamũcookeirie ũtonga wake na akĩmũhe maita meerĩ ma indo iria aarĩ nacio mbere. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">42:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 9:13">Ayub 9:13</ref></char></note>Ariũ na aarĩ a nyina othe, na mũndũ o wothe wamũũĩ mbere, magĩũka makĩrĩĩanĩra nake mũciĩ gwake, nao makĩmũhooreria na makĩmũcakaithia nĩ ũndũ wa mathĩĩna marĩa mothe Jehova aamũreheire. Andũ acio o mũndũ akĩmũhe gĩcunjĩ kĩa betha na gĩcũhĩ gĩa thahabu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Jehova nĩarathimire matukũ ma mũthia ma muoyo wa Ayubu gũkĩra marĩa ma mbere. Nĩaagĩire na ngʼondu 14,000, na ngamĩĩra 6,000, na ndegwa cia kuohwo macooki 1,000, na ndigiri 1,000. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nĩacookire akĩgĩa na aanake mũgwanja na airĩtu atatũ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Mwarĩ wa mbere aamũtuire Jemima, na wa keerĩ aamũtuire Kezia, nake wa gatatũ akĩmũtua Kereni-Hapuku. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ handũ o na ha bũrũri-inĩ wothe hangĩonekire andũ-a-nja athaka ta airĩtu a Ayubu, nake ithe wao akĩmahe igai hamwe na ariũ a nyina.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Thuutha wa maũndũ macio-rĩ, Ayubu nĩatũũrire mĩaka igana rĩa mĩrongo ĩna; akĩona ciana ciake na akĩona ciana ciacio, nginya rũciaro rwa kana. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">42:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 15:15">Kĩam 15:15</ref></char></note>Nake agĩkua arĩ mũkũrũ, na arĩ na mĩaka mĩingĩ.</para>
</usx>
